# TODO: Translation updated at 2026-06-05 10:23

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_42360e89:

    # "The lock is loose."
    "鎖鬆開了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9fc507f6:

    # "I can pull it off the bars."
    "能從欄杆上拉下來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:12
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_73830a0c:

    # "For some reason, there the air feels a little lighter. Like pressure from a valve being released through a nozzle."
    "不知為何，空氣感覺輕鬆了一些。像是閥門中的壓力從噴嘴釋放了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:14
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_47f51ff3:

    # "Ralph lets out a one note laugh."
    "Ralph笑了一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:15
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3384420f:

    # ra "\"So how {i}did{/i} you know how to open that?\""
    ra "所以{i}你是怎麼知道{/i} 要怎麼打開那東西的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:17
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_50a1bb40:

    # "I’m not sure if I should say it was Dahlia who left us the bread crumbs."
    "我不確定該不該說出是Dahlia留線索給我們的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:18
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7a2cbe1e:

    # "Seems like she’s gone out of her way to stay out of this as much as possible, for whatever reason."
    "出於某種原因，她始終都想盡量置身事外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:22
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e38ef156:

    # mu "\"Must have been one of the combinations we’ve come across in my mother’s office during the search.\""
    mu "一定是我們在搜查母親辦公室時發現的其中一個組合。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:25
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bff92a5a:

    # "Ralph looks doubtful."
    "Ralph面帶質疑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:27
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_481d974f:

    # "I can tell from the look on Blithe’s face that she doesn’t believe that for a second."
    "Blithe的表情則顯示她一點都不信。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:28
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1ddf8a2:

    # "But neither of them speak up."
    "但兩人都沒開口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:37
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c9004566:

    # nei "\"Don’t go leaving us in anticipation now.\""
    nei "別一直吊我們胃口了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:41
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a4e898ea:

    # reu "\"I’d like to see what’s inside as well.\""
    reu "我也想看看裡面是什麼！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:44
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c9228e6a:

    # reu "\"Hurry up.\""
    reu "快點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:47
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8b7dc5a9:

    # ji "\"Just make sure somebody keeps a gun aimed forward.\""
    ji "先確保有人一直拿槍指向前。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:50
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1a3eacf6:

    # ji "\"Whoever we saw before {i}is{/i} still probably down here.\""
    ji "我們之前看到的人，大概{i}還在{/i} 還在下面。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:56
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a7925863:

    # "The fake wall moved a little too smoothly for the kind of thing it was."
    "假牆與外觀不符，移動得有點太滑順了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:60
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_68ff60ce:

    # "There’s a light switch on the side of the wall too."
    "牆邊還有一道電燈開關。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:63
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2073fa92:

    # "It works."
    "能用。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:65
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f260f927:

    # "Doesn’t sit right with me."
    "感覺不太對勁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:66
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6800323a:

    # "What we see behind it doesn’t make much sense ‘neither."
    "出現在牆後的景象同樣不太合理。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:67
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_44c11ada:

    # "A long hallway decked with polished wood. The kind you’d find at the front of a soda shop."
    "是一條長廊，鋪著那種能在汽水店前面看到的拋光木板。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:68
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6217095a:

    # "Ralph surveys the shelves and lets out a low whistle."
    "Ralph檢閱架子，吹了一聲低沉的口哨。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:70
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ecbe2350:

    # ra "\"Laudanum, heroin, strychnine, and milk thistle.\""
    ra "阿片酊、海洛因、士的寧和奶薊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:72
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8ad6649c:

    # ra "\"There’s loads of medicine in these cabinets.\""
    ra "這些櫃子裡有一大堆藥。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:74
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fc9c7ea9:

    # ra "\"Some of these brands I recognize.\""
    ra "有些品牌我認得。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:76
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e3bf376b:

    # ra "\"Some of this looks like it was personally sourced.\""
    ra "有些像是私下管道取得的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:78
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c55aafa1:

    # "He chuckles to himself."
    "他暗暗輕笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:79
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_74f004b0:

    # ra "\"Somebody’s been stockpiling for a very long time.\""
    ra "有人囤了好一大段時間的貨囉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:84
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_de202b8a:

    # "Reubin looks around himself and hums."
    "Reubin環顧四周，哼了一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:86
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5587c13c:

    # reu "\"Say, Jim.\""
    reu "我說，Jim。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:89
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f0f3ce7c:

    # ji "\"Yes?\""
    ji "嗯？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:91
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_235591f8:

    # "Jim sounds a little more strained than usual."
    "Jim的聲色比平時緊繃了些。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:92
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1a4c3955:

    # "He doesn’t seem happy to know about this room."
    "發現這間房，他似乎不太高興。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:94
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ae231c2c:

    # reu "\"Do you think it’s possible that this building was initially used as an infirmary?\""
    reu "你覺得這棟建築，本來是用來當醫務室的嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:96
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_191138bd:

    # "Jim is still looking at the shelves rather than Reubin."
    "Jim依舊望著櫃子，沒有看Reubin。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:98
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eee0d5ed:

    # ji "\"Why do you say that?\""
    ji "怎麼這麼問？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:101
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aace6b8a:

    # "I can see there’s also a door frame at the end of the hall that leads into a larger honeycomb chamber with a domed roof."
    "我看到走廊盡頭還有一道門框，通往一個更大的蜂巢狀圓頂房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:102
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_712a80f1:

    # "There's a door on each wall."
    "每面牆都有一扇門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:117
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c63f924b:

    # ji "\"I knew your mother was severe, but I didn’t know she’d built a gulag beneath the school.\""
    ji "我是知道你媽很嚴厲，但沒想到她甚至在學校底下建了個古拉格。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:120
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9e85264e:

    # dh "\"No.\""
    dh "不。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:122
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_52bea8d3:

    # "Dahlia shakes her head."
    "Dahlia搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:124
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_139d2382:

    # dh "\"These rooms were built before her.\""
    dh "這些房間在她來之前就建好了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:127
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_98b139ff:

    # "Neil’s eyes narrow."
    "Neil眯起眼睛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:129
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_11ed1cbb:

    # nei "\"And how would you know?\""
    nei "這妳怎麼知道？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:131
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1f77492a:

    # "She points at the wall."
    "她指向牆壁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:133
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a106e5bc:

    # dh "\"See the datemarks on the lumber?\""
    dh "看到木材上的日期戳記了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:137
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3d9d9549:

    # mu "\"Says 1855.\""
    mu "上面寫著1855。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:141
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b11e5ff8:

    # ji "\"No need to be on guard, I was merely trying to lighten the mood.\""
    ji "不用那麼警戒，我只是想緩和氣氛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:145
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ef71a673:

    # bl "\"You had the right idea.\""
    bl "你的想法是對的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:150
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_833c704c:

    # bl "\"These doors only lock from the outside.\""
    bl "這些門只能從外側上鎖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:152
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eaf6963f:

    # "I idly unlock one of them and swing it open."
    "我隨手解鎖並甩開其中一扇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:154
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_53b7f699:

    # ji "\"Now wait a minute--\""
    ji "等一下——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:156
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b25728aa:

    # mu "\"Sam, what are you--\""
    mu "Sam，你是在——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:158
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e1a3e938:

    # "I move out of the way to show them what I see."
    "我移開，給他們瞧瞧我看到了什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:160
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_21b73de1:

    # "Just a little room, with a small desk and a made bed."
    "只是一間小房間，有張小桌子和打理好的床。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:165
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_79a248d6:

    # m "\"Bit plush for a prison, ain’t it?\""
    m "以監獄而言，是不是有點太豪華了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:167
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2d4d0909:

    # ra "\"What’s that supposed to mean?\""
    ra "你這話什麼意思？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:168
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0093c302:

    # m "\"I mean all the county jail gives you is a pillow if you’re lucky.\""
    m "我是說，在郡監獄能有個枕頭都要偷笑了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:170
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c09adc9f:

    # ji "\"...You’ve been arrested?\""
    ji "……你被逮捕過？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:172
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_79cf73fc:

    # "All eyes look to me."
    "眾人全看向我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:174
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_83b24450:

    # m "\"Of course.\""
    m "那當然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:176
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_073a419d:

    # m "\"You all know what I do.\""
    m "你們都知道我是做什麼的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:178
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7ee8d7e6:

    # "The ones who don’t know about what I do for William seem to buy it and look away."
    "不清楚我跟William做了啥勾當的人，似乎都接受了這個說法並別開視線。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:180
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_35fc8e5e:

    # "My cheeks feel a little bit hot."
    "我的臉頰有點發燙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:185
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3007a12d:

    # reu "\"More support for my infirmary idea.\""
    reu "那我的醫務室猜想就更站得住腳了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:188
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a07b66de:

    # reu "\"It’s not unusual for schools to host infirmaries during an epidemic.\""
    reu "在流行病期間，學校設置醫務室並不罕見。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:191
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_883d61c0:

    # reu "\"But if the local churches took up that responsibility, and the facilities were never used--\""
    reu "但如果當地教會承擔了責任，而這些設施未曾被使用——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:195
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_842fea37:

    # ji "\"These facilities were never used.\""
    ji "這些設施從來沒被用過。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:200
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1670f75:

    # ji "\"At least not in our time at school.\""
    ji "至少在我們學生時代沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:213
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5f215d53:

    # me "\"So who’s still making the beds?\""
    me "那現在是誰還在整理床鋪？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:216
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b9452ad3:

    # mu "\"{i}Why{/i} are they making the beds?\""
    mu "又{i}為何{/i} 要整理床鋪？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:221
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_17327c23:

    # bl "\"Take a look.\""
    bl "你們看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:225
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1a4b0ccc:

    # "The cat pulls the chair away from the wall."
    "貓把椅子從牆邊拉開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:228
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_146b144a:

    # "Next, she pulls away the desk."
    "然後拉開桌子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:230
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_78f935aa:

    # "Then she points down."
    "並指向下方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:232
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_193d589f:

    # "I blink to make sure I’m not imagining something."
    "我眨眼確認自己沒有看錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:234
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1edb9a82:

    # "The floor is looking up at us."
    "地板正仰望著我們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:236
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7e9b239b:

    # "Carved into the wood is a staring eyeball."
    "木頭上雕刻著一隻瞪大的眼睛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:238
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7ba09029:

    # "It’s draped in the heavy eyelid of its sinking skin."
    "被沉重下垂的眼皮覆蓋。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:240
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2bc6bacd:

    # "It’s so detailed I half expect it to blink."
    "細緻到我以為它會眨眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:242
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6f9a23a8:

    # "There are words carved below it too."
    "下面還刻著文字。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:244
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c76e55b1:

    # "{i}Just his look.{/i}"
    "{i}他的目光。{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:258
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9f66acd8:

    # mu "\"That’s unexpected.\""
    mu "這倒是出乎意料。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:260
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9a5f16d2:

    # "Ralph looks down at the big eye and chews the inside of his cheek."
    "Ralph低頭看著那隻大眼，咬著臉頰內側。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:262
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_de5704ed:

    # ra "\"Ya think?\""
    ra "這還用說？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:265
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ce928a3f:

    # mu "\"I mean that it looks like drawings I’ve seen of Balor’s evil eye.\""
    mu "我是說，它很像我見過的巴羅爾邪眼圖畫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:267
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c0ccb56a:

    # "I take a look at it again."
    "我又看了一眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:269
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1af69389:

    # "We’re all looking at it."
    "我們都在看它。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:271
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d32c360f:

    # "Time seems to pass a little slower when I do."
    "我看著的時候，感覺時間似乎過得慢了一些。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:273
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8a878b57:

    # "So I speak up."
    "於是開口問："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:287
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4fc5c7ef:

    # m "\"...Who?\""
    m "……誰？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:288
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d0f335ac:

    # "Murdoch clears his throat."
    "Murdoch清了清嗓子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:291
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5b12a686:

    # mu "\"He’s just a monster from old Eire mythology.\""
    mu "愛爾蘭神話中的怪物。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:293
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a516886b:

    # mu "\"Not exactly something you’d expect to see out here in the desert, even among the immigrants.\""
    mu "哪怕在移民之間，也沒人會人預料到在這片沙漠中看到這東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:296
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aa308c39:

    # "Blithe ignores us and hooks her claws into the carved lid."
    "Blithe無視我們，用爪鉤住雕刻的蓋板。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:300
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cb39077f:

    # "The trapdoor rises, letting out a noise like it’s yawning."
    "活板門升起，發出像在打呵欠的聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:301
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_904858f9:

    # "There’s a drop below but just a small one."
    "有小小一段落差。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:308
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_383f1c00:

    # "Blithe doesn’t hesitate to hop in."
    "Blithe毫不猶豫地跳進去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:309
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6b372d66:

    # ra "\"Hey, you shouldn’t do that.\""
    ra "喂，妳別這樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:311
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1908acd3:

    # "He says it fairly casually."
    "他隨興一說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:314
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d6109281:

    # "The door closes after her with a clang." with vpunch
    "門在她身後砰地一聲蓋上。" with vpunch

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:316
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c870db3f:

    # "I reach down to grab at it, to open it back up."
    "我伸手去抓，想打開門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:318
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_87417fc6:

    # "But it’s stuck."
    "但是卡住了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:319
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1379f74e:

    # "My heart jumps in my chest as the rest of our party rushes forward."
    "我的心猛然一跳，其他人也衝了上來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:330
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c4100b24:

    # "Then it opens."
    "然後門開了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:331
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_04c3b59b:

    # "The cat’s head pops out."
    "貓的頭冒了出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:334
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6a3c39de:

    # bl "\"Just fuckin’ with ya.\""
    bl "只是鬧鬧你們而已。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:336
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_087c9f79:

    # "The tense silence lets her know that none of us appreciated that."
    "緊繃的沉默讓她知道我們沒人欣賞這個玩笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:337
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a40fa3f9:

    # bl "\"There’s more tunnel down here but I don’t think it leads far.\""
    bl "下面還有更多隧道，但應該沒有多長。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:340
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f36de157:

    # mu "\"Would we even fit down there?\""
    mu "我們能擠得下去嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:342
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_80587ea7:

    # bl "\"I can if I crouch. A grown man definitely could if he crawled on his hands and knees.\""
    bl "我蹲著就可以。只要匍匐前進，大男人肯定也行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:343
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4be0f1ca:

    # bl "\"But it gets wider the farther you go.\""
    bl "不過越往前就越寬。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:344
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e6ecc810:

    # bl "\"There’s a chamber with a big capstone in the middle of it.\""
    bl "有個房間中央有一大塊頂石。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:345
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1712ae19:

    # bl "\"I need somebody big enough to help me move it.\""
    bl "來個夠壯的人幫我移開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:347
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5e49c8aa:

    # m "\"Hell no.\""
    m "我絕對不要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:349
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9122812f:

    # bl "\"Okay.\""
    bl "好吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:351
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c9783129:

    # bl "\"I don’t give a shit who does it, but it’s gotta be somebody with stronger legs and arms than I’ve got. This thing is a bitch to move.\""
    bl "我是不管你們誰要來，只要手腳比我強壯就行。這死東西難搬得很。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:353
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_01d93c8f:

    # ra "\"I’ll go.\""
    ra "我去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:356
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8e0f7fb0:

    # bl "\"I {i}said{/i} stronger arms and legs than me.\""
    bl "我{i}說了{/i} 要手腳比我強壯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:368
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_25f42159:

    # bl "\"What about the rich guys? They’re big enough.\""
    bl "那些有錢人呢？他們塊頭夠大。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:372
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_91fb3322:

    # nei "\"I haven’t made it to where I am in life by dropping into dark holes.\""
    nei "我又不是靠跳進深坑才爬到今天這個地位的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:375
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_44a70271:

    # reu "\"I’d just be in the way.\""
    reu "我也只會礙事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:378
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_afcf219a:

    # "Jim looks between the two of them. They both seem to be avoiding everyone else’s gaze."
    "Jim看向他們兩個。雙方都在躲著他人的目光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:380
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_871c4582:

    # ji "\"I’ll go.\""
    ji "那我去吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:384
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c445a00f:

    # "That snaps their attention back to him."
    "他們的注意力應聲回到他身上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:387
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a136d429:

    # reu "\"Now that’s a bit cavalier for you, don’t you think?\""
    reu "你也太有騎士精神了吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:390
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9dd2232b:

    # nei "\"Prodding at deep holes in the earth certainly is his speciality.\""
    nei "打探地球上的深坑，確實是他的專長。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:395
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_79125958:

    # ji "\"If I’m going to be here then it strikes me I should be useful.\""
    ji "既然來都來了，總該派上點用場吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:397
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_60de10a2:

    # "The jab rolls off the dog like water on wax paper but the cat’s fur bristles."
    "這句挖苦對那隻狗來說像水珠滑過蠟紙，貓卻毛髮直豎。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:400
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ef276451:

    # reu "\"Make better decisions and you won’t need to see how useful I am with a tourniquet.\""
    reu "你們別做傻事，就用不著明白我止血帶在我手裡多麼有用。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:402
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8eb171e9:

    # "I motion at Reubin."
    "我指向Reubin。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:403
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_052aee31:

    # m "\"I agree with him.\""
    m "我同意他說的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:405
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dbde96af:

    # mu "\"If the five of us go together, will you come down, Sam?\""
    mu "如果我們五個人一起下去，你要來嗎，Sam？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:406
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d86c26b6:

    # m "\"For what purpose?\""
    m "為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:408
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b6cd45a2:

    # mu "\"I think I need to know what’s down there.\""
    mu "我感覺應該要探明下面有什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:410
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a6d77dbe:

    # m "\"It won’t be anything good.\""
    m "不會是什麼好東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:412
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cc9fda47:

    # mu "\"It doesn’t have to be good if it explains what’s going on down here.\""
    mu "不需要是好東西，只要能解釋這裡發生的事就好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:414
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_396b6edd:

    # "He looks back at his sister, then lowers his voice."
    "他回頭看他妹妹，然後壓低聲音："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:415
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_155f2e33:

    # mu "\"She’s still not telling me something.\""
    mu "她還有事瞞著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:416
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_43b32bc7:

    # mu "\"If it’s about the particular about what’s going on with this town, she might never say.\""
    mu "如果是關於這個小鎮正在發生的事，她恐怕永遠不會說出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:417
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_937c191f:

    # mu "\"It might be something she needs me to see for myself...\""
    mu "可能有些事，她要我親眼目睹……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:418
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_14a8650d:

    # m "\"But what would be the {i}point{/i}?\""
    m "但這有什麼意義？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:419
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0b1ee227:

    # m "\"And why’s it gotta be {i}you{/i}?\""
    m "而且為什麼一定要是你？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:420
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_128fa6ff:

    # "He doesn’t answer immediately."
    "他沒有馬上回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:421
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5aa39db3:

    # m "\"You don’t even know what you’re looking for, do you?\""
    m "你連自己在找什麼都不知道，對不對？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:423
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4644884e:

    # "He scowls at me."
    "他對我皺眉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:424
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_04d60e4b:

    # mu "\"...Are you coming or not?\""
    mu "……你到底來不來？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:429
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_226a4451:

    # "Murdoch has already disappeared into the hole with {nw}"
    "Murdoch已經消失在洞裡，{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:431
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7bca8db8:

    # extend "Ralph following closely behind, a flashlight in his paw."
    extend "Ralph爪拿手電筒，緊跟在後。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:436
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_544d3f01:

    # bl "\"It’s up this way.\""
    bl "往這邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:438
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_59ddb484:

    # "She sure as hell wasn’t lying about how narrow the tunnel was."
    "她確實沒騙人，這隧道有夠窄。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:440
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cf10c7ae:

    # m "\"Is that even safe to go through?\""
    m "這樣走真的安全嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:442
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0a968f5e:

    # ji "\"The walls here are unnaturally smooth.\""
    ji "這裡的牆壁光滑得很不自然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:443
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_35e8be37:

    # "I can hear Jim’s voice right next to me, but I can’t see him as clearly."
    "Jim的聲音就在我身邊響起，但看不太清楚他的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:444
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_03b7f413:

    # ji "\"Whoever did this used an acid compound to melt though solid bedrock.\""
    ji "做這件事的人用了酸性化合物來熔化堅硬的基岩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:446
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_979a4fbe:

    # ji "\"You’re climbing through solid rock, and there’s no indication of fissures.\""
    ji "我們在固體岩石中爬行，卻完全沒看見裂縫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:448
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_47b22b0f:

    # "He sounds a bit unnerved when he says that for some reason."
    "出於某種緣故，他的語氣有點不安。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:450
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a1fa868b:

    # m "\"So what’s the problem, then?\""
    m "這有什麼問題嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:452
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_117a2f2b:

    # ji "\"This looks far more stable than anything I’ve ever seen in the mines.\""
    ji "這看起來遠比我在礦坑見過的任何事物來得穩定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:454
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f76bf814:

    # ji "\"This would have been an elaborate, expensive, and time consuming process.\""
    ji "是極其複雜、昂貴又耗時的工程。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:456
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c353f2cd:

    # mu "\"So then there’s no reason to stop going.\""
    mu "那就沒有理由止步不前了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:458
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_025b7975:

    # "Murdoch sticks his head into the hole first, then wriggles his way past dirt and roots, his tail disappearing into the earth."
    "Murdoch先把頭伸進洞裡，然後扭動身體越過泥土和樹根，尾巴消失在地底。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:459
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c013f602:

    # ji "\"That’s not the point.\""
    ji "問題不在這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:461
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_db8f5f8f:

    # "Murdoch seems uninterested in listening."
    "Murdoch好像沒興趣聽。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:463
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_110e172c:

    # "I hear him grunt and grumble as I follow his twitching tail through that slim passage, short enough to move through with ease, but just deep and dark enough to make me wonder why it exists."
    "我跟著他抽動的尾巴穿過狹窄的通道，一路聽著他悶哼和嘟嚷。這通道短到可以輕鬆通過，但又深又黑，讓我好奇是為何而存在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:465
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9168a5e6:

    # "I touch the wall to follow it along, and Jim is right."
    "我摸著牆壁前進，發現Jim說得沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:467
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1150877f:

    # "It’s smooth to the touch."
    "摸起來很光滑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:469
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8fab2cb0:

    # "For some reason I get the same feeling I used to get back at the church my parents used to take me to."
    "不知怎麼地，我產生了一種和以前爸媽帶我去教堂時相同的感覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:471
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c7feb665:

    # "It was a feeling I’d only get when the service was over, after even the church had cleared out."
    "只有在禮拜結束後、教堂空無一人時，我才會有那種感覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:473
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c82805fd:

    # "It would just be me and that altar, in that empty room."
    "空房間中獨留我和那個祭壇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:475
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8ae4e651:

    # "But it never felt empty."
    "但我從未感覺空蕩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:477
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_308c438a:

    # "There was always some sense of presence."
    "總覺得有什麼存在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:479
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ed0662f6:

    # "Something filling up the air that made that empty room feel not so empty."
    "空氣中充斥著什麼，讓空房間感覺並不空蕩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:481
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8b9b71da:

    # "And it ain't never felt bad."
    "從沒給人不好的感覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:483
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_944bb155:

    # "And it ain't never felt good."
    "也從沒給人好的感覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:485
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_98f64b5c:

    # "It just felt like somebody was looking at you, from every direction, through the light."
    "只是感覺有人從各個方向看著你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:487
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c88bb0c2:

    # "Through the shadows."
    "透過光線、透過陰影；"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:489
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a68e96e0:

    # "Places where solitude couldn’t exist."
    "來自孤獨無法存在的那些地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:491
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f38a1a88:

    # "When we come out of the hole, I can make out the shape of Blithe as she pulls us out."
    "我們從洞裡出來時，我看見Blithe的輪廓正把我們拉出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:492
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d98360d3:

    # bl "\"Don’t stand up, it’s not tall enough for even me.\""
    bl "別想站起來，這裡連我都站不直了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:493
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_15039acd:

    # "I hear Ralph grunting as his frame runs into me."
    "Ralph的身體撞到我，悶哼一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:494
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_75681268:

    # "The light of his torch illuminates the space."
    "他手電筒的光照亮了這個空間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:495
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0a6b9d2e:

    # "The girl’s right."
    "女孩說得對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:498
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a3afbad3:

    # "None of us could stand up if we tried."
    "我們沒人能站起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:499
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7e53eaae:

    # "The ceiling is domed, and the width of the room is wide, maybe twelve feet across by my estimation."
    "天花板是圓頂的，房間寬度很寬，我估計約莫十二呎。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:500
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4a12463f:

    # "It feels like we’re in the hive of some weird insect, but the walls were clearly built by men."
    "感覺像在某種奇怪昆蟲的巢穴裡，可牆壁又明顯是人類建造的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:502
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0c940ef4:

    # m "\"Damn.\""
    m "媽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:503
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_684b456b:

    # m "\"Did they just give up?\""
    m "他們就這麼放棄了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:504
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f843ae75:

    # ra "\"What are you talking about?\""
    ra "你在說什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:505
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_25604ae7:

    # m "\"I mean it seems like they put more care into the tunnels and then gave up and called it a day.\""
    m "我是說，他們好像在隧道上花了比較多心思，然後就直接收工不管了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:507
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a20736d9:

    # ji "\"No.\""
    ji "不對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:509
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e21c9bee:

    # ji "\"Whatever this is, it’s intentional.\""
    ji "不管這是什麼，都是有意而為。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:511
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0726ef02:

    # ji "\"Look at the walls.\""
    ji "看看牆壁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:513
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_339a80fd:

    # "They were stacked layers of stones, overlapping and spiraling upwards, like no walls I’ve ever seen before."
    "牆壁是以石層螺旋向上堆疊，我從來沒看見這種東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:514
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_89959d84:

    # "If I had to guess, it looks more like something you’d see in a castle than in the middle of the desert."
    "要我來猜的話，感覺更像會在城堡裡看到的景象，而不是在沙漠中央。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:516
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e4900d1b:

    # m "\"Who the hell would go through this much trouble to build a ceiling this short?\""
    m "到底是誰會這麼大費周章蓋這麼矮的天花板？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:517
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9bbbc906:

    # mu "\"The buildings techniques here look like corbelling.\""
    mu "這裡的建築技術看起來像是疊澀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:518
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_296ba126:

    # mu "\"You’ve never heard of a souterrain have you?\""
    mu "你從沒聽過「souterrain」吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:519
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7fc635bc:

    # "I grunt at him."
    "我向他悶哼一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:520
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7cb54c5e:

    # bl "\"If I haven’t ever heard of it, he sure as hell hasn’t.\""
    bl "我都沒聽過了，他肯定也沒聽過。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:521
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_480d39c7:

    # m "\"The hell is that somethin’ I’d need to know anyways?\""
    m "我需要知道那什麼鬼東西嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:522
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_483de1ca:

    # mu "\"You see them show up in old forts in Eire.\""
    mu "在愛爾蘭的古堡就能看見。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:523
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4b0fc407:

    # mu "\"Grandma said people unfamiliar with them weren’t supposed to go into them, so people would seal them up with rocks when they found them.\""
    mu "奶奶說不熟悉它們的人就不該進去，所以人們在發現時會刻意用石頭封住。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:524
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_67eaf69f:

    # mu "\"She’d say shamans would use them to communicate with the otherworld, under the veil of perfect darkness.\""
    mu "說是薩滿會在完全黑暗的遮蔽下，靠它們與冥界溝通。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:525
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a4ee1203:

    # mu "\"But the books I looked into suggest they were also defensive structures, where people would hide in the ground when raiders on the surface were attacking.\""
    mu "但我查閱的書，表示它們也是防禦性建築，讓人民在遭人劫掠時躲進地底。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:526
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_906328f3:

    # mu "\"So we might want to be careful about the capstone.\""
    mu "所以我們對那塊頂石最好小心點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:527
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_91099e25:

    # m "\"...Why?\""
    m "……為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:528
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ebe8694c:

    # mu "\"Could be designed to make us fall in.\""
    mu "有可能被設計成會害人掉進去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:529
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c6beb1aa:

    # m "\"Then why even open it?\""
    m "那為什麼還要打開它？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:530
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_321bd34a:

    # "He pauses, like he’s thinking about it."
    "他停頓了一下，像是在思考。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:531
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_755a083b:

    # mu "\"Whoever built this...\""
    mu "依我看，建造這個的人……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:533
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9306367f:

    # mu "\"My guess is they don’t expect anybody to be poking around if they weren’t meant to be here.\""
    mu "怕是不期望有不速之客在這裡亂翻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:534
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bed3879c:

    # ra "\"Let’s each get a corner.\""
    ra "我們各抓一個角吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:535
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3a00f570:

    # ji "\"I’ve got the back left.\""
    ji "我抓左後方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:537
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_18713952:

    # "I move to the front and place my fingers under the capstone."
    "我移動到前方，把手指放在頂石底下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:538
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9bb27b3b:

    # ra "\"Lift on three.\""
    ra "數到三就抬。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:539
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f56d6f71:

    # "I spread my legs and crouch, hinging my knees."
    "我張開雙腿、彎曲膝蓋蹲下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:540
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d1700414:

    # "As Ralph begins the count-off I half suspect I’ll see something I shouldn’t, or hear a real loud noise that’ll make my footing slip."
    "Ralph開始倒數時，我有點懷疑自己會因為看到不該看的東西或聽見巨響而腳滑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:541
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cfa049b0:

    # "But it’s just real dark and quiet down here."
    "但這裡只是一片漆黑而寂靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:542
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dae06a6f:

    # ra "\"Two...\""
    ra "二……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:543
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2a2ea390:

    # ra "\"Three!\""
    ra "三！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:546
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5a904d70:

    # "I hear the bunch of us grunt as I shift the weight bearing down on my arms to my knees."
    "我把壓在手臂上的重量轉移到膝蓋，大伙發出悶哼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:547
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_237271b6:

    # ra "\"Twist it sideways! Slide it off!\""
    ra "轉向側邊！把它滑開！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:549
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c9a765b6:

    # "The capstone scrapes against the stone container it covers as we rotate it, pulling it off."
    "頂石在被我們轉動並拉開時，刮蹭著它所覆蓋的岩石容器。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:552
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c252ac38:

    # "It falls to the ground with a damp thud."
    "發出潮濕的悶響砸在地上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:553
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_24384ccb:

    # "The sealed air wafts up."
    "密閉的空氣飄散而上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:555
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_609ebbbf:

    # ra "\"It smells like ash.\""
    ra "聞起來像灰燼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:556
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f35855c3:

    # mu "\"Give me some light.\""
    mu "來點光線。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:557
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_02d7e9a7:

    # "Blithe hands Murdoch her flashlight."
    "Blithe把手電筒遞給Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:558
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1d1a9104:

    # "He holds it over the pit."
    "他照向坑裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:559
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bb00167f:

    # "What’s below doesn’t look like more than a few foot drop."
    "下面的高度落差看起來不過幾呎。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:560
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e660bbc4:

    # "Smooth black sand."
    "一片平滑的黑沙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:561
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c5981d6d:

    # "Poking through the sand, there are shards of white."
    "沙中冒著一些白色碎片。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:562
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_760b7417:

    # "Not a single soul among us then and there had a whole lot of doubts about what we’re looking at."
    "在場全員無一看不出那些是什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:563
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_238de74c:

    # ji "\"Somewhat elaborate for a tomb.\""
    ji "以墳墓而言有點太講究了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:564
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f8b38125:

    # "It’s Jim breaking the silence that brings us back to the present."
    Jim打破沉默，把我們拉回現實。""

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:565
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c0ee42f1:

    # "I don’t really know what to say."
    "我真的不知道該說些什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:566
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d7d21a9d:

    # "So I say the only thing I think I can."
    "於是便把唯一能想到的事脫口而出："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:567
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ac62df2d:

    # m "\"I’m sorry about your classmates, Blithe.\""
    m 我為你的同學感到遺憾，Blithe。""

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:568
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5cfa534a:

    # bl "\"No.\""
    bl "不對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:569
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f10803a9:

    # bl "\"This ain’t them.\""
    bl "這些不是他們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:570
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_101d0f6e:

    # "She sounds completely certain."
    "她語氣無比肯定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:571
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b0d82195:

    # "I don’t know why."
    "不知怎麼地……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:572
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3dd434cd:

    # "But I wish I had a little more of what she does from time to time."
    "我有時也希望自己能擁有她那樣的態度。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:573
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5ead028e:

    # "Even when I might be wrong."
    "哪怕可能是錯的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:574
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c04e9f45:

    # m "\"How do you know?\""
    m "你怎麼知道？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:575
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f830e75e:

    # bl "\"Melissa said Mary wasn’t burned.\""
    bl "Melissa說Mary沒被燒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:576
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_12b8db3f:

    # bl "\"They cut her up and threw her in the water.\""
    bl "是被分屍然後丟進水裡的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:577
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_abfb65b0:

    # bl "\"These are different.\""
    bl "跟這些不一樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:578
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1b451e7c:

    # "She’s right."
    "她說得對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:579
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bfa12f5f:

    # "These are burned and tucked away."
    "這些是被燒過才藏起來的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:580
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e137a085:

    # "Where they were placed was marked with that carving."
    "被放置的地方有那個雕刻作為標記。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:581
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_99910d47:

    # "It feels more like an offering than a disposal."
    "感覺更像是獻祭而非丟棄。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:582
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6da54844:

    # "What an ugly thought."
    "我這想法真令人作嘔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:583
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_774d866e:

    # ra "\"So who are they, then?\""
    ra "那這些又是誰？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:585
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_45730a7c:

    # bl "\"I don’t really know.\""
    bl "這我就不知道了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:587
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_57fe750b:

    # bl "\"I think we all know who does though.\""
    bl "但要說誰知道，我想大家都心知肚明吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:589
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0f06ca6c:

    # "Everybody eyes Murdoch."
    "大家都看向Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:590
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a62cbbca:

    # "It seems like he arrived at the same thought before any of us did."
    "看來，他的思考比其他人要快一步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:591
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_63c8b4e2:

    # "He’s looking to the exit tunnel of the chamber."
    "他正望向房間的隧道出口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:597
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aa077936:

    # "One by one, we climb out from the hatch, and back to the room."
    "我們一個接一個從活板門爬出，回到房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:600
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_497604da:

    # "Dahlia waits for us standing in a corner."
    "Dahlia正站在角落等著我們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:601
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8b59ca75:

    # "She’s staring down one of the beds in the room, making a point not to sit on it."
    "她盯著房間裡的一張床，示意別坐上去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:603
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_906fb6a6:

    # "Blithe looks so sharply around the room her hat almost falls off."
    "Blithe猛然掃視房間，帽子差點掉下來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:605
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6702e8df:

    # "She speaks in a tone that’s more of an order than it is a question."
    "她開口的語氣更在下令而非提問："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:607
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d4719340:

    # bl "\"Where’s Melissa?\""
    bl "Melissa人呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:610
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bdc80c8d:

    # dh "\"Gone with Jim’s friends.\""
    dh "跟Jim的朋友一起走了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:613
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_befc65fd:

    # dh "\"They wanted to check the other rooms.\""
    dh "他們想去查看其他房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:616
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_740d844d:

    # m "\"Because you know they’ll find other carvings?\""
    m "妳知道他們會找到其他雕刻吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:617
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aff3e71a:

    # "Everybody stands just a little more still."
    "大家站得更加僵硬了些。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:618
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_119cc3b6:

    # m "\"Right?\""
    m "沒錯吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:620
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ddba2c8e:

    # "The small fox adjusts her glasses."
    "小狐狸調整了一下她的眼鏡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:621
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2c80461f:

    # "Slowly, she nods."
    "緩緩點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:623
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aa1bd80c:

    # "For a figure so short, her shadow seems long."
    "她身形如此矮小，影子卻顯得很長。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:625
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b3e12f8d:

    # dh "\"I suspect they will...\""
    dh "我估計他們會的……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:628
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_48b79696:

    # dh "\"Won’t they?\""
    dh "你說是吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:631
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_99b43d95:

    # mu "\"Dahlia.\""
    mu "Dahlia。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:632
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_24ae2104:

    # "Murdoch’s voice is somewhat shaky."
    "Murdoch的聲音有些發顫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:633
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8a6675a3:

    # "But it’s sober and sharp."
    "但清醒而銳利。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:634
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ae61d557:

    # "He sounds tired."
    "語氣疲憊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:636
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e2605629:

    # mu "\"We’re well past the point of surrepetition here.\""
    mu "該拐彎抹角的時期早就過了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:638
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1305eb75:

    # mu "\"Be frank with us now.\""
    mu "現在就打開天窗說亮話吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:640
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d83ba17e:

    # "She frowns."
    "她皺起眉頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:642
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_37cf6b28:

    # dh "\"Alright.\""
    dh "那好吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:645
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ff50f44b:

    # dh "\"This ought to be enough witnesses, anyway.\""
    dh "反正現在目擊者也夠多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:647
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7944d5bb:

    # "Murdoch pauses."
    "Murdoch停頓了一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:649
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0b48b13e:

    # "Then he finds his voice again."
    "然後再次開口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:651
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_180d7180:

    # mu "\"Did mother or father have anything to do with those bones?\""
    mu "母親或父親跟那些骨頭有關嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:653
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4c54c2e7:

    # dh "\"That’s not the question you should be--\""
    dh "現在的問題不在——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:658
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e286f423:

    # "His fist hits the door."
    "他一拳砸在門上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:660
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_72860162:

    # mu "\"What did I just SAY?\""
    mu "我剛剛{b}問的是{/b}什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:663
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b1a48976:

    # dh "\"Murdoch. {i}No.{/i}\""
    dh "{i}沒有{/i}，Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:665
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dfc5563f:

    # "She’s just as severe as he is now."
    "她現在跟他一樣嚴肅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:667
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a22e1263:

    # dh "\"You’re smart enough to process what the evidence suggests.\""
    dh "你夠精明，能理解證據所暗示的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:670
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b29d1247:

    # dh "\"These bones were here {i}before{/i} our family came to this town.\""
    dh "但這些骨頭早在我們家族來到這個鎮上{i}之前{/i}就存在了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:672
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_44030b58:

    # "Murdoch looks at her like she had just hit him square between the eyes with a frying pan."
    "Murdoch的表情像是臉被她用平底鍋砸了個正著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:674
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3d72207d:

    # mu "\"Then why hide it?\""
    mu "那這有什麼好隱瞞的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:677
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c1fc4efa:

    # dh "\"You know why.\""
    dh "你知道為什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:680
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a581fba0:

    # dh "\"This town needs secrets.\""
    dh "這個小鎮需要秘密。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:683
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bf480315:

    # dh "\"This town doesn’t {i}work{/i} without {i}secrets{/i}.\""
    dh "沒有{i}秘密{/i}，這個小鎮就無法{i}運作{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:691
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cfd28927:

    # "Blithe topples one of the wooden desks."
    "Blithe翻倒一張木桌。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:693
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_13abdf48:

    # "It cracks on the floor, tumbling loudly."
    "砸在地上裂開，發出巨大聲響。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:696
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8f1a9dba:

    # bl "\"So she knew about it then!\""
    bl "所以她早就知道了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:699
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_92754ef9:

    # "She kicks it again."
    "她又踢了它一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:702
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e0b17d01:

    # bl "\"She fucking.\""
    bl "她，他媽的"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:705
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c8485294:

    # bl "\"KNEW.\""
    bl "{b}早就知道{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:709
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0d7b2695:

    # bl "\"ABOUT IT!\""
    bl "{b}這件事了！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:713
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_89330176:

    # dh "\"Yes.\""
    dh "是的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:718
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b5ee74b0:

    # "She picks it up and slams it again."
    "她撿起來又砸了一次。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:722
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_24e04bba:

    # "Ralph wears a very bitter look on his face."
    "Ralph表情十分苦澀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:724
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8901bced:

    # ra "\"It’s how she kept Hendricks from running the school, wasn’t it?\""
    ra "她就是以此阻止Hendricks掌管學校的，沒錯吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:725
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eeac67b0:

    # "Dahlia’s scowl tightens."
    "Dahlia臉上的怒意更加緊繃。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:727
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_56098ad3:

    # dh "\"I’m certain.\""
    dh "我很確定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:730
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_89330176_1:

    # dh "\"Yes.\""
    dh "沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:733
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_909588c7:

    # dh "\"All of the evidence of what his grandfather did.\""
    dh "他祖父所作所為的所有證據。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:736
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b7674e83:

    # dh "\"It’s all down here.\""
    dh "全都在這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:740
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_003f5cac:

    # mu "\"You’ve been telling me about bodies for months.\""
    mu "妳這幾個月來，一直在告訴我關於屍體的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:742
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e742ba1d:

    # mu "\"When did you find out?\""
    mu "妳是什麼時候發現的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:746
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_59796829:

    # dh "\"The spring.\""
    dh "春天。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:748
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4fff13ab:

    # m "\"Why not tell anybody directly?\""
    m "為什麼不直接告訴別人？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:749
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b0d4da12:

    # "She doesn’t talk for a while."
    "她沉默了一陣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:751
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_de1e7b93:

    # m "\"Well?\""
    m "妳說啊？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:753
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_125913f4:

    # dh "\"Because if the wrong people find out, the truth doesn’t come out.\""
    dh "要是被錯誤的人發現，真相就會被埋沒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:756
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f9aa7890:

    # dh "\"I found out by accident.\""
    dh "我是意外發現的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:759
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7bb204ae:

    # dh "\"I was hoping others might do the same.\""
    dh "我希望其他人也能這樣發現。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:762
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6752392f:

    # dh "\"The right kind of people.\""
    dh "對的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:765
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d6febbf2:

    # dh "\"No ties to the town.\""
    dh "跟小鎮沒有牽連的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:768
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1b02d8a9:

    # dh "\"The lifeblood of it all.\""
    dh "這一切的命脈。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:771
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_563c3f08:

    # dh "\"There are belongings down here that I’ve never seen because I haven’t looked.\""
    dh "這裡有些東西我從沒看過，因為我沒有去查看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:774
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9b10c483:

    # dh "\"But now that you know there’s burnt remains...\""
    dh "但現在你們已經知道，這裡有燒焦的遺骸……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:777
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_92ee3212:

    # dh "\"Shouldn’t it be concerning that people know about it but it hasn’t been brought to the sheriff?\""
    dh "難道不會擔憂，有人對警方知情不報嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:780
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cc0ad2b3:

    # dh "\"Somebody else knows about this place and uses it regularly.\""
    dh "有人知道而且還持續利用這個地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:783
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_79a8395e:

    # dh "\"I’ve been checking it regularly.\""
    dh "我都會定期查看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:786
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_52e74c17:

    # mu "\"So who else?\""
    mu "那還有誰？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:789
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_919cfeda:

    # dh "\"At the very least mother or father, right?\""
    dh "至少母親或父親之一，對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:794
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ea4e7d22:

    # dh "\"But you and I both work at the school.\""
    dh "但你我都在學校工作。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:797
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_501b16ef:

    # dh "\"We could be implicated in something we aren’t involved in if the wrong person was told, or we didn’t have enough witnesses.\""
    dh "如果透露給錯誤的人或是證人不足，我們可能會被牽扯進與我們無關的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:800
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1f5f8a30:

    # "Murdoch gives her a hesitant look."
    "Murdoch遲疑地望著她。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:801
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f769d633:

    # "I don’t think she’s lying."
    "我不認為她在說謊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:802
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_caa0eec4:

    # "But I get the sense she’s still not sayin’ everything."
    "但感覺她還是沒全盤托出。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:803
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5eb58777:

    # "Maybe she doesn’t want to incriminate herself."
    "也許是不想受到牽連。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:804
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_63c9c64e:

    # "Maybe she’s just still scared the wrong person will find out."
    "也許只是還在害怕會被錯誤的人發現。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:805
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eb0a562c:

    # "I have to wonder if a disaster of this caliber is the best thing that could have ever happened to Dahlia Byrnes."
    "我不禁好奇，對Dahlia Byrnes來說，現在這種級別的災難是否是她最大的僥倖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:806
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fabdfd06:

    # "I don’t really know for sure."
    "我真的說不準。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:807
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dbfc101f:

    # "Maybe I never will."
    "或許我永遠不會知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:815
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8ad14e03:

    # "Outside in the hall, we hear a scream."
    "外頭走廊傳來一聲尖叫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:821
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7298ede4:

    # "It sounds like Melissa."
    "聽起來像是Melissa。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:825
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e04e8946:

    # "Blithe is the first person out the door."
    "Blithe第一個衝出門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:827
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5a71f01f:

    # "I’m the second one out."
    "我是第二個。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:829
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8872a831:

    # reu "\"What the hell do you think you’re--\""
    reu "你他媽是在——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:833
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f39f35a9:

    # "There’s a thud, and then a cry." with vpunch
    "悶響與哭喊接連傳來。" with vpunch

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:835
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9776a62b:

    # "I hear his voice coming from the door on the opposite side of the chamber from us."
    "他的聲音是從房間另一頭的門發出的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:842
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_df66415e:

    # "Neil turns on his slide, taking out a gun and {nw}"
    "Neil轉身掏槍，{nw}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:843
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_80b87144:

    # extend "slamming the side of the door with his side." with hpunch
    extend "用身側撞開門" with hpunch

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:845
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9e54185c:

    # nei "\"Get away from them now or I shoot!\""
    nei "立刻離開他們，不然我就開槍！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:847
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7dbd4e04:

    # haunk "\"Stop right there!\""
    haunk "別動！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:849
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8ff22be6:

    # haunk "\"Your man charged me first!\""
    haunk "是你們先襲擊我的！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:850
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_21f6e1a5:

    # "I know that voice."
    "我認得那個聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:851
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e9bb441f:

    # haunk "\"I yield!\""
    haunk "我投降！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:852
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_537657da:

    # bl "\"How the FUCK did this happen?\""
    bl "這他媽到底怎麼回事？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:854
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_258c8638:

    # "Neil still stands to the side of the doorway, holding a gun forward."
    "Neil依然站在門邊，持槍對準前方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:857
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2f6356d3:

    # "A much larger rabbit stoops over the figure of a smaller one."
    "一隻體型大得多的兔子彎身俯視著較小的兔子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:859
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cf79bfbd:

    # "His hands are bloodied."
    "雙手染血。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:861
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3da20631:

    # "So is the steel trap, clamped around Melissa’s foot."
    "夾住了Melissa腿的鋼夾也是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:863
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_986201d1:

    # "Reubin is lying on the floor."
    "Reubin倒在地板上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:864
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_059a51e5:

    # "He has a dark bruise on his forehead."
    "額頭上有明顯的瘀青。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:866
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a71020e5:

    # "He doesn’t look like he’s moving."
    "好像沒有了動靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:868
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_130adc7d:

    # ha "\"She ran in while I was asleep and stepped on a trap.\""
    ha "她趁我睡著時跑進來，踩到了陷阱。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:870
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b7cad54d:

    # m "\"Harlan?\""
    m "Harlan？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:872
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f6f2abd6:

    # "The man pauses before he answers."
    "那男人停頓了一下才回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:874
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_06132e13:

    # ha "\"...Sam.\""
    ha "……Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:876
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cc95ae84:

    # "I’m suddenly very glad Cynthia isn’t here right now."
    "我突然很慶幸Cynthia現在人不在這。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:884
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b4f99538:

    # bl "\"What did you do?!\""
    bl "你做了什麼！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:886
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c155047b:

    # "Blithe wildly gestures as she speaks."
    "Blithe抓狂地說道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:888
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6169cf0e:

    # ha "\"I was getting the trap off of her before the gentleman in the tuxedo put his hands around my neck, and I clocked him with the end of my shotgun!\""
    ha "我還沒來得及幫她取下陷阱，那個穿禮服的先生就掐住了我的脖子，我只好用霰彈槍槍托敲他！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:891
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_33c208e5:

    # bl "\"I {i}mean{/i} WHY is she ASLEEP?!?\""
    bl "我是{i}在問{/i} 她{b}為什麼不省人事{/b}！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:894
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_67963fc3:

    # bl "\"She’s not the type to pass out from pain!\""
    bl "她可不是會被痛暈的人！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:896
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9d8ae5e5:

    # ha "\"I always carry medicine on me!\""
    ha "我身上一直都帶著藥！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:899
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f0251c43:

    # ha "\"I put her out so she wouldn’t struggle with the trap!\""
    ha "讓她睡去，就不會在我解開陷阱時亂動了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:902
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_42e33c40:

    # ha "\"She could still hurt herself if I don’t disarm it!\""
    ha "要是我沒解開，她可能會受更多傷！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:905
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2ab59c22:

    # "Blithe pulls out her own pistol, becoming the second person to aim it at this man."
    "Blithe拔出自己的手槍，成為第二個用槍指著這男人的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:907
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ba5f5d5a:

    # "Neil takes his eyes off the old hare."
    "Neil把視線從老兔子身上移開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:909
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2b718d17:

    # "He doesn’t look like he expected her to have one too."
    "看來他沒料到她也有槍。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:912
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fd269f29:

    # bl "\"Then {i}do{/i} it!\""
    bl "那就{i}快點{/i}！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:915
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_58a94988:

    # bl "\"TAKE IT OFF!\""
    bl "{b}解開！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:918
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8cd47c18:

    # "Harlan lowers his hands slowly."
    "Harlan緩緩放下手。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:921
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1f97133d:

    # "He puts his bloodied hands on the trap, pressing something inside as he does."
    "把沾血的雙手放在陷阱上，按下裡面的什麼東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:923
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_721b5fce:

    # "Blood squelches out of her leg as he unclamps the trap, slowly."
    "隨著他緩緩鬆開陷阱時，鮮血從她腿上湧出。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:926
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_71bcf0b2:

    # "He pulls it brusquely off of her leg, twisting slightly, bits of her skin flayed as he drags the metal device off of her like he would a stocking."
    "他稍微扭轉，一把將金屬裝置從她腿上扯下來，像在拉開絲襪一樣，她的些許皮膚也隨之剝落。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:927
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_960b50d9:

    # ha "\"It’s off.\""
    ha "好了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:931
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2a346d3b:

    # ha "\"She’s going to need medical assistance.\""
    ha "她會需要醫療照護。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:933
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b30de8a5:

    # m "\"You took out the medical assistance.\""
    m "醫療照護已經被你幹掉了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:934
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2a4572bb:

    # "I jerk my head to the crumpled form on the ground."
    "我扭頭朝倒在地上的身影示意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:935
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ba8349ac:

    # "I’m not sure if I’m imagining it, but Harlan looks a little relieved."
    "我不確定是否看錯了，但Harlan似乎稍微鬆了口氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:937
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_751be44a:

    # ha "\"Unlucky.\""
    ha "真不湊巧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:940
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9d96ed1e:

    # nei "\"He’s still breathing.\""
    nei "他還有呼吸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:943
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_82bc0c92:

    # nei "\"Lucky for you, hare.\""
    nei "算你走運，兔子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:947
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_37dedaa6:

    # ha "\"I have a name, you know.\""
    ha "我有名有姓的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:948
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f4f3393e:

    # "He looks at me, nodding."
    "他朝向我點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:950
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a4df599d:

    # ha "\"He said it, after all.\""
    ha "畢竟他剛才喊過了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:954
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_45a8dc49:

    # "Neil looks to me as if asking for clarification."
    "Neil看向我，尋求說明。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:955
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_935eaa7c:

    # m "\"He’s the bartender at the Hip.\""
    m "他是Hip酒館的酒保。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:957
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d258310d:

    # m "\"Or, at least he used to be.\""
    m "或者至少原先是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:960
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c0a310e3:

    # ha "\"What, is there some trouble at the Hip?\""
    ha "怎麼，Hip酒館出什麼事了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:963
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cb497e7c:

    # m "\"It’s burning to the ground, Harlan.\""
    m "快要被燒毀了，Harlan。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:963
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f4a2f29f:

    # "He swallows his spit, his eyes still on the gun barrels pointed at him."
    "他吞了口口水，眼睛仍盯著指向他的槍管。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:964
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_92c48ca9:

    # m "\"It’s all gone.\""
    m "全沒了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:966
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9358ee91:

    # "He looks up and a glint of light shines off the lens of his glasses."
    "他抬起頭，眼鏡鏡片反射出一道光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:968
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_702a30f4:

    # ha "\"Now that just can’t be true, can it?\""
    ha "你說的不是真的吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:971
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0beeb817:

    # m "\"I said it’s all burning to the ground, Harlan.\""
    m "我跟你說了，就快被燒毀了，Harlan。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:972
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e5f4dd6d:

    # ha "\"Well, the whole city is burning now, isn’t it?\""
    ha "唉，現在整座城市都燒起來了，不是嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:975
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a3c054f3:

    # ha "\"Seems like we’re not the only ones in for a struggle, are we?\""
    ha "看來苦苦掙扎的不只有我們吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:977
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_432ffdff:

    # m "\"Harlan.\""
    m "Harlan。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:978
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e866b904:

    # "I’m pretty sure he’s lying."
    "我很確定他在撒謊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:980
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c6053cb1:

    # "I just can’t tell if he knows I think that."
    "只是不清楚他是否知道我的想法。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:993
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c6e43c1f:

    # ji "\"What’s going on over there?\""
    ji "你們那邊怎麼了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:995
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_74e11e5d:

    # mu "\"We heard screaming.\""
    mu "我們聽見了尖叫聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:997
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9d9743ac:

    # "Murdoch sees all of the blood and then covers his mouth."
    "Murdoch看到一堆鮮血後捂住了嘴。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:999
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f7e55c7a:

    # mu "\"Oh Jesus.\""
    mu "噢，天啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1001
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ca1c6930:

    # bl "\"We need to get her leg wrapped NOW.\""
    bl "我們要包紮她的腿，{b}趕快{/b}！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1006
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3b438cfc:

    # ra "\"I’ve dressed wounds before.\""
    ra "我包紮過傷口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1008
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9b07415e:

    # ra "\"Try not to move her before we wrap it.\""
    ra "包紮之前盡量別移動她。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1010
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_52cc7ddb:

    # ra "\"We need to find sanitizer.\""
    ra "要先找消毒用品。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1015
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0a2565dc:

    # ha "\"There’s chemicals in the front in the cabinets.\""
    ha "前面的櫃子裡有化學藥物。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1017
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3da3d777:

    # m "\"Are you sure?\""
    m "你確定？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1019
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_005fa2e5:

    # ha "\"Positve.\""
    ha "對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1021
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_10b4f986:

    # "There’s another silence."
    "又一陣沉默。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1023
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8070d76f:

    # ha "\"Don’t look at me like that.\""
    ha "別用那種眼神看我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1026
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9114d61f:

    # ha "\"I’ve had hours to raid this place, and I know what rubbing alcohol looks and smells like when I find it.\""
    ha "我已經在這裡搜刮好幾個小時了，又不是不認得醫用酒精的樣子和氣味。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1029
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_74198eb1:

    # ha "\"They’re in the cabinets near the shelf up front.\""
    ha "就在前面架子旁的櫃子裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1032
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_99d37046:

    # bl "\"Which cabinets!?\""
    bl "哪個櫃子！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1035
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bd22f39c:

    # ha "\"They’re painted green and they have glass panels.\""
    ha "有玻璃面板的綠色櫃子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1037
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e6af73a1:

    # ha "\"They look like soda shop cabinets.\""
    ha "像汽水店裡的櫃子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1040
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_432ffdff_1:

    # m "\"Harlan.\""
    m "Harlan。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1041
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5b693ac2:

    # "The hare looks frustrated with me."
    "兔子好像對我很不爽。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1043
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8bad2544:

    # ha "\"{i}What,{/i} Sam?\""
    ha "幹嘛，Sam？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1046
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cfc822a8:

    # m "\"I think you should talk about how you know where this place is.\""
    m "我想你該解釋一下，你怎麼知道這個地方的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1047
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_40f925d9:

    # ha "\"Why?\""
    ha "為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1049
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dd0a1d47:

    # "Is he playing dumb?"
    "他是在裝傻嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1050
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ff8dc426:

    # "He must be playing dumb."
    "絕對是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1055
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f7cc2881:

    # mu "\"Don’t you understand what this looks like?\""
    mu "……你難道不清楚你現在的處境嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1056
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5de8ec86:

    # ha "\"Of {i}course{/i} I--\""
    ha "我{i}當然{/i}——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1058
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_03e8da50:

    # "He clears his throat."
    "他清了清嗓子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1060
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0de74c6c:

    # ha "\"Alright.\""
    ha "好吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1063
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4b2ba6c4:

    # ha "\"Just listen.\""
    ha "先聽我說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1066
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bee98217:

    # ha "\"I found my way here from an annex of tunnels starting near the train station.\""
    ha "我是沿著火車站附近的一條隧道支線來到這的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1068
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cbd555cc:

    # m "\"The trains are out of service right now.\""
    m "火車現在停駛了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1070
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_34d98bbc:

    # ji "\"Yes, we already tried--\""
    ji "對，我們已經試過——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1074
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2d291b62:

    # ha "\"Hence why I’m {i}here.{/i}\""
    ha "所以我才會在{i}這裡{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1076
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_76bd288d:

    # "His voice is an angry hiss."
    "他語帶威憤。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1078
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_87ea6e2e:

    # ha "\"I followed the voices and found my way here.\""
    ha "我是跟著聲音來到這裡的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1080
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9f595066:

    # m "\"...the voices?\""
    m "……聲音？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1082
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0c0ed958:

    # ha "\"These tunnels echo.\""
    ha "這些隧道會產生回音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1085
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a1f7cdfc:

    # ha "\"They named it that for a reason.\""
    ha "正如其名。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1088
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4e087ab3:

    # m "\"Don’t you mean the canyon?\""
    m "你指的難道不是峽谷嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1089
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_893a56bf:

    # ha "\"That’s not the true source.\""
    ha "那不是真正的源頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1091
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2eed0d2a:

    # m "\"But--\""
    m "可是——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1094
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dd7d9844:

    # ra "\"Ask him later, Sam.\""
    ra "晚點再問吧，Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1094
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_335f11da:

    # ra "\"Right now I need you clear some space so I can deal with her leg, that girl is still bleeding.\""
    ra "現在先幫我清出空間，好讓我處理那女孩的腿，血還在流呢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1096
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d618dd90:

    # ra "\"Get me some rope.\""
    ra "也找條繩子來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1098
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a6c65754:

    # m "\"...alright.\""
    m "……好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1100
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b152a948:

    # ji "\"She should never have been down here.\""
    ji "她根本不該下來這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1107
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9bc4d1dc:

    # bl "\"Says who!?\""
    bl "誰說的！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1110
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ffed42c1:

    # bl "\"She’s been down here making it a hell of a lot longer than either of you.\""
    bl "她早就在這待得比你們所有人都久了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1113
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7fb33540:

    # ra "\"I SAID I NEED ROPE!\""
    ra "{b}我叫你們找繩子來！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1116
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cac64004:

    # "I take off my cumberbund."
    "我解下腰帶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1117
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c786b110:

    # m "\"These are adjustable.\""
    m "這個可以調整。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1122
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_197f110b:

    # "He presses the dark cloth to Melissa’s leg, wrapping it a good several times before tightening the ribbon through the strap of the loop."
    "他把深色布料壓在Melissa腿上，繞了幾圈，然後把帶子穿過環扣拉緊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1124
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4956fd2c:

    # m "\"Will it be tight enough?\""
    m "這樣夠緊嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1126
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5d86190f:

    # "Ralph wipes his brow, hands bloodied and eyes red from all of the smoke."
    "Ralph擦了擦額頭，滿手是血，雙眼因濃煙而發紅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1128
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_655b8a3d:

    # ra "\"I really don’t know, but it sure is all we have right now, isn’t it?\""
    ra "我不太清楚，但現在能做的也就這麼多了吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1130
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e297391e:

    # mu "\"I can help move her to the bed.\""
    mu "我可以幫忙把她搬到床上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1135
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cec80a1c:

    # bl "\"Just don’t let anybody else be alone with them.\""
    bl "記得別讓任何人和他們獨處。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1138
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_13d74767:

    # bl "\"Especially him.\""
    bl "尤其是他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1140
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f0b6d2c1:

    # "She points at Harlan."
    "她指向Harlan。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1142
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9a0d1934:

    # bl "\"Get him {i}out{/i} of here.\""
    bl "把他帶{i}出去{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1147
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6870b0a7:

    # "Blithe and Dahlia elect to stay in the room watching over Melissa and Reubin while Jim, Neil, Ralph, Murdoch and myself are left with Harlan."
    "Blithe和Dahlia決定留在房間照看Melissa和Reubin；Jim、Neil、Ralph、Murdoch和我則跟Harlan在一起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1149
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2a764bfd:

    # "I know something is wrong, and can’t help but feel we’re already down two able-bodied people while things are getting worse around us."
    "我知道事態不對勁，又為少了兩個戰力而擔憂，周遭情況也是越來越惡劣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1151
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a38b2fbc:

    # "There’s still no way to make sense out of Harlan being here and there ain’t no way I’m the only one who feels the same."
    "Harlan出現在這裡還是毫無道理，而且這麼想的絕對不只我一個人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1152
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_09822ab6:

    # "Dahlia’s words about this place start to feel a hell of a lot more concerning."
    "Dahlia口中關於這個地方的故事，越來越讓人擔心了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1154
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5baac3ca:

    # "Who else has been here?"
    "還有誰來過這裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1156
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9f1d68b6:

    # "Apparently anybody can be, if Harlan of all people is here."
    "連Harlan也在這，那誰來過都不奇怪。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1157
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b05d4051:

    # "I hear Neil and Jim whispering to the hare but I can’t make out what they’re saying."
    "Neil和Jim在和兔子低語，但我聽不清內容。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1159
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_436855d5:

    # "But the old man just keeps shaking his head."
    "老人只是不停搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1162
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2f3896a2:

    # "Me and Murdoch wait by the door until Ralph comes out."
    "我和Murdoch在門口等到Ralph出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1164
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f6ba367f:

    # m "\"That girl okay?\""
    m "那女孩還好嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1166
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3ea2934f:

    # ra "\"I think she should be fine, but she’ll be out for hours.\""
    ra "應該沒有大礙，但會昏睡好幾個小時。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1168
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b12a4ec6:

    # "Ralphs eyes narrow in on Harlan, who’s flanked by Jim and Neil on the other side of the room."
    "Ralph瞇眼瞪向Harlan，對方正被Jim和Neil包夾著站在房間另一側。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1170
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_295fbbb6:

    # "He struts on over towards them, raising his voice."
    "他大步走向他們喊話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1172
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cd3eef82:

    # "Me and Murdoch follow his lead."
    "我和Murdoch跟了上去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1186
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6ff2d86a:

    # ra "\"Now what the hell was that guy doing down here, again?\""
    ra "這傢伙到底是來幹嘛的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1188
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_05d13ebd:

    # mu "\"We didn’t get to ask.\""
    mu "我們還沒機會問。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1191
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_beaf2d8e:

    # ha "\"A good point, my boy.\""
    ha "說得好，小子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1194
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1b5567e7:

    # ha "\"If you’d let me explain, you’d understand that this is a misunderstanding.\""
    ha "只要聽我解釋，你們就會明白這是個誤會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1196
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8f8cd91d:

    # m "\"Do we need to?\""
    m "有這個必要嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1198
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8e9bc419:

    # m "\"If he’s down here, he wasn’t up to any good.\""
    m "他會出現在這，肯定是有什麼企圖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1200
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_82547a76:

    # ji "\"So that was him running around in the basement then?\""
    ji "所以之前在地下室亂跑的就是他？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1203
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1b1ee654:

    # ha "\"I don’t know a {i}thing{/i} about any basement. I don’t even know where {i}here{/i} is.\""
    ha "我不知道什麼地下室。我連{i}這裡{/i} 是哪都不知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1205
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_902e53cc:

    # ra "\"Yet here you are.\""
    ra "但你人就在這。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1207
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1311676f:

    # ha "\"This is a tunnel that connects from the south end of the bank to the train tracks.\""
    ha "這是一條從銀行南端通往火車軌道的隧道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1210
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c1129655:

    # ha "\"It’s not a well-known trail, but I have worked with them in the past, and I’m certain that if they were here, they would back up my claim.\""
    ha "雖說不是什麼知名路徑，但我以前跟他們一起工作過。要是他們也在，一定會替我作證。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1214
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_af82c34a:

    # mu "\"You’re below the school.\""
    mu "這裡是學校底下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1217
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_23858675:

    # ha "\"What?\""
    ha "什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1219
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_36ccd868:

    # "I can’t tell if he’s genuinely surprised or not."
    "我看不出他是不是真的驚訝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1220
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3657569c:

    # "But he sure as hell sounds it."
    "但聽起來確實很驚訝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1221
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_98fb6633:

    # "Then again, I know Harlan had an acting career before he was a bartender."
    "不過，我也知道Harlan在當酒保之前有過演員生涯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1222
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ca8d2425:

    # mu "\"I’m telling you that you’re some ways away from the bank or the tunnels.\""
    mu "我告訴你，你離銀行或那些隧道有一大段距離。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1225
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_574d3131:

    # ha "\"Well, ah... hrm.\""
    ha "呃，這……嗯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1228
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_083e4126:

    # ha "\"I suppose that wouldn’t be impossible, now, would it?\""
    ha "這也不算那麼不合理吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1231
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_54f01a5f:

    # ha "\"In fact, I probably would have stayed on the correct course if I hadn’t heard the voices.\""
    ha "事實上，要不是聽見了那些聲音，我大概會走在正確的路上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1233
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eb679854:

    # m "\"Voices?\""
    m "聲音？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1235
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_82cabc85:

    # ha "\"{i}Yes.{/i}\""
    ha "{i}對。{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1238
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0c3c9ecb:

    # ha "\"Your voices.\""
    ha "你們的聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1241
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0dafe171:

    # ji "\"And you’re saying that’s how you found yourself down here.\""
    ji "你是在說，你就是這樣才跑到這裡來的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1245
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ba13e259:

    # ha "\"Well, yes.\""
    ha "嗯，對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1247
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0426b711:

    # ha "\"As you already know, all hell broke out on the surface.\""
    ha "你們也知道，地上已經亂成一團了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1250
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3d7b3f67:

    # ha "\"There’s looting and glass smashing.\""
    ha "建築東塌西倒，有人趁火打劫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1253
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e26b5fca:

    # ha "\"Stampedes of people crowding toward the train station, some running over each other waiting for the services to start again.\""
    ha "眾人朝火車站蜂擁而去，互相推擠踩踏，等著交通恢復。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1256
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_548c2c4e:

    # ha "\"I thought it would be best to wait it out, once the crowd has thinned.\""
    ha "我認為等人群散了再出去比較好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1259
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0d978bee:

    # m "\"Down here in the basement of the school?\""
    m "守在學校地下室？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1260
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_05e6a58c:

    # ha "\"I told you that I just wandered here.\""
    ha "就說了我只是碰巧來到這的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1264
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_26b5d865:

    # "Ralph nods."
    "Ralph點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1265
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ab80b2d8:

    # "Slowly."
    "緩緩地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1266
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eb3fe38d:

    # "All understanding-like."
    "表示出理解的樣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1267
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f4c308f8:

    # ra "\"Right.\""
    ra "行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1268
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e34d68e4:

    # ra "\"How’d you get in?\""
    ra "那你是怎麼進來的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1269
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_26c58c46:

    # "Harlan points to one of the doors in the chamber."
    "Harlan指向房間裡的一扇門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1272
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_97296e8a:

    # ha "\"That door to my south must be connected to the bank tunnel.\""
    ha "我南邊那扇門應該是連著銀行的隧道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1275
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6c87cbb7:

    # ha "\"In my haste, I must have picked a wrong door.\""
    ha "我一定是在慌忙之中走錯門了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1278
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b03d830a:

    # ha "\"Normally there’s a arrow painted on the outside of it.\""
    ha "通常外面有畫著一個箭頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1281
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_48e4382b:

    # ha "\"If I think about it for a while, the one I saw must have been blue instead of...\""
    ha "仔細一想，我看到的那個應該是藍色的，而不是……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1283
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ae263388:

    # mu "\"Instead of what?\""
    mu "而不是什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1285
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_75207d07:

    # "The hare shrugs a bit."
    "兔子微微聳肩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1288
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_deb18507:

    # ha "\"Well, instead of the color it normally is.\""
    ha "而不是平常的顏色。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1290
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_018d8b21:

    # "Harlan scratches the back of his head."
    "Harlan搔了搔後腦勺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1292
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_812e2971:

    # ha "\"Now that I think more on it...\""
    ha "話又說回來……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1295
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a6180302:

    # ha "\"...you all look finely dressed for the occasion.\""
    ha "……你們穿得都相當正式。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1298
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b9949daf:

    # ha "\"Nicer than most folks tend to dress around here anyway.\""
    ha "少說是比這裡大多數人的常服要好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1301
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3ad548e4:

    # ha "\"I take it some of you must be from out of town?\""
    ha "你們有些人應該是外地來的吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1304
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e59daef7:

    # ji "\"No, but I am one for travelling.\""
    ji "我不是，但我喜歡旅行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1308
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e6729152:

    # nei "\"I’m from out of town.\""
    nei "我是外地人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1312
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f789c745:

    # ha "\"Ah!\""
    ha "哦！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1315
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5a1f7fbb:

    # ha "\"There we are.\""
    ha "那就對了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1320
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_79a20ac3:

    # ha "\"If I’m not mistaken, that means you lot will almost certainly want the first train ticket out of here.\""
    ha "要是我沒猜錯，你們肯定想搭最早離開這裡的火車。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1323
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8a3e4e84:

    # ha "\"And at the earliest convenience.\""
    ha "越早越好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1329
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ffb04236:

    # ji "\"Yes, but we’re lying low.\""
    ji "對，但要先躲避風頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1330
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cad0915a:

    # "Harlan nods."
    "Harlan點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1332
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e9444839:

    # "His expression looks awfully thoughtful."
    "表情深思。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1335
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_62d341e0:

    # ha "\"Looking for the best opportunity to leave, then?\""
    ha "那就是在找絕佳的離開時機？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1338
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9ddb195e:

    # "Jim pinches the bridge of his snout."
    "Jim捏了捏鼻樑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1340
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_107537ec:

    # ji "\"Yes.\""
    ji "對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1343
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bceb7502:

    # ji "\"Quite.\""
    ji "沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1346
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5c68ff84:

    # "Harlan makes an open gesture with his arms."
    "Harlan張開雙臂示意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1348
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_95c27b6b:

    # ha "\"Okay!\""
    ha "那好！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1352
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eff83ea9:

    # ha "\"Perhaps we can help each other.\""
    ha "或許我們可以互相幫助。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1354
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_402fa237:

    # ha "\"You gents would be terribly exposed to walk that trip from the school in the middle of the day.\""
    ha "你們大白天從學校走出去會非常顯眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1357
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_65175cd7:

    # ha "\"Forgive me for my little scare here and I’ll show you the right way to the train tracks.\""
    ha "只要你們原諒我先前造成的驚動，我就帶你們走正確的路到火車軌道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1360
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bd478ecd:

    # ha "\"That seem fair?\""
    ha "這樣公平吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1365
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bfd002c9:

    # "Jim’s brow quirk and I see a flash in Neil’s eye."
    "Jim揚起眉毛，Neil也眼神一亮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1367
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b2fd7e9c:

    # "They seem interested."
    "貌似頗感興趣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1370
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6c543501:

    # "I need to say what I’m going to say next awfully careful-like."
    "我得謹慎思考接下來要說的話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1371
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1c4d73df:

    # m "\"Seems more than fair for somebody who doesn’t have a whole lot to gain, don’t it.\""
    m "你又得不到什麼好處，這都不只是一句公平能概括了吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1375
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_07469a61:

    # "Jim shoots me a frown when I say that while Neil looks merely curious."
    "Jim一聽就對我皺眉，而Neil只露出了好奇的神情。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1377
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_94660eeb:

    # ha "\"All I ask is that nobody press charges for my scare.\""
    ha "我只是希望不會因為驚擾到別人而被告。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1379
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0443a01d:

    # m "\"But your scare took two people out within seconds.\""
    m "你所謂的驚擾，可是在幾秒內就幹掉兩個人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1381
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7e095448:

    # "Harlan flinches."
    "Harlan略為退縮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1383
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d7ac166e:

    # "His mouth opens for a while, like he’s {nw}"
    "他像有話要說，{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1385
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_42e4ed52:

    # extend " about to say something."
    extend "嘴巴張了好一會兒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1386
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9173c158:

    # "Finally, he does."
    "最後，他答道："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1388
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_34b8d4e4:

    # ha "\"You aren’t usually this blunt with me, Sam.\""
    ha "你平常跟我可沒這麼直接啊，Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1390
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e1fbd28c:

    # m "\"We never did talk much.\""
    m "我們本來就沒怎麼說過話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1391
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4ee3c88d:

    # m "\"Part of my job was making sure I gave you no disrespect.\""
    m "對你以禮相待也是我工作的一環。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1393
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e3c28c9a:

    # ha "\"And that’s no longer the case?\""
    ha "現在不是了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1395
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_894a143b:

    # m "\"No Hip, no job, Mr. Perkins.\""
    m "Hip酒館沒了，我也就沒工作了，Perkins先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1398
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1a103f8a:

    # ha "\"Are you accusing me of something, Mr. Ayers?\""
    ha "你是在指控我什麼嗎，Ayers先生？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1399
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0fbfc0f2:

    # "I put my paws in my pocket."
    "我把爪插進口袋。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1401
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c651d0c8:

    # m "\"No.\""
    m "沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1403
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_630654bc:

    # m "\"Just pointing out the situation.\""
    m "只是點明現況。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1405
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4a135a17:

    # m "\"You’re much faster than I would expect for a man your age.\""
    m "你都這把年紀了，動作卻敏捷得出奇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1407
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d4cdd38e:

    # "Harlan looks at me."
    "Harlan望著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1409
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c970197e:

    # "It’s a serious look."
    "表情嚴峻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1410
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3c3fb83b:

    # "Kind of like the one he’d give me whenever I’d ask him to talk about himself on slower days."
    "我在因酒館生意清淡而找他聊些個人話題時，他就會露出這種表情。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1412
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_10736399:

    # ra "\"I can understand knocking somebody unconscious if you hit them in the head while you’re still surprised.\""
    ra "在受驚時不巧擊中對方頭部導致昏迷，是能理解。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1413
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_72fee96d:

    # ra "\"It’s an easy thing to do.\""
    ra "這很容易發生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1415
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0b68ff31:

    # ra "\"But where did the steel trap come from?\""
    ra "但那鋼夾又是哪來的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1417
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e9044258:

    # ha "\"That wasn’t mine.\""
    ha "那不是我的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1421
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7dd41323:

    # ha "\"They’re in all of the rooms.\""
    ha "每個房間都有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1422
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aa5c614b:

    # mu "\"All of the rooms?\""
    mu "所有房間？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1424
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fb0a4bfa:

    # ha "\"Yes...\""
    ha "對……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1426
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_64d03e71:

    # ra "\"Every one?\""
    ra "每個都有？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1428
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8f9cf66c:

    # ha "\"I’d bet my life on it.\""
    ha "要我拿性命擔保都行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1433
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cf3486ca:

    # "Murdoch and Ralph exchange a look before "
    "Murdoch和Ralph交換眼神後，{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1435
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d470246e:

    # extend "Murdoch looks at me."
    extend "Murdoch看向我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1437
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_218be32d:

    # ha "\"Take a look if you don’t believe me.\""
    ha "不信的話大可自己去看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1441
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aef0ebd9:

    # ra "\"No thanks.\""
    ra "不用了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1443
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d85e7098:

    # ra "\"I believe you.\""
    ra "我相信你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1446
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_401778af:

    # ha "\"It’s good that you do.\""
    ha "你相信就好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1449
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a068fa3f:

    # ha "\"There’s forces at work here that would prefer it otherwise.\""
    ha "這裡有些力量可不這麼希望。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1453
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3d1a62f8:

    # "Murdoch’s ears perk up."
    "Murdoch耳朵豎了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1454
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b69bf42c:

    # mu "\"When you say that...\""
    mu "你說這話……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1455
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7d3a8473:

    # mu "\"What do you mean?\""
    mu "是什麼意思？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1456
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3eea5f3a:

    # "The hare slowly nods his head."
    "兔子緩緩點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1458
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6337fab6:

    # ha "\"You’re religious, boy.\""
    ha "你很虔誠吧，孩子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1461
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_38292c14:

    # ha "\"You should have a pretty good idea what I mean.\""
    ha "你應該很清楚我的意思。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1464
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c88f2c27:

    # "Jim scowls and Neil retains his stony expression."
    "Jim皺起眉頭，Neil則保持一臉冷淡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1469
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_31f7ce44:

    # ra "\"I’m not religious.\""
    ra "我不是信徒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1471
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_801520a3:

    # ra "\"Walk me through it?\""
    ra "能跟我解釋一下嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1473
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c969e04f:

    # ha "\"No.\""
    ha "不行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1475
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_13f0ce49:

    # ha "\"Talking to somebody without faith about this sort of matter would fall on deaf ears.\""
    ha "跟沒有信仰的人談這種事，只會被當耳邊風。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1477
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fb738166:

    # m "\"Then talk to me.\""
    m "那就跟我說吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1478
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e9ca5e69:

    # "I stare him down."
    "我瞪著他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1479
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c1487ff1:

    # m "\"You know that I pray.\""
    m "你知道我會禱告。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1480
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2a8c067c:

    # m "\"You’ve seen me.\""
    m "你有看過。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1481
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_089bf4f5:

    # "Harlan goes quiet for a little while again."
    "Harlan又沉默了一陣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1483
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8679d3b5:

    # ha "\"You all see things that aren’t supposed to be there sometimes, don’t you?\""
    ha "你們有時會看見理應不存在的東西，對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1485
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_33100f17:

    # "I wonder if I should answer."
    "我猶豫著要不要回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1486
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2b41612a:

    # "Nobody else does."
    "其他人也沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1487
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8224070d:

    # "There were the pictures... then the voice."
    "是有那些照片……和那個聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1488
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aa8bf631:

    # "But I haven't heard it for some time now."
    "但我已經很久沒聽見了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1490
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aa2ecee1:

    # ha "\"Your face tell me that you already know.\""
    ha "你的表情告訴我你已經知道了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1493
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ff6265d1:

    # ha "\"Everybody in this town does, the longer they stay.\""
    ha "這個鎮上的人，待得越久就越清楚。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1495
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5f9023e2:

    # "If I ain’t hearing nothin’ no more, could whatever had happened to the town be over?"
    "如果我不再聽見，是不是代表鎮上發生的事已經結束了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1496
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8bdd5ca4:

    # "I don’t know."
    "我不知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1497
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8c3eb6d7:

    # "The fires aren’t likely extinguished yet, at least."
    "至少火應該還沒滅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1498
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cd0d235c:

    # "Harlan leans in."
    "Harlan湊近。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1500
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1c2dd94:

    # ha "\"I’ll tell you all sorts of people learn about the tunnels too.\""
    ha "我跟你說，各式各樣的人都知道這些隧道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1504
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e57d7f52:

    # ha "\"First you start to dream about them.\""
    ha "起初，會先夢見它們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1507
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dbbb94e9:

    # ha "\"Then you start to wake up in them.\""
    ha "然後發現自己在裡面醒來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1511
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e06822be:

    # ha "\"Am I right?\""
    ha "我說得對不對？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1513
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_23e9cad4:

    # "I half expect everybody to look at Harlan like he’s talkin’ crazy."
    "我以為大家都會覺得Harlan在說胡言亂語。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1514
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9c904628:

    # "But nobody is."
    "但沒人這麼想。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1515
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9770b503:

    # "He looks to Neil."
    "他看向Neil。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1517
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e7de225e:

    # ha "\"If even the newcomers have dreams, that’s how I know it’s bad.\""
    ha "如果連新來的人都會做夢，我就知道情況有多糟了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1522
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_26e5dd8c:

    # nei "\"Sorry, but I don’t know what you’re talking about.\""
    nei "抱歉，我不知道你在說什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1526
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_27ed4a80:

    # "The hare {nw}"
    "兔子{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1528
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_29bccd6d:

    # extend "blinks, surprised."
    extend "詫異地眨眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1530
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6c1a641b:

    # nei "\"I just feigned interest to see what you’d say.\""
    nei "我只是假裝有興趣，想看看你會說什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1533
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4ced9ace:

    # ha "\"Ah.\""
    ha "哦。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1536
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8c0d62ac:

    # nei "\"All you needed for support from me was your original promise.\""
    nei "你原本的承諾就足以得到我的支持了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1538
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cd56699d:

    # "Harlan nods enthusiastically, then he looks to Jim, then to Murdoch."
    "Harlan熱情地點頭，先後看向Jim和Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1540
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7bc559e8:

    # ha "\"This earth is the kingdom of none other than the Deceiver.\""
    ha "這片土地是屬於欺瞞者的國度。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1543
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fe66d4e8:

    # ha "\"The gates of the kingdom of heaven will only open to the worthy.\""
    ha "天國之門只會向應得的人敞開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1549
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_120a1e17:

    # mu "\"Do you think that you’re unworthy?\""
    mu "你認為自己不應得嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1550
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_150be21f:

    # "It’s an awfully pointed question, especially for Murdoch."
    "這問題異常刁鑽，尤其還是出自Murdoch之口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1554
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_15d90032:

    # ha "\"Well, I think we all deserve a chance at redemption.\""
    ha "我是認為，救贖的機會是我們都應得的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1557
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_713c8fac:

    # ha "\"I believe that that’s the reason we’re {i}here.{/i}\""
    ha "我相信這就是我們在這裡的緣由。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1559
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_54fc6b0f:

    # "Jim and Neil look unimpressed."
    "Jim和Neil興趣缺缺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1560
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_10136634:

    # "Ralph is harder to read."
    "Ralph比較難捉摸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1561
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_16d0c724:

    # "Murdoch looks fascinated."
    "Murdoch看起來很入迷。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1564
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d0a7f9f7:

    # ha "\"Say uh...\""
    ha "我說……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1567
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7ddd07ee:

    # ha "\"I think it’s pretty obvious that I’m not in the greatest health.\""
    ha "我的健康狀況顯然不是很好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1570
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_696abcbb:

    # ha "\"I get dizzy easy, and my heart flutters in this strange way when I’m anxious. I sweat too much.\""
    ha "我很容易頭暈，焦慮時心跳會出問題，還會流很多汗。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1573
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8d39cafd:

    # ha "\"Do any of you have something to drink?\""
    ha "你們有什麼能喝的嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1576
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4b89c634:

    # ha "\"Just like the rest of you, I’ve been running around this godforsaken town for hours.\""
    ha "我跟你們一樣，已經在這該死的鎮上徘徊了好幾個小時。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1579
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_54e101db:

    # ji "\"We had to rush.\""
    ji "我們剛才很匆忙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1581
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0010e58a:

    # ra "\"Because there hasn’t been any time.\""
    ra "因為時間緊迫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1583
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0b434bb2:

    # "Harlan groans."
    "Harlan懊惱呻吟。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1585
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f96993da:

    # ha "\"Surely there’s a spigot around here?\""
    ha "這裡總該有水龍頭吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1590
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d8ba1493:

    # mu "\"Water to the school is turned off in the summer.\""
    mu "學校供水在夏天是關閉的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1592
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4ced9ace_1:

    # ha "\"Ah.\""
    ha "喔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1595
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_483c0e96:

    # ha "\"In my old age, I do believe my memory is slipping.\""
    ha "上了年紀，我的記憶力確實在退化。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1597
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1f501f9a:

    # "The hare unhooks a strap around his neck, holding out a container."
    "兔子解開脖子上的帶子，拿出一個容器。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1600
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fd45900b:

    # ha "\"I believe that poor girl who snagged her foot on the trap was carrying some water.\""
    ha "那可憐的女孩踩到陷阱時，身上倒是帶著水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1601
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_924a7e96:

    # "I try to remember if she was carrying this canteen or not."
    "我試著回想她是否帶著這個水壺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1603
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_89180294:

    # m "\"Is that really Melissa’s canteen?\""
    m "那真的是Melissa的水壺嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1605
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_210d4485:

    # mu "\"It is.\""
    mu "的確是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1608
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1b68d667:

    # mu "\"I remember seeing her with it.\""
    mu "我記得有看到她帶著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1612
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_008b17d9:

    # ra "\"Me too.\""
    ra "我也記得。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1613
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ea9f2aa7:

    # ra "\"Plus, the pattern matches her clothes.\""
    ra "圖案也跟她的衣服很搭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1615
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_30f18b82:

    # ra "\"That’s definitely hers.\""
    ra "那絕對是她的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1617
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f4e5957c:

    # ha "\"Perhaps she wouldn’t mind us sipping just a bit?\""
    ha "她應該不會介意我們喝一點吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1620
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6120f0c6:

    # ha "\"She seems like a good soul.\""
    ha "她看著像是個好孩子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1622
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_150eb487:

    # "He holds up the canteen."
    "他舉起水壺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1623
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_544efb96:

    # "Ralph takes it first."
    "Ralph先接了過去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1625
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1fee495:

    # "He unscrews the cap, and sniffs."
    "擰開蓋子一嗅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1627
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7198714b:

    # ra "\"It smells like water.\""
    ra "聞著像是水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1629
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_af3c7dbf:

    # "The hare shrugs his wrists and the rat hands the container back to him."
    "兔子甩甩手腕，老鼠把容器還給他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1633
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c401ca56:

    # ji "\"Well, I wasn’t exactly expecting Miss Boike to be packing whiskey anyway.\""
    ji "我本來也沒指望Boike小姐會帶著威士忌。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1636
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_725c8bf9:

    # nei "\"Just hand the damn thing over.\""
    nei "把那東西給我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1639
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b06a5be9:

    # nei "\"This heat is giving me a migraine.\""
    nei "我頭都要被熱疼了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1643
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_61f883f8:

    # ha "\"Just a sip. We ought to conserve the supply.\""
    ha "只能喝一小口。現在得節約資源。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1645
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1b7a52d:

    # "But an idea comes to me."
    "我腦中卻浮現了一個想法。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1646
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5c02bad7:

    # "It’s an idea I think Murdoch would be proud of, but I can’t tell him about it right now."
    "這想法應該會讓Murdoch很佩服，但我現在不能告訴他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1648
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7a2e700f:

    # "One by one, we each take a swig."
    "我們輪流各自喝了一口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1649
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f277df2c:

    # "I let Harlan see the water go into my mouth."
    "我讓Harlan看到水進了我嘴裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1650
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_de5586a4:

    # "He doesn’t look at me for long."
    "他沒有盯著我太久。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1653
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_799df0ea:

    # mu "\"So.\""
    mu "好了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1654
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f3115df2:

    # mu "\"Now that we’ve come to a certain understanding, Mr...\""
    mu "既然現在我們算是達成共識了，這位……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1658
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3ee89cfb:

    # ha "\"Perkins.\""
    ha "Perkins。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1662
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f2999823:

    # mu "\"Mr. Perkins.\""
    mu "Perkins先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1665
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4d720897:

    # mu "\"Would you mind telling me how long you’ve been seeing things?\""
    mu "你介意告訴我，你看到那些東西已經多久了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1668
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0e4459ce:

    # ha "\"Since years ago.\""
    ha "好幾年了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1671
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a2f89f9b:

    # ha "\"I wasn’t being completely dishonest when I said they named the town Echo because of all the voices the early settlers heard from one another, due to resonance in the the caverns.\""
    ha "我先前說到，這個小鎮之所以被命名為回音，是因為早期移民因洞穴共振而聽見彼此的聲音，不完全是個謊言。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1674
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f4338573:

    # ha "\"But of course, half truths occlude the reality of things, sometimes worse than lies can.\""
    ha "只是想當然，真假參半的話有時比謊言更能掩蓋真相。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1677
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_36f21115:

    # ha "\"People in this town talk about repeating events that haven’t happened yet.\""
    ha "這個鎮上的人會談論尚未發生卻重複上演的事件。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1680
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5959893c:

    # ha "\"Usually quite terrible things.\""
    ha "通常是大災厄。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1683
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d6d2934f:

    # ha "\"Or slightly different versions of terrible things that have happened.\""
    ha "或是跟過去的慘劇大同小異的事件。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1686
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5eebc7c0:

    # "Neil makes an awful noise."
    "Neil嘔了一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1688
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_26f33905:

    # "I half expect to see some evidence of pain or sickness."
    "我還以為他吃痛或身體不適。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1690
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_401d71a9:

    # "But instead, he looks annoyed."
    "只見他一副不耐煩的樣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1692
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dad62cc6:

    # ha "\"I see we’ve grown bored of theology, so now we’re onto parapsychology.\""
    ha "已經懶得談神學，轉向超心理學了是吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1695
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_90354bb5:

    # ha "\"Did I say something to offend you, sir?\""
    ha "我有哪裡冒犯到你了嗎，先生？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1698
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_250e9d06:

    # nei "\"The whole subject is offensive.\""
    nei "整個話題都很冒犯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1701
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fca7533f:

    # ha "\"Now there’s a familiar sentiment.\""
    ha "這下我懂了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1704
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_32dcf4e6:

    # ha "\"I suppose you don’t believe in the world beyond?\""
    ha "你應該不相信冥界存在吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1707
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_03947809:

    # ha "\"You fancy yourself a man of modernity?\""
    ha "你自認為是現代人？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1710
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_939b405f:

    # "Neil lets out what sounds to me like a long-suffering sigh."
    "Neil發出忍耐許久後的嘆息。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1712
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_85177a75:

    # nei "\"Trust me, I respect the showmanship.\""
    nei "我還是挺尊重你的表演的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1715
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c792d0aa:

    # nei "\"I really do.\""
    nei "真的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1718
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_15aac7fa:

    # nei "\"But I’ve run afoul of more fortune tellers and magicians than I would care for in politics.\""
    nei "但我在政治圈已經碰過夠多算命師和魔術師了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1721
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_91e9a64b:

    # ha "\"You sound like you don’t have much respect for my line of thinking.\""
    ha "你的說法倒是不太尊重我的思考方式啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1724
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3e3be70d:

    # "Neil scoffs gently."
    "Neil輕輕嗤笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1726
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f6876620:

    # nei "\"Sir.\""
    nei "先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1729
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c6dd73f1:

    # nei "\"Your line of thinking is like a contagious disease.\""
    nei "你的思考方式無異於傳染病。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1732
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3b4c560d:

    # nei "\"Except in your case, people are excited to get sick, for reasons that escape me.\""
    nei "只不過，其他人倒是積極想被你感染，我是怎麼也想不通。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1735
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_437b0bc2:

    # ha "\"Sick you say?\""
    ha "你說疾病？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1738
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b9dc1967:

    # ha "\"In what sort of manner?\""
    ha "哪個方面？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1743
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_52c67c4b:

    # nei "\"It’s the thrill of happy lies.\""
    nei "愉快的謊言會帶來刺激。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1746
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6e3ebef6:

    # nei "\"When people want to believe in something, I find they’re much more insistent that the thing is true.\""
    nei "只要人有意相信某件事，就會更加堅持那是真的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1749
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_da351498:

    # ha "\"I’ve heard this dismissal before.\""
    ha "我以前聽過這種駁斥。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1754
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b63eb87b:

    # nei "\"I’m sure you have.\""
    nei "這我不意外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1757
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6bcafa0b:

    # nei "\"Frequently, no doubt.\""
    nei "肯定很頻繁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1759
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7558e8e5:

    # ha "\"Not so frequently around here.\""
    ha "在這裡沒那麼頻繁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1761
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_02713622:

    # nei "\"Well.\""
    nei "嗯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1764
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d250f076:

    # nei "\"Creativity serves, when proper entertainment is scarce.\""
    nei "在沒什麼正經娛樂的地方，創意自然能大展身手。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1770
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2b06d4dd:

    # ha "\"There’s nothing entertaining about watching somebody you know cut somebody open and then finding out that it has happened.\""
    ha "看見熟人砍殺別人，才發現以前也出過事，可一點都不有趣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1774
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1e96243d:

    # nei "\"And this has happened to you?\""
    nei "你經歷過？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1778
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c05ebffb:

    # ha "\"It’s happened to people in this town.\""
    ha "這個鎮上的人經歷過。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1781
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f7c32088:

    # ha "\"People see themselves hurt the ones they love and then proceed to do it.\""
    ha "人們會看見自己傷害心愛的人，然後真的照做。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1787
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b7bfac47:

    # mu "\"Could you explain what you mean by that?\""
    mu "你能解釋這畫是什麼意思嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1789
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_02ccf733:

    # "Harlan hums."
    "Harlan應了一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1793
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9af898e7:

    # ha "\"Surely you must know what I’m talking about?\""
    ha "你們肯定明白我的意思吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1795
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3389919a:

    # ha "\"Where the sky is as red as it is today?\""
    ha "今天天空都一片火紅了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1798
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_11f92e28:

    # ha "\"Where the town is always on fire?\""
    ha "整個小鎮都燒起來了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1800
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_31c66d86:

    # mu "\"Admittedly I haven’t experienced anything quite so vivid.\""
    mu "老實說，我還真沒經歷過這麼生動的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1802
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_04d5be99:

    # mu "\"My friend and I believe there’s conditions you can create to avoid the worst symptoms.\""
    mu "我和朋友們相信，可以創造某些情境來避免最糟糕的症狀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1805
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e29e5852:

    # ha "\"Naturally.\""
    ha "這是自然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1808
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9f1a5184:

    # ha "\"Cultures older than our current dominion have used medicines to protect themselves under spiritual warfare.\""
    ha "比現代當權者更古老的文化，曾靠藥物在生靈爭戰中自保。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1811
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_36cf279e:

    # ha "\"It’s more difficult for a spirit to control your body when you can’t maintain control yourself.\""
    ha "靈體在人無法自制時，會更難掌控其身體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1814
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2dde6e8b:

    # ha "\"You can trick them into believing they’ve won possession.\""
    ha "有辦法欺騙，讓它們以為已經成功附身。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1819
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a8e7b0af:

    # mu "\"Is that why I can see the man inside of you now?\""
    mu "所以我現在才能看到你體內那個人嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1822
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_95064bf6:

    # "Ralph gives Murdoch a look as if he had just eaten a pawful of bees."
    "Ralph看向Murdoch的表情活像剛生吞了一大把蜜蜂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1824
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_94314e48:

    # ha "\"He thinks he’s better at hiding than he actually is.\""
    ha "他以為自己藏得很好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1827
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c4735579:

    # ha "\"In honesty, I think he would have preferred somebody younger, but he’s somewhat desperate.\""
    ha "其實我認為他更偏好年輕人，但算是走投無路了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1830
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_45ff0fc2:

    # ha "\"Sometimes I’m not even sure if he’s dead yet.\""
    ha "我有時候都不確定他是不是已經死了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1833
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_760ce2dc:

    # ha "\"Have you ever considered if it’s possible to be possessed by somebody who’s still alive?\""
    ha "你有沒有想過，人有可能被還活著的人附身？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1835
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e47d7577:

    # "The old man laughs, perfectly joyous, perfectly calm."
    "老人笑了起來，極為喜樂而坦然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1837
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e7d16f3d:

    # ha "\"Sometimes I have to wonder.\""
    ha "我有時候也不免感到好奇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1841
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_caf808fa:

    # "Neil is rolling his eyes."
    "Neil翻了個白眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1843
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d5b4d5dd:

    # "Jim seems entirely checked out of the conversation."
    "Jim似乎完全不在意這場對話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1845
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1a94dcaa:

    # "He’s staring at the wall."
    "他正盯著牆壁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1847
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_58b92900:

    # "Whatever he’s looking at, he seems interested."
    "不知道他在看什麼，但興致盎然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1849
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2b71e165:

    # "But then again, this is a man who is incredibly interested in rocks."
    "不過，他本來就是對岩石非常感興趣的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1852
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9fa53099:

    # mu "\"Does this spirit claim to hurt all of the people here?\""
    mu "這靈體有表示要傷害這裡所有人嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1854
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1611af77:

    # mu "\"In Echo, I mean.\""
    mu "我是說，回音鎮上的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1856
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d685f13b:

    # ha "\"Can you hear him?\""
    ha "你聽得到他嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1859
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1dd1dd94:

    # mu "\"No, but I see his lips moving.\""
    mu "聽不到，但看得到他嘴唇在動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1862
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4ced9ace_2:

    # ha "\"Ah.\""
    ha "哦。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1865
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1bc0b5f:

    # ha "\"Well, based on what he’s telling me, he certainly seems to think so.\""
    ha "據他所言，他確實是這麼想的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1868
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7ca9c9bd:

    # ha "\"In fact, he seems to think there would be no Echo without him.\""
    ha "事實上，他認為沒有他，回音也不復存在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1871
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_778ce14d:

    # mu "\"So if I’m able to see him...\""
    mu "既然我看得見……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1872
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_57171125:

    # mu "\"...do you think I could hurt him?\""
    mu "……你覺得我動得了他嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1874
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_731ecaff:

    # "The hare starts laughing again."
    "兔子又笑了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1877
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aba28a3c:

    # ha "\"Well I certainly won’t mind if you try!\""
    ha "哎，我肯定不介意你試試！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1881
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0854394e:

    # ha "\"After all, I think he’s been lying to me.\""
    ha "畢竟，我覺得他一直在騙我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1886
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_341cc85d:

    # nei "\"For the love of god, please cease this incoherent babbling.\""
    nei "看在老天爺的份上，你們這些胡言亂語還是消停一下吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1889
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bb2f2269:

    # ha "\"So you do believe in God, then?\""
    ha "所以你其實是相信上帝的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1892
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0c76c8a3:

    # nei "\"It’s a common expression.\""
    nei "我這只是個習慣用語。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1895
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ae8e7a48:

    # ha "\"So if you’re not a man of God you would call yourself... what?\""
    ha "既然你不是上帝的子民，那你怎麼……自稱？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1899
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_93f9ae48:

    # nei "\"A man of observation.\""
    nei "一介觀察者。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1902
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f789c745_1:

    # ha "\"Ah!\""
    ha "啊！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1905
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_21b9b491:

    # ha "\"Very good!\""
    ha "好極了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1908
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_52639230:

    # ha "\"Hopefully you can observe my ensuing confusion then.\""
    ha "那希望你能觀察一下我的困惑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1911
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_50e20085:

    # ha "\"You see, personally I’m not sure why you’re complaining?\""
    ha "這麼說吧，我個人是不太明白你有什麼好抱怨的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1914
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_77c7488d:

    # ha "\"You assured me that you only thought I was a performer, and you admit that you have time to kill?\""
    ha "你不是說過只覺得我是個演員，也表示有意殺時間嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1917
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6919a7df:

    # ha "\"Therefore, my outlandish antics should help pass the time quicker.\""
    ha "因此，我言行古怪，理應更有助於打發時間才對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1920
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ce9110d1:

    # ha "\"No?\""
    ha "不是嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1922
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_53581a66:

    # "Neil’s face remains stony."
    "Neil表情依然冷淡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1924
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b5201a91:

    # nei "\"A change in act would be more than appreciated.\""
    nei "換個表演會更受青睞。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1927
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8bf71350:

    # ha "\"How about some slapstick then.\""
    ha "那就來點鬧劇如何？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1930
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d998aedc:

    # "Harlan stands up."
    "Harlan站了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1932
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1d611c25:

    # "It might just be the angle of the light, but the shadow he casts feels much bigger than before."
    "可能是光線角度的問題，但他的影子感覺比之前大了不少。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1935
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0ea568e4:

    # ha "\"My young assistant, Mr. Byrnes, shall attempt a demonic exorcism today.\""
    ha "我的年輕助手Byrnes先生，今天將嘗試驅魔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1938
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_558ad111:

    # ha "\"What, may I ask, is his weapon of choice?\""
    ha "請問，他會以什麼作為武器呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1947
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_be8edf52:

    # "Murdoch stands up, more quickly than I’m used to seeing him move."
    "Murdoch站了起來，動作比平時要快。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1949
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_37da5ae0:

    # "He doesn’t answer the question."
    "他沒有回答問題。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1951
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8b74c62e:

    # "He just lunges at the man with his bare claws."
    "直接亮爪撲向那男人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1953
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7f14299d:

    # "None of us expected him to make this move."
    "沒人預料到他這舉動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1956
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_50c19871:

    # "But he gets knocked back against the wall." with hpunch
    "但他被彈回牆上。" with hpunch

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1958
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e6b84f76:

    # ra "\"...What the fuck?!\""
    ra "……什麼鬼！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1960
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d025acd4:

    # "I didn’t see whether the force came from Harlan or this supposed spirit."
    "我沒看清楚那股推力是來自Harlan還是那所謂的靈體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1963
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ae9023e1:

    # "But Murdoch was on the floor, and I could smell a bit of copper."
    "但Murdoch倒在地上，我聞到一點血腥味。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1965
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6a98ccd2:

    # "Ralph and I jump out of our seats, rushing to check on Murdoch."
    "Ralph和我從坐姿跳起，衝去查看Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1967
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ad74dfc3:

    # ra "\"I heard the thud from that slam!\""
    ra "都撞出聲來了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1969
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5eebd49d:

    # m "\"Are you fucking bleeding?!\""
    m "你他媽流血了！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1972
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_176df037:

    # "To my surprise, the fox chuckles."
    "出乎我意料，狐狸輕笑起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1974
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_929810ec:

    # mu "\"Just my ear.\""
    mu "耳朵而已。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1976
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1edcd70c:

    # mu "\"But Sam.\""
    mu "不過，Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1978
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_99bc57c6:

    # "His smile is a little too wide."
    "他笑得有點過於燦爛了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1980
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_49a780f9:

    # "His eyes don’t look focused."
    "眼神沒有聚焦。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1982
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_06f7643b:

    # mu "\"{i}It screamed.{/i}\""
    mu "{i}它尖叫了。{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1984
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c1da7f8b:

    # m "\"Murdoch, I know you can’t tell right now, but there’s something wrong with you.\""
    m "Murdoch，我知道你沒什麼自覺，但你不太對勁喔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1986
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_be8acbba:

    # mu "\"No.\""
    mu "沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1989
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ce7cc10a:

    # mu "\"I feel great, Sam.\""
    mu "我感覺好極了，Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1992
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_813d2312:

    # mu "\"Did you hear what I said?\""
    mu "你聽到我說的話了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1995
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b0115da3:

    # mu "\"I said it...\""
    mu "我說它……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1997
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_79a7787e:

    # "His gaze looks really out of focus now."
    "他眼神徹底渙散了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:1999
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_856cfabd:

    # mu "\"Sam, it screamed...\""
    mu "它尖叫了，Sam……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2003
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7b90b6e5:

    # "I look over to the others."
    "我看向其他人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2005
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6c433b54:

    # "Jim is still staring at the wall."
    "Jim依舊盯著牆壁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2007
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3e299b04:

    # "This time, instead of interested, he looks scared."
    "現在不再是趣味盎然的樣子，而是恐懼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2009
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b48236d2:

    # "But he’s on his back."
    "但他正仰躺著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2011
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5bfd6803:

    # "His eyebrows are drooping."
    "眉毛下垂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2013
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_37f036cb:

    # "Neil has his head between his legs."
    "Neil把頭埋在雙腿之間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2015
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d13054e5:

    # "I can’t tell if he’s extremely bored, or just very sleepy."
    "看不出他是極度無聊，還是單純累了想睡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2017
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_27f08e20:

    # "But we all know it’s a bad idea to sleep without agreeing to shifts."
    "沒先商量好次序就睡覺絕對很糟糕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2020
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_126b1ca8:

    # ha "\"It appears that the young man has had some success in research!\""
    ha "看來這位年輕人在研究上有些成果！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2023
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4c02bf42:

    # ha "\"I’ll make sure to pass his knowledge on.\""
    ha "我會確保他的知識能傳承下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2026
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6649d74d:

    # ha "\"As a man of observation, I can tell that you understand how sluggish your body grows.\""
    ha "作為一介觀察者，我看得出你知道身體變遲鈍了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2029
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_80e00806:

    # ha "\"Lifting your eyelids used to be second nature, but now it’s becomes something of a chore.\""
    ha "以往自然而然就能抬起的眼皮，現在卻成了苦勞。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2032
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0e4ff912:

    # ha "\"Just stay comfortable.\""
    ha "你就儘管放鬆吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2035
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_101de8d1:

    # ha "\"The worst part happens when you aren’t awake.\""
    ha "等你不再清醒，才是最糟的部分呢……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2037
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d2670d0e:

    # "His voice is strangely soothing."
    "他的聲音奇妙地舒心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2039
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_53f26a4b:

    # "Closing my eyes feels better than I thought it would."
    "閉上眼睛的感覺，比我想像中還要舒服。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2040
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6dc834b1:

    # "After all, none of us have had the rest we needed."
    "畢竟，我們大家都沒能得到應有的休息。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2045
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d273147e:

    # "I can’t believe this has happened."
    "不敢相信居然發生了這種事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2049
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b3482228:

    # bl "\"It was only just yesterday that we found her Ms. Byrnes.\""
    bl "我們可是昨天才找到她的，Byrnes女士。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2050
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c00f01b4:

    # "Her eyes are closed."
    "她的眼睛閉著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2051
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_12f1e99a:

    # "Her chest is rising, just barely."
    "胸膛勉強還在起伏。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2052
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2554c0f0:

    # bl "\"How the hell did this happen?\""
    bl "到底為什麼會發生這種事？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2053
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_129b6b87:

    # "Ms. Byrnes stares forward, here eyes as wide as saucers."
    "Byrnes女士望著前方，眼睛瞪得像碟子一樣大。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2055
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ee8cd1e9:

    # dh "\"Because this is an evil place Miss Washington.\""
    dh "因為這裡是個邪惡的地方，Washington同學。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2058
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_689494c1:

    # dh "\"It was evil and she knew just as much as the rest of us.\""
    dh "它很邪惡，而她知道的和我們其他人一樣多。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2060
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cb8b88dc:

    # bl "\"Yes.\""
    bl "沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2062
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_46fa1dcf:

    # dh "\"Should I have told her she couldn’t come with us?\""
    dh "我是不是應該叫她別跟我們一起來？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2064
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_69fabf09:

    # bl "\"Yes!\""
    bl "那當然！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2066
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b9231836:

    # dh "\"Would she have listened either way?\""
    dh "可是她會聽嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2068
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eb9114c4:

    # "She wouldn’t have."
    "她不會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2069
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ccf91094:

    # bl "\"We could have tried to make her.\""
    bl "可以強迫她啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2071
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_14cdedcb:

    # dh "\"You can’t control her any more than I can control you.\""
    dh "妳控制不了她的，就像我控制不了妳一樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2073
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fb6e33a2:

    # "Shit."
    "媽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2074
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ac040100:

    # "Shit shit shit."
    "媽的媽的媽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2075
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_07b8067d:

    # "God fucking damn it shit fuck ass idiot asshole balls GARBAGE."
    "天殺的狗屎操蛋蠢貨廢物垃圾人渣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2077
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fd335c25:

    # me "\"...Bli...\""
    me "……Bli……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2078
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8411e3b4:

    # bl "\"Melissa?\""
    bl "Melissa？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2079
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_efdcd9f3:

    # bl "\"Melissa are you up, baby?\""
    bl "Melissa，你醒了嗎，小寶貝？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2080
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_af451baa:

    # me "\"...Too dizzy.\""
    me "……頭好暈。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2081
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_197fd13f:

    # me "\"Not safe yet... is it?\""
    me "現在還很危險……對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2082
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2df5109f:

    # bl "\"You’re safe.\""
    bl "妳很安全。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2083
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_99efe038:

    # bl "\"I’ll always make sure you’re safe.\""
    bl "我永遠都會保護妳周全。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2084
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9812b219:

    # bl "\"Even if no one else in this whole wide world can.\""
    bl "哪怕全世界沒有別人能做到。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2085
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1152e161:

    # me "\"Not... me.\""
    me "不是……我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2086
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c1086b74:

    # me "\"...Check... them.\""
    me "……去看看……他們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2087
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2cc7b95a:

    # "I blink."
    "我眨了眨眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2088
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4705778c:

    # bl "\"Check who?\""
    bl "看誰？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2089
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_df65996b:

    # me "\"...others.\""
    me "……其他人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2090
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_94871ed8:

    # "Why?"
    "為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2091
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0e8a4007:

    # "Does she mean... the old man?"
    "她是指……那個老頭嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2092
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6915c32d:

    # "Surely four young men can more than handle him."
    "四個年輕力壯的男人肯定能輕鬆搞定他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2093
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_83c66d22:

    # "Mr Ayers alone can probably handle him."
    "光是Ayers先生一個人可能就夠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2094
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_72fdd4f7:

    # "Even if he is slow."
    "雖然他是個傻缺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2095
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_47373b9e:

    # "...Checking wouldn’t hurt though, would it?"
    "……不過去確認一下也沒什麼壞處吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2097
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d07d828b:

    # "I crack the door just to see."
    "我把門打開一條縫查看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2102
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_74f19545:

    # "This has already been a mistake."
    "這就已經是個錯誤了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2103
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4d8c4393:

    # "God damn it."
    "天殺的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2105
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fabf2e6b:

    # "Not now."
    "現在不行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2106
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_af93ef5d:

    # "It is not the time for this."
    "現在不是時候。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2107
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_91b3dc06:

    # "Any time but now."
    "什麼時候都可以，就是現在不行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2109
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2f120190:

    # "I see children rising from the hills."
    "我看到一群孩子自山丘上升起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2110
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bcf6dd4d:

    # "No."
    "不對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2111
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_944b6161:

    # "Some of them are adults too, but they’re short."
    "有些是成人，但很矮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2112
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0a7142ed:

    # "There’s girls, and boys."
    "有女孩，也有男孩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2113
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_65e9c298:

    # "They stretch their arms out when they rise, like they’re sleeping."
    "伸展手臂起身，像是剛睡醒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2114
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_abfb6ba7:

    # "All of them wear white gowns."
    "全都穿著白色長袍。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2115
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_adce386f:

    # "Woven poppies sit atop their crowns."
    "頭戴手編罌粟花冠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2116
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7808039b:

    # "They don’t look sad, but they don’t look happy either."
    "不顯傷悲，但也不露喜樂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2117
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e2f579a5:

    # "They look surprised to be awake."
    "似乎對蘇醒感到驚訝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2119
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f6e82c87:

    # "They march in one line."
    "排成一列前行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2120
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d0a11768:

    # "One procession."
    "一列隊伍。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2121
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dbfbbebd:

    # "Each of them grabs the back of the next one’s robe, like they’re hiding in each other’s sheets."
    "每個人都抓著下一個人的袍子後方，像是躲在彼此的被單裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2122
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d2487f3d:

    # "I don’t think I will follow them."
    "我不想跟著他們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2123
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0e2dd205:

    # "They don’t like that."
    "可他們不樂意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2124
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f7447156:

    # "They will become unhappy with me if I do not follow."
    "要是我不跟著，就會惹他們不高興。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2125
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fa28f937:

    # "So I don’t have a choice then."
    "所以我別無選擇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2126
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2e2e176d:

    # "That’s okay, and fine, and fair."
    "這樣也行、沒關係、很公平。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2127
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_738d95d4:

    # "So here I am."
    "所以我在這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2128
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d7e55ccd:

    # "Here in their endless bed of grass and marigolds."
    "在他們由草和萬壽菊花鋪成、一望無際的床上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2130
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2cc4ade0:

    # "I hear the beach for some reason."
    "我莫名聽到了海的聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2131
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1c9d93d2:

    # "We’re nowhere near the beach."
    "我們離海邊很遠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2132
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7fb07cc0:

    # "Does that matter?"
    "但這重要嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2134
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c9f019e3:

    # "It never does to them."
    "這對他們而言，從來都無所謂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2136
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c16be3f2:

    # "Regardless, I am here."
    "總而言之，我人來到了這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2137
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a1d521f4:

    # "There is a nice porch to a stone and wood house by the sea."
    "海邊有一棟由石頭和木頭建成的房子，有個漂亮的門廊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2139
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6d559665:

    # "They open both doors."
    "他們把兩扇門都打開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2140
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5691f9e2:

    # "Light from the outside floods in, but that doesn’t matter."
    "室外的光芒湧入，但這不重要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2141
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_20837f9e:

    # "Light does not enter this house, but I do, and so does this procession."
    "光無法進入這棟房子，但我可以，這列隊伍也進去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2144
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b1491616:

    # "We glide up twisting staircases."
    "我們順著螺旋階梯滑行而上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2146
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d7c90448:

    # "We move past impractically placed furniture."
    "經過擺放不切實際的家具。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2147
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cee1ad6c:

    # "We roll past corners that lead to nowhere."
    "拐過通向無處的轉角。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2149
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ea59a776:

    # "Ambling eventually to nondescript, vacuous somewhere."
    "最後漫步至毫無特色的空曠之地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2150
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_51195d5a:

    # "Shapes eventually fall into place, organizing the architecture."
    "形狀最終歸位，組織起建築。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2152
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9ffe55a0:

    # "I now see a dark room."
    "我現在看到一間暗房。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2153
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b8884e48:

    # "Backlit by a crimson wash."
    "被腥紅的逆光照亮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2154
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e4927b18:

    # "The only way I can describe how it feels is if light could bleed."
    "我唯一能用來形容的詞語，就是光流血的樣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2155
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8bdd7256:

    # "Or if light could get an infection."
    "或者光被感染的樣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2156
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5ea6ea8c:

    # "Light that rots and festers."
    "會腐爛、潰爛的光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2157
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cc50aa0c:

    # "Bleeching rays that stain your skin with some sort of hot poison that clings stubbornly to you like an oily residue."
    "漂白般的射線以某種灼熱的毒藥浸染皮膚，像油性殘渣一樣頑強沾黏。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2158
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cec91cc7:

    # "In this dark room, there is a giant bed."
    "在這間暗房裡，有一張巨大的床。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2159
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_874c2174:

    # "It is layered in more sheets than I would have expected on a bed."
    "鋪了數量離譜的床單。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2160
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8aa829a4:

    # "They travel upward, covering a figure who somehow is too tall for the huge mattress it sits upon."
    "床單向上延伸，蓋住一道坐在床墊上的身影。它對於床墊而言實在太高大了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2161
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9e5ffdef:

    # "It leans over another wrapped figure, who lies on the bed."
    "它俯身在另一道被包裹住、躺在床上的身影。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2162
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_07e33cf2:

    # "This one is much smaller, but completely cocooned by the blankets."
    "這道身影小得多，但完全被毯子包裹。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2163
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b6dc6728:

    # "I can’t see its face, but by the way its chest heaves, I know it’s Melissa."
    "我看不到它的臉，但從胸膛起伏的樣子，我看出那是Melissa。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2164
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_84a56c90:

    # "She’s struggling to get out."
    "她正在掙扎著想爬出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2165
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5126f601:

    # "I want to help her, but the children grow angry when I do."
    "我很想幫她，但孩子們會生氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2166
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9de552e7:

    # "I don’t know what they are, but I don’t think they are children anymore."
    "我不清楚他們是什麼，但感覺已經不再是孩子了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2167
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4456c65d:

    # "I wonder what to do."
    "我尋思該採取什麼行動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2168
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_33b6a066:

    # "I’m reminded of butterflies."
    "我聯想到了蝴蝶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2169
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_17d5b3c3:

    # "You’re not supposed to let them out of their cocoons early, or else they’ll wither and die."
    "不能讓牠們過早破繭，否則會夭折。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2170
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_649b6140:

    # "But the draped thing leans over her again."
    "但那道披著床單的身影再次俯向她。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2171
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cedaf5be:

    # "It puts its hands on her."
    "它把雙手放在她身上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2172
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_94f6ce0e:

    # "{i}He{/i} puts his hands on {i}her{/i}."
    "{i}他{/i}把雙手放在{i}她{/i}身上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2173
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0ddca73f:

    # "I don’t know how I know it is a he, but I just know that it is."
    "我不清楚自己是如何得知它是他的，但我就是知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2174
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ca7e75dd:

    # "He’s going to tear her out too soon."
    "他會過早把她扯出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2175
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d7a92349:

    # "He’s going to tear her out and kill her."
    "他會把她扯出來殺掉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2176
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_65d9cfc0:

    # "Does he think he is safe because he can’t see me?"
    "他是因為看不到我，才以為自己很安全嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2177
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_341aa168:

    # "Does he think I am harmless because he does not look at me?"
    "是因為眼中沒有我，才以為我算不上威脅嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2178
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dac271e3:

    # "My hands move on their own even though my mind would have given the message just as surely."
    "我的手擅自動了起來——雖說頭腦肯定也會下達同樣的指令就是了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2179
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1910a6d2:

    # "To protect what I love he must die."
    "為了保護我心愛之人，他必須死。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2180
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b79bb643:

    # "He must die."
    "他必須死。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2181
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b79bb643_1:

    # "He must die."
    "他必須死。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2184
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_37193e62:

    # "And so the blade slips through him like butter."
    "刀刃像在切奶油一樣刺入他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2185
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b36c2064:

    # "It goes in deep but not fare enough to get through him."
    "刺得很深，但還不足以貫穿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2186
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7e0c1c57:

    # "The silken bedsheets fade into a meek paisley."
    "絲綢床單淡化成柔和的佩斯利花紋。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2187
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_08f68bb9:

    # "Crimson stains blossom in the off-white rags."
    "腥紅的污漬在米白的破布上綻放開來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2188
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_64318a11:

    # "I see the wild eyes of a dying old man look back at me."
    "垂死老人以驚狂的眼神回望我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2189
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6332daf1:

    # "He’s not a monster."
    "他並不是怪物。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2190
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b53fdbda:

    # "He’s just a dying person."
    "只是一個垂死之人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2191
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_270f335d:

    # "He tries to gore me with his horns, but I pull the sword out, and watch his mouth foams red."
    "他試圖用角刺我，但我拔出劍，看著他嘴巴吐出紅色泡沫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2192
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ec38724e:

    # "The things that aren’t children tear at him like he’s a feast of warm bread, but they aren’t able to touch him."
    "那些不是孩子的東西，像看到了溫暖的麵包一樣爭相上前撕扯，但碰不到他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2193
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_efea11c0:

    # "The red light fades."
    "紅光消退。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2195
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1af170d8:

    # "The eyes of one old man fades to another."
    "一位老人的眼睛淡化成另一位。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2196
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3ae0d840:

    # "A dead hare stares back at me."
    "一隻死去的兔子瞪著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2197
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c69c4ffe:

    # "My sword through his neck."
    "我的劍刺穿了他的脖子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2198
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_08586291:

    # "His hands on Melissa’s throat."
    "他雙手正掐著Melissa的咽喉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2199
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a59fbdb8:

    # "I can’t help but think that the wound looks strange."
    "我不禁覺得傷口看起來很奇怪。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2200
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6006cb40:

    # "If I didn’t know any better, I’d say the pokes look more like a bug bite than a stab wound."
    "要不是我知道那是被劍刺的，還以為那是蟲咬的呢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2201
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0123a866:

    # "I wander over to the trap door."
    "我走向活板門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2202
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_27aee7c9:

    # "I open it up."
    "拉開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2203
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_169c431c:

    # "I let him fall."
    "讓他掉下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2204
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_76ed4ce3:

    # "Then I seal it up."
    "然後封住。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2206
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b31f007f:

    # "Ms. Byrnes looks over at me."
    "Byrnes女士看向我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2207
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_885e561d:

    # "I wonder about what kind of thing she’s going to say, considering she must have seen it all."
    "我很好奇她會說什麼，畢竟她肯定目睹了一切。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2209
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_688ce480:

    # "But she just says a number out loud."
    "但她只是大聲說出一個數字。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2212
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eeb5bc53:

    # "I bar the door with the bed since I can’t lock it from the inside."
    "我用床抵住門，因為沒法從裡面上鎖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2214
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_496b119f:

    # "I’m not moving it until I know the sun is up."
    "在確定太陽升起之前，我是不會動它的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2220
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9aa4a7ac:

    # "I hear a door slam."
    "我聽到門被甩上的聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2225
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1ebe84e:

    # "Then I open my eyes."
    "然後睜開雙眼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2226
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dc74b4a0:

    # "Letting somebody drag me by my feet while I pretended to sleep might have been one of the hardest things I’ve ever done."
    "假裝睡著被人拉著腿拖走，可能是我做過最難的事之一。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2228
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1d7a011b:

    # "But if this is going to work, I know I have to surprise him."
    "但是我知道，要想成功，只能給他一個出其不意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2230
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7577d1a7:

    # "I needed to know whether he was really lying or not."
    "我要知道他是不是真的在騙人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2232
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a0946d9d:

    # "And everybody else needed to know he’d betray us, that the path to the train was just a trick."
    "其他人也得知道他會背叛、那條通往火車的路只是個騙局。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2234
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0d84e628:

    # "I’m in one of those little rooms."
    "我身處其中一間小房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2235
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_134f04fb:

    # "I hear the sound of somebody breathing."
    "聽見某人的呼吸聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2237
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_88ce4c97:

    # "I put my hands on them and shake them."
    "伸手搖晃對方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2239
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e302cbb4:

    # "They don’t rouse."
    "不省人事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2241
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_28226c0f:

    # "When my eyes adjust a bit to the dark I can see it’s Neil."
    "眼睛適應黑暗後，我才看出那是Neil。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2243
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f22faecc:

    # "Jim is next to him, chest rising slowly."
    "Jim在他旁邊，胸膛緩緩起伏。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2245
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bc2aec7d:

    # "When I shake Jim, his eyes flutter open briefly, but then he goes back to sleep."
    "在我搖晃Jim時，他眼睛睜開了一瞬間，卻又睡了回去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2247
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_90547c94:

    # "I crawl over to the next person I hear."
    "我爬向聽見的下一個人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2249
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d66e605e:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}Careful where you place your hand.\""
    ra "{cps=35}你可別亂碰啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2251
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0001d414:

    # m "\"Ralph, you’re awake?\""
    m "Ralph，你還醒著？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2253
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fc030c6e:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}Of course I’m awake.\""
    ra "{cps=35}我當然醒著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2255
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9058fe79:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}I spat the water out just like you did.\""
    ra "{cps=35}我跟你一樣把水吐掉了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2257
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a8752863:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}We’re lucky none of us were caught.\""
    ra "{cps=35}幸好沒被發現。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2259
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_08ad5323:

    # m "\"So there’s no doubt about it now.\""
    m "所以現在就毫無疑問了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2261
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8ec23e10:

    # m "\"When everybody here wakes up, there won’t be any denying.\""
    m "等大伙都醒來，就不會有人有異議了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2263
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_aefa63c0:

    # m "\"We either shoot him or jump him on sight.\""
    m "看到他就開槍或直接撲上去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2265
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6c36aa85:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}What makes you think everybody’s getting up?\""
    ra "{cps=35}你怎麼認為大家都會醒來？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2267
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9d3344cb:

    # m "\"What do you mean?\""
    m "什麼意思？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2269
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_de1a01e4:

    # m "\"He just put everybody to sleep...\""
    m "他只是把大家弄昏了……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2271
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_03701ca4:

    # "Didn’t he?"
    "不是嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2273
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_45c2ade2:

    # ra "\"{cps=34}Nobody’s hands are tied.\""
    ra "{cps=34}沒人手被綁著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2275
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6ce7cd29:

    # "A creeping tingle works up my spine."
    "一股寒意竄上脊椎。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2277
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5fd58ffd:

    # ra "\"{cps=34}All of the witnesses here suspect him of arson, isn’t that right?\""
    ra "{cps=34}這裡所有目擊者都懷疑是他放的火，對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2279
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fe973ccd:

    # ra "\"{cps=34}If you merely woke up then I have no doubt that you’d be able to batter the door down.\""
    ra "{cps=34}你能平安醒來，肯定是能把門撞開的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2281
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_151edb41:

    # m "\"Murdoch didn’t drink...\""
    m "Murdoch沒喝……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2283
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_757eb7b3:

    # ra "\"{cps=34}Of course he did.\""
    ra "{cps=34}他當然喝了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2285
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6a20a80d:

    # "I shake my head."
    "我搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2287
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_206236d4:

    # m "\"No, he wouldn’t...\""
    m "不對，他不會的……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2289
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7a7b8d1b:

    # "I crawl through the dark, listening to where the breathing sounds are coming from."
    "我在黑暗中爬行，聽著呼吸聲從哪裡傳來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2291
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f3aa5675:

    # "I catch the chemical scent of his lemon aftershave and his sweat, which has a sickly tinge to it now."
    "聞到了他檸檬鬍後水的化學藥劑味和汗味——現在帶著病懨懨的味道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2293
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_40d2b016:

    # m "\"But I’m sure he knew there was something in the flask.\""
    m "可是我很確定他知道那瓶子有問題。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2295
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a5e6239e:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}And you also know that he’d put something in his body if he thought he’d get a chance to get another way of looking at things.\""
    ra "{cps=32}但你也知道，吞下些什麼東西，就是他逃避現實的方式。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2297
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_56842ba4:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}He’s been desperate to get here.\""
    ra "{cps=32}來到這裡是他的夙願。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2299
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fbc666b3:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}Wherever {i}here{/i} is.\""
    ra "{cps=32}無論{i}這裡{/i}是什麼地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2301
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_59fa6338:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}There was no way to stop him without tipping off the old man.\""
    ra "{cps=32}想在不讓那老頭起疑的前提下制止他，是不可能的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2303
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4b294e6e:

    # m "\"But why the hell would he do that?\""
    m "可是他到底為什麼要這樣？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2305
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_16d47f19:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}Maybe because he saw what I saw.\""
    ra "{cps=32}也許是因為看見了我找到的東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2307
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9e113ddb:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}There’s activated charcoal in those cabinets up front.\""
    ra "{cps=32}前面的櫃子裡有活性炭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2309
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7cea3e22:

    # "I rise off of my feet."
    "我站了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2311
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2e80c20a:

    # m "\"I’m gonna bust this door down.\""
    m "我要把這扇門撞開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2313
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8b7bf16a:

    # "But the rat grabs my wrist."
    "但老鼠抓住我的手腕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2315
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_976b9ae1:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}Wait.\""
    ra "{cps=32}慢著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2317
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_28a1882c:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}Remember what happened to the girl?\""
    ra "{cps=32}還記得那女孩怎麼了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2319
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bbe2ecfe:

    # "He points a long claw at the foot of the door."
    "他用一隻長爪指向門前地上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2321
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_22e93e89:

    # "Light from behind the door shines off the surface of steel teeth."
    "鋼牙反射著門後面的光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2323
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_336ef3af:

    # "There might be three or more of them."
    "可能不只三具。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2325
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7bf1dd97:

    # ra "\"{cps=32}If you find something weighted to set them off--\""
    ra "{cps=32}如果能找到重物觸發——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2327
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6a20a80d_1:

    # "I shake my head."
    "我搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2329
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c651d0c8_1:

    # m "\"No.\""
    m "不行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2331
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_05e72fe7:

    # m "\"These kinds of traps are loud.\""
    m "這種陷阱很大聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2333
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c0bb9e9e:

    # m "\"You hear them go off in the woods if you’re close enough.\""
    m "在森林裡時，不離太遠都能聽到觸發的聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2335
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_541a128f:

    # "I look a little longer into the dark."
    "我在黑暗中多看了一會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2337
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fb100e92:

    # "There’s enough light to make out the shine of a chain."
    "有足夠的光線能看出鎖鏈的反光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2339
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f4bc9761:

    # "I step carefully."
    "我小心踏步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2341
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bf1c6274:

    # "Hunch down."
    "蹲下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2343
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_22a0b6a2:

    # "Then I feel for the cool edges of the chains."
    "然後摸索著鎖鏈冰冷的邊緣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2345
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e252cb3a:

    # "They’re coarser to the touch than I had expected."
    "觸感起來比我想像中更粗糙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2347
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_60e20e4f:

    # "They’re rusted."
    "生鏽了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2349
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2eaee259:

    # "They must have been here for a long time."
    "一定已經很老舊了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2351
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f13daa46:

    # "Slowly, I drag the chain."
    "我緩緩拖動鎖鏈。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2353
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ab80b2d8_1:

    # "Slowly."
    "慢慢地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2355
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ab80b2d8_2:

    # "Slowly."
    "慢慢地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2357
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ca10e61c:

    # "I hear the soft clang of metal."
    "金屬輕聲碰撞。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2359
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_029aa8fc:

    # "That’s how I know where the other trap is."
    "這樣就能知道另一具陷阱在哪了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2361
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d8fd18e8:

    # "It’s too dark to see where it starts but the sound is enough."
    "太暗了看不清楚位置，但聽聲音就夠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2362
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d428c3a8:

    # "This is how we used to snag our supper when the fish didn’t bite."
    "以前釣不到魚的時候，我們就是這樣抓晚餐的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2364
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2d66eb3e:

    # "Sometimes I’d set as many as thirty a day, under hot sun, choked by the warm, wet fog that sticks in your lungs when you try to breathe."
    "有時候我一天會設個三十具，在大太陽下被溫熱濕黏的霧氣嗆到肺底。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2366
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_147a8a7b:

    # "I used to think that place was hell on earth."
    "我以前覺得那地方就是人間地獄。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2368
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3882cc2b:

    # "But hell keeps finding me wherever I go."
    "但不管我去哪，地獄總是跟著不放過我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2370
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_dcd1a774:

    # "Every day I survive, it makes everything just a little bit easier."
    "那些經歷給了我活下去的能力。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2372
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bcc4a028:

    # "If things had been good, would I be alive today?"
    "但如果一切本就安好，我現在還會活著嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2374
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4d148263:

    # "I don’t really know."
    "我真的不知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2376
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f550634b:

    # "It’s hard to know who to thank for the evils inflicted on you."
    "很難說自己受那麼多苦難，究竟該感謝誰。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2378
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d3a8ddac:

    # "I hear the third clang of metal."
    "第三聲金屬碰撞響起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2380
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_abba3278:

    # "The chain is easy to find on this one too."
    "這一具的鎖鏈也很好找。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2382
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d36ba445:

    # "All I need to do is drag them out of the doorway."
    "只要把這些拖離門口就好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2384
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_19fe774e:

    # "The weight of them scrapes against the ground."
    "陷阱重重刮著地面。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2386
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7006b761:

    # "But I get them out of the way soon enough."
    "但很快就移開了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2388
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8d54853a:

    # "I lay them down, just as slowly, just as careful as before."
    "我跟先前一樣緩慢小心地放下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2390
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bb7a02fc:

    # "I’m just as mindful of the chains, so they’re coiled and out of the way."
    "我對鎖鏈也是同樣細心，捲好後擺在一旁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2391
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_887053a6:

    # m "\"The door is clear.\""
    m "門口清乾淨了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2392
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cb52a1cf:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}Do you hear anybody outside?\""
    ra "{cps=30}聽得見外面有沒有人在嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2393
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_31be2ffd:

    # "I press my ear against the wood."
    "我把耳朵貼在木頭上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2395
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cf202ed8:

    # "It’s thicker than I remember, but there’s gaps in the planks."
    "比我印象中厚，但木板之間有縫隙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2397
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7e539b8b:

    # "So it’s definitely not soundproof."
    "所以隔音不好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2399
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_826368da:

    # "I wait around for a while."
    "我等了一陣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2401
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4c9a0977:

    # "I try to listen for sounds of breathing or shuffling around."
    "在聽有沒有呼吸聲或走動聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2402
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5bf9ccd6:

    # "But there’s nothing."
    "但什麼都沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2404
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_45a087cd:

    # "If he tried to get to the girls then they would have likely barricaded themselves in."
    "如果他的目標是女孩們，她們肯定會把門擋住。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2406
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_45c8948f:

    # "At the very least I would have heard a struggle with the door."
    "這樣我至少會聽到他破門的動靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2408
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7af622c8:

    # "Unless he had some way to get them to open it willingly."
    "除非他有辦法令她們自願開門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2410
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8061dd50:

    # "Harlan isn’t dumb enough to risk sleeping himself right now."
    "Harlan沒笨到會冒險在這種時候睡覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2412
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_36a780aa:

    # "I know I wouldn’t be, after what he’s done."
    "都已經做出了那些事，換作是我也不會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2414
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_531d988a:

    # "I don’t need to know why he did it."
    "我不必知道他為什麼要做。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2416
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7f6d3cc5:

    # "I just know that he did."
    "知道他做了就夠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2418
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1ae7ebf0:

    # "If I doubted before that he started the fire in his room at the Hip, the doubt is long gone."
    "就算之前對Hip酒館是不是他放的火還有疑慮，現在也已經很清楚了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2420
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4a584779:

    # "I’m certain of what he’s capable of."
    "我很清楚他做得出什麼事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2422
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_09c317cb:

    # "The question now is just..."
    "當前的問題只有……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2424
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_64b21c15:

    # "Where is he?"
    "他人在哪裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2426
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_021389f3:

    # "Is he hiding then?"
    "是躲起來了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2428
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_469cd171:

    # "Maybe."
    "是有可能。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2430
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ac194471:

    # "But that doesn’t line up with how he’s acted."
    "但這跟他之前的行為不符。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2432
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f95203ef:

    # "He does damage and then he runs."
    "他是幹了就跑的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2434
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1940c6d3:

    # "For all I know he could be miles away from us by now if he really knows how to navigate those tunnels."
    "要是他真的熟悉隧道的路線，現在可能已經跑好幾里遠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2436
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a5a2c3d5:

    # "Still, I should take a weapon."
    "不過，我還是該拿把武器。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2438
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d7da34c6:

    # "I remember that Neil has a gun."
    "我記得Neil有把槍。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2440
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_1ec42d03:

    # "Turning around, I loom over his body."
    "我轉身，俯視他的身體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2441
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_52730f7a:

    # "I move his arm, and it seems like he’s waking up."
    "動了他的手臂後，他是有要醒來的跡象。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2443
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e97bc6d9:

    # "But he just grimaces and goes limp again."
    "但只是皺了皺臉，又癱軟下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2445
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_25633c8c:

    # "Like he’s having a bad dream."
    "像是在做惡夢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2447
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5ca2ad69:

    # "I can see the imprint of his revolver making a dent in his coat pocket."
    "他外套口袋突起左輪手槍的形狀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2449
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2c2420cc:

    # "I’m just going to borrow this for a little while."
    "我就是借用一下這個。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2451
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7ce100d3:

    # "Sorry."
    "不好意思。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2454
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2c98dc7b:

    # m "\"Ralph, help me with the door.\""
    m "Ralph，來幫我撞門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2456
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_96aac006:

    # "The rat looks straight forward."
    "老鼠直視前方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2458
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_571115e7:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}I probably shouldn’t move around too much.\""
    ra "{cps=30}我最好還是別亂動了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2460
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c4717c66:

    # "I give him a look."
    "我看向他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2462
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fdcfd18e:

    # m "\"Why?\""
    m "為啥？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2464
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_596953c3:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}Had to hold the water longer than you.\""
    ra "{cps=30}我水含得比你久。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2466
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_75b2d712:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}He knew I was a chemist.\""
    ra "{cps=30}他知道我是化學家。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2468
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e6fd0d37:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}I swallowed some.\""
    ra "{cps=30}吞了一點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2470
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fb6e33a2_1:

    # "Shit."
    "媽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2472
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b0967675:

    # "So he’s going to need medicine too."
    "所以他也需要藥。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2474
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_88491e1a:

    # m "\"Do you know what kind of poison he used?\""
    m "你知道他下的是什麼毒嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2476
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2fb1698d:

    # ra "\"{cps=27}Nobody’s having violent seizures so that’s the good news.\""
    ra "{cps=27}沒人劇烈抽搐，這是好事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2478
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3bf58f5b:

    # ra "\"{cps=27}If I had to guess, he used deathcap.\""
    ra "{cps=27}要我猜的話，應該是死帽菇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2480
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eed233ff:

    # ra "\"{cps=27}That one puts you to sleep before you go.\""
    ra "{cps=27}會讓人在死前先陷入沉睡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2482
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f5db4ae8:

    # ra "\"{cps=27}Fifty grams of charcoal would be enough to cover the toxicity for adults.\""
    ra "{cps=27}對成人而言，50克的活性炭就能對抗體內的毒性了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2484
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_22089f0c:

    # m "\"Fifty {i}what?{/i}\""
    m "五十{i}什麼{/i}？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2486
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b0ecaf3a:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}...Just knock the door down and I’ll measure the proportions.\""
    ra "{cps=25}……你只管把門撞開就是了，比例我來測量。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2488
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6735575e:

    # "I exhale as I rise, looking back at the door behind me."
    "我吐著氣站起身子，回頭看向身後的門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2490
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5a70fef6:

    # "I need a running start."
    "需要助跑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2492
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_996cd6c3:

    # "I stare forward."
    "我盯著前方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2494
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ccfe9347:

    # "Then I move as quickly forward as I think I can make my body go."
    "然後盡速向前衝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2496
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b69c2e1c:

    # "Before colliding with the door, I turn to my side."
    "在撞上門之前轉身側對著門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2498
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_318b7bf4:

    # "I slam into the door and hear a crack." with hpunch
    "猛撞在門上，聽見碎裂的聲音。" with hpunch

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2499
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_cbb5edf2:

    # "A dull ache of pain runs through my shoulder."
    "肩膀一陣鈍痛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2502
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d9d4143a:

    # "The force of my body wasn’t strong enough to break the door, but the latch had rotted out."
    "我身體的力量不足以撞破門的本體，但門閂早就腐朽了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2503
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_16a18e00:

    # "The door is open."
    "門就這麼開了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2505
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b6420999:

    # "I see somebody staring right at me."
    "我看到有人正面盯著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2506
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_db514e91:

    # "I flinch, expecting to see the angry eyes of a hare staring back at me."
    "我嚇了一跳，以為會是兔子憤怒的眼神。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2507
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8b9675c4:

    # "Instead, they’re the cold eyes of a young fox."
    "然而，卻是一隻年輕狐狸的冰冷眼眸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2509
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3456cff9:

    # "He isn’t there for long."
    "他沒有待很久。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2510
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_df6007d7:

    # "If he ever really was."
    "假如他真的存在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2511
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5a0ab5d3:

    # "If he’s the one Murdoch is doing this for, I don’t think he should trust it."
    "如果他就是Murdoch做出這種傻事的目的，那我覺得他最好別信任它。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2512
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c7e37386:

    # "Especially if it might be talking to him."
    "尤其是它會向他說話的情況。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2513
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4967536e:

    # "For all I know, it’s whispering in his ear, just like it was whispering in mine a few days ago."
    "就跟幾天前它向我低語一樣，也會向他低語。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2514
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2ffa1cff:

    # "But I don’t have any control over what he does."
    "但我控制不了他的行為。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2516
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ecf9c226:

    # "Ralph stumbles out behind me, slumping, barely hanging onto the door frame."
    "Ralph在我身後拖著身體出來，勉強抓著門框。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2517
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_532d1068:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}Help me to the cabinet.\""
    ra "{cps=25}扶我到櫃子那邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2519
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_5eb73a18:

    # "I wrap his arm around my neck."
    "我把他的手臂繞過我的脖子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2521
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0714d1c9:

    # "He’s not too heavy to carry."
    "他不算太重。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2522
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c4583ed1:

    # "Just awkward."
    "只是行動不便。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2526
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_828a592f:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}You know how to use a scale, don’t you?\""
    ra "{cps=25}你知道怎麼用秤吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2528
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_7ce50b65:

    # "I feel the corner of my mouth turning up."
    "我感覺自己嘴角上揚。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2530
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c806ebc0:

    # m "\"Yeah.\""
    m "嗯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2532
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_6f4317b6:

    # "Ralph lets out a grunt of surprise."
    "Ralph驚訝地悶哼一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2534
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_88c367b4:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}No kidding?\""
    ra "{cps=25}不是開玩笑的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2536
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8c526106:

    # m "\"We had to weigh meat in the butcher shop back home.\""
    m "在我老家的肉店秤過肉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2538
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9d3fbc66:

    # ra "\"{cps=23}I didn’t take you for a numbers sort of fellow.\""
    ra "{cps=23}沒想到你還會算數。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2540
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_ee892291:

    # m "\"I’m not.\""
    m "我不會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2542
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2f81721a:

    # m "\"I just wrote them down.\""
    m "我只負責寫下來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2544
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2539f3ce:

    # ra "\"{cps=23}That will be enough.\""
    ra "{cps=23}那就夠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2549
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_807f0cb1:

    # ra "\"{cps=23}See that cabinet there?\""
    ra "{cps=23}看到那個櫃子了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2551
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c806ebc0_1:

    # m "\"Yeah.\""
    m "嗯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2553
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a2104e6d:

    # ra "\"{cps=23}I saw a scale in there.\""
    ra "{cps=23}我有在裡面看到一把秤。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2555
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_2fd05df8:

    # ra "\"{cps=23}Pray that it works.\""
    ra "{cps=23}祈禱還能用吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2557
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f0331905:

    # "I open the compartment."
    "我打開隔間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2559
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_789b2201:

    # "It looks awfully clean for a place that hasn’t been touched for fifty years."
    "這裡都五十年沒人動過了，它卻乾淨得過分。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2561
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e42adc79:

    # "Of course, I doubt anybody believes this place is really abandoned."
    "當然，應該也沒人相信這個地方被遺棄了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2563
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_b0f7ba18:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}You should also see a bottle with the label {i}Activated Charcoal.{/i}\""
    ra "{cps=22}應該也能找到一個標著活性炭的瓶子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2565
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4c7c625d:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}That’s one of the things that we’re going to need.\""
    ra "{cps=22}那是我們需要的東西之一。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2567
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c84e1a27:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}There’s something else too.\""
    ra "{cps=22}還需要別的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2569
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a7b71754:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}A bottle labeled {i}Milk Thistle.{/i}\""
    ra "{cps=22}一瓶標著奶薊的瓶子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2571
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f1e1cb15:

    # "What is he talking about?"
    "他說的是什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2573
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d6e09eb0:

    # "What if it’s not here."
    "沒有的話怎麼辦？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2575
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d84609b0:

    # m "\"I don’t...\""
    m "我沒……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2577
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_69a47d60:

    # "My paw glides across a smaller bottle with a green cap."
    "我的爪滑過一個綠色蓋子的小瓶子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2579
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_58d1a37e:

    # "It’s what he asked for."
    "這就是他要的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2581
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a52e1283:

    # m "\"Here it is.\""
    m "有了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2583
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_338496b6:

    # m "\"Did you find this earlier?\""
    m "你之前就發現這個了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2585
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_16099ccc:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}No.\""
    ra "{cps=22}沒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2587
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e628e822:

    # m "\"Then how did you know it would--\""
    m "那你怎麼知道會——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2589
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0d77bcd6:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}A good poisoner usually carries an antidote.\""
    ra "{cps=22}擅長用毒的人通常都會帶著解毒劑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2591
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c0a9b048:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}We’re lucky we’re not dealing with an amateur.\""
    ra "{cps=22}幸好對手不是外行人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2593
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a2590ede:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}If I wasn’t certain we were dealing with deathcap before, I am now.\""
    ra "{cps=22}之前還不能確定是不是死帽菇，現在可以了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2595
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_320c3f7c:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}Weigh the charcoal.\""
    ra "{cps=22}秤活性炭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2597
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9bf6eb1c:

    # m "\"How much of it?\""
    m "多少？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2599
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8ba92c89:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}All of it.\""
    ra "{cps=22}全部。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2601
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f5d65f6b:

    # ra "\"{cps=22}Slip a piece of paper on the scale before you do.\""
    ra "{cps=22}秤之前先放一張紙上去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2603
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_75a6504d:

    # "All of the supplies I need I can find in the cabinets."
    "我需要的東西全都能在櫃子裡找到。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2605
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8f55edab:

    # "I would feel better about that if I didn’t know what that meant."
    "要不是知道這代表什麼，還能讓我安心點呢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2607
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_15b14808:

    # "The paper shakes a bit as I put it on the scale."
    "紙被放到秤上時微微搖動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2609
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_533cf2b8:

    # "All of the black powder comes out of the bottle."
    "瓶裡所有的黑色粉末都倒出來了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2611
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e7e1b998:

    # "It doesn’t seem like that much."
    "看著沒多少。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2613
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_d73d33b0:

    # "I move the weight slider from one direction to the other."
    "我把砝碼滑片從一邊移到另一邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2615
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_759b6d31:

    # "It tilts to one side when I get to 400 g."
    "在400g時，秤傾向一邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2617
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_9408468d:

    # "Then I move the smaller slider."
    "然後移動較小的滑片。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2619
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_3eee914d:

    # "It balances at 17 g."
    "在17g時平衡了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2621
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fe398926:

    # m "\"There’s 417 {i}grams{/i} here.\""
    m "總共有417{i}克{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2623
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_24e867ab:

    # m "\"I think.\""
    m "應該吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2625
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_17000abd:

    # ra "\"{cps=20}Okay.\""
    ra "{cps=20}好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2627
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c5730da2:

    # ra "\"{cps=20}I’m starting to fade.\""
    ra "{cps=20}我快撐不住了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2628
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a164dc5d:

    # ra "\"{cps=20}So here’s what you have to do.\""
    ra "{cps=20}所以我要你這樣做："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2630
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_0e7ba916:

    # ra "\"{cps=19}Make everybody drink 50 grams of charcoal dissolved in one hour.\""
    ra "{cps=19}在一小時內讓所有人喝下50克活性炭溶液。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2632
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8574b35b:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}Add just a pinch of that milk thistle-- that’ll help our livers if they aren’t already damaged.\""
    ra "{cps=18}再加一小撮奶薊——對沒受損的肝臟很有幫助。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2634
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_bdc76834:

    # ra "\"{cps=17}We’ll probably throw up.\""
    ra "{cps=17}大概會導致嘔吐。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2636
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_a3b40784:

    # ra "\"{cps=16}After two hours we’ll need 25 grams of charcoal every two hours.\""
    ra "{cps=16}之後每隔兩小時需要25克活性炭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2638
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_8516a5fb:

    # ra "\"{cps=15}Just two more times after the first should be good enough.\""
    ra "{cps=15}第一劑之後再來兩劑應該就夠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2641
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_c708b977:

    # "Ralph slides to the ground."
    "Ralph滑坐在地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2643
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_eb589694:

    # m "\"Wait, wait, wait.\""
    m "等一下、等一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2645
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4244b472:

    # m "\"But what’s the fastest way to divide it all up?\""
    m "要怎麼樣才能最快把這些全分好？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2647
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_4bafd222:

    # "He doesn’t respond."
    "他沒有回應。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2649
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_59aa8be0:

    # "That must have been the last of his energy."
    "剛才就是他最後的力氣了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2651
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_fb6e33a2_2:

    # "Shit."
    "媽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2653
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f0657274:

    # "Okay."
    "好吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2655
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_f0657274_1:

    # "Okay."
    "別慌。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2657
translate Tchinese murdochroute4b_e34165a8:

    # "I have 417 grams."
    "我有417克。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2672
translate Tchinese medicine1_f2dde8ab:

    # "Half of the dosage is over 200 grams."
    "一半就超過了200克。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2689
translate Tchinese medicine2_3767029b:

    # "That’s the first dosage taken care of."
    "第一次的劑量搞定了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2691
translate Tchinese medicine2_a16b645e:

    # "Now for the second and third dosages."
    "接下來是第二和第三次的劑量。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2705
translate Tchinese medicine3_f0657274:

    # "Okay."
    "行了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2719
translate Tchinese medicine4_08409931:

    # "I have the dosages mixed now."
    "我已經搞定劑量了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2729
translate Tchinese medicine5_4fee121e:

    # "Shit, there’s something missing."
    "操，還少了什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2736
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_c23257e8:

    # "The milk thistle!"
    "是奶薊！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2737
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_2af9aae9:

    # "Jesus."
    "我的天啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2738
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_97645536:

    # "Okay..."
    "好了……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2741
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_465552ec:

    # "Ralph {i}did{/i} menition thistle."
    "Ralph{i}提過{/i}薊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2742
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_6ea67541:

    # "I quickly scan the shelves for labels starting with a {i}T{/i}."
    "我快速看了遍櫃裡有沒有{i}T{/i}開頭的標籤。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2743
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_17891049:

    # "No {i}Thistle{/i} among them."
    "沒有寫著{i}薊{/i}的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2744
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_fb6e33a2:

    # "Shit."
    "操"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2750
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_9de3216c:

    # "Ralph did mention {i}something{/i} about {i}milk{/i}."
    "Ralph好像還有提到{i}奶{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2751
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_4ede2504:

    # "But that {i}can’t{/i} be right."
    "但那肯定{i}不對{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2758
translate Tchinese medicinemissing_9e1552dc:

    # "No, that can’t be it."
    "不，肯定不對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2772
translate Tchinese medicinetimeout_3cdf708a:

    # "I hear Ralph grunt on the ground."
    "Ralph倒在地上悶哼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2773
translate Tchinese medicinetimeout_2fb00ad9:

    # "I’m wasting time here."
    "我這是在浪費時間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2776
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9b2c9c08:

    # m "\"Ralph.\""
    m "Ralph"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2777
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c9cc367:

    # "I crouch down with the medicine in my hand."
    "我手拿著藥蹲下來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2779
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c8363327:

    # "He rouses for a moment, looks at me with bleary eyes."
    "他暫時醒了過來，朦朧地望著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2781
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e377e2c8:

    # "He sees the jar in my hand and opens his mouth."
    "看見我手裡的罐子，便張開嘴巴。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2783
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ffb5731c:

    # "I prop him up with my arm."
    "我用手臂扶起他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2785
translate Tchinese medicinedone_90c15ebd:

    # "He struggles to get it down."
    "他使勁嚥了下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2787
translate Tchinese medicinedone_50d3e6a2:

    # "It doesn’t seem pleasant."
    "看來味道不好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2789
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ed85293:

    # "But he finishes."
    "但他全吞了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2791
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bfa50ddb:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}Ugh.\""
    ra "{cps=25}嘔呃……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2793
translate Tchinese medicinedone_24644ecb:

    # m "\"Feeling any better?\""
    m "感覺好點了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2795
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7fdf058b:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}The fuck would I be feeling better?\""
    ra "{cps=25}這他媽有可能嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2797
translate Tchinese medicinedone_378a0851:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}Do you know how long this takes to work?\""
    ra "{cps=25}你知不知道這要多久才會生效？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2799
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7400298c:

    # "He certainly sounds better."
    "聽起來確實已經好多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2801
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f3bb7a1d:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}Don’t waste any more of your time on me.\""
    ra "{cps=25}別在我身上浪費時間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2803
translate Tchinese medicinedone_410a264b:

    # ra "\"{cps=25}Go help the others.\""
    ra "{cps=25}去救其他人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2809
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f363629d:

    # "Jim and Neil are both easy enough to medicate."
    "餵Jim和Neil服藥都很輕鬆。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2811
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48438c92:

    # "They cooperate with me and drink."
    "他們配合我喝了下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2813
translate Tchinese medicinedone_73eab177:

    # "For Jim it goes down easy."
    "Jim喝得很順。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2815
translate Tchinese medicinedone_92c66f0e:

    # "Neil does his best, but sputters."
    "Neil盡力了，但還是被嗆到。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2817
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b473f725:

    # "Now just one left."
    "只剩一個人了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2819
translate Tchinese medicinedone_90cd340b:

    # m "\"Where’s Murdoch?\""
    m "Murdoch在哪？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2821
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5fc25144:

    # "I don’t know why I expect anyone to answer me."
    "我不知道為什麼會期望有人回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2823
translate Tchinese medicinedone_db7e05f9:

    # "They’re all out of it."
    "他們都神志不清。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2825
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aecc91e1:

    # "I think I saw him lying at the front."
    "我記得他是躺在前面。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2827
translate Tchinese medicinedone_178f32e5:

    # "But I hear something at the back of the room."
    "但房間深處有聲音傳來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2829
translate Tchinese medicinedone_be800d9e:

    # "He’s there."
    "他就在那裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2831
translate Tchinese medicinedone_db6b5911:

    # "Lying over the trap door."
    "躺在活板門前。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2833
translate Tchinese medicinedone_38a8bd72:

    # "Staring at the eye."
    "盯著那隻眼睛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2835
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc65449b:

    # "He wasn’t passed out like the others?"
    "他沒像其他人那樣昏睡嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2837
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8998a122:

    # "I wonder why."
    "真令人在意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2839
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a6ba21f:

    # m "\"Murdoch, sit up.\""
    m "Murdoch，坐起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2841
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e3c04568:

    # m "\"I want you to drink this.\""
    m "把這個喝下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2843
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8c82d21a:

    # "He doesn’t answer me."
    "他沒回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2845
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2cd5ad3b:

    # m "\"Hey.\""
    m "喂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2847
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e4ff1d42:

    # m "\"I’m talking to you.\""
    m "我跟你說話呢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2849
translate Tchinese medicinedone_96d1c534:

    # "He still doesn’t answer."
    "他還是不回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2851
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e3f3f552:

    # "I kneel down and put my hand on his back."
    "我跪下把手搭上他的背。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2853
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fbdfaccf:

    # "He flinches."
    "他抖了一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2855
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3153558f:

    # "I suddenly realize that he was sleeping with his eyes open."
    "我這才意識到，他是在睜著眼睛睡覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2857
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd46756c:

    # "That doesn’t seem natural."
    "看著很不自然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2859
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0d8629d6:

    # "But that don’t matter right now."
    "但這不是重點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2861
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7933a732:

    # m "\"I’m flipping you over.\""
    m "我先把你翻過來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2863
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ba21d36:

    # "He doesn’t really get to argue about it."
    "他沒能抗議。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2865
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f022abdf:

    # "He looks up at me, supine on the floor."
    "他癱倒在地板上，抬頭看我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2867
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d379770f:

    # "I kneel down and let his head rest on my arm, bending him upward."
    "我跪下讓他的頭靠在我手臂上，好把他撐起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2869
translate Tchinese medicinedone_482c6cf7:

    # m "\"You need to drink this.\""
    m "你要把這個喝下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2871
translate Tchinese medicinedone_adc3e2cf:

    # "He nods."
    "他點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2873
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a87adab4:

    # "He’s the one who struggles most to get it down."
    "他是吞得最辛苦的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2875
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d88fdc8d:

    # "But I make sure he does."
    "但我還是確保他喝下去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2877
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2035f6d3:

    # "I want to ask him why he drank the water."
    "我很想問他為什麼喝了那些水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2879
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f0aaef3a:

    # "But not now."
    "但現在不是時候。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2881
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d6909fde:

    # "Ralph said they need time."
    "Ralph說過他們需要時間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2883
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a7e20dbc:

    # "I’m worried about them."
    "我很擔心他們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2885
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1fe59b50:

    # "Worried about the girls too."
    "也擔心那些女孩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2887
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e6874920:

    # "I haven’t heard anybody for a good while."
    "我有好一陣子沒聽見任何動靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2889
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cea37e98:

    # "But when I check the watch on Jim’s wrist I can see how late it is."
    "但一查看Jim手腕上的錶，才發現時間已經很晚了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2891
translate Tchinese medicinedone_07f2ea0b:

    # "They probably found somewhere to sleep."
    "她們大概已經找到地方睡覺了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2893
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fa91ff98:

    # "Or to hide, if they heard somebody."
    "或者聽見動靜就躲了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2895
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fab6ee47:

    # "I’m not sure what to do with myself to pass the time, because I can’t be the one to go to sleep."
    "我不知道該做什麼來打發時間，畢竟我不能睡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2897
translate Tchinese medicinedone_91ef7fbe:

    # "I’m worried that I haven’t heard any noises that could sound like Harlan."
    "沒聽見任何像是Harlan發出的聲響，讓我很擔心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2899
translate Tchinese medicinedone_40a120d6:

    # "But I’m growing more confident that he isn’t here any more."
    "但我越來越確信他已經不在這了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2901
translate Tchinese medicinedone_32b909da:

    # "I feel my body go slightly numb as my eyelids droop."
    "我感覺眼皮下垂，身體微微發麻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2903
translate Tchinese medicinedone_07cc803e:

    # "It feels like hours have gone by but it’s hard to tell how much time has actually passed."
    "感覺已經過了好幾個小時，但很難確定實際過了多久。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2904
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d568d45a:

    # "I don’t hear anything."
    "我什麼都沒聽見。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2905
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5dc7ab6a:

    # "No tossing or turning."
    "沒人翻身。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2906
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1feeb290:

    # "No mumbling."
    "沒人出聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2907
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7a60b823:

    # "Something’s wrong."
    "不對勁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2910
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9b2c9c08_1:

    # m "\"Ralph.\""
    m "Ralph。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2911
translate Tchinese medicinedone_53221fcf:

    # "I crouch down and put my paw on the rat’s shoulder."
    "我蹲下來用手搭著老鼠肩膀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2912
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6c195dec:

    # "He stirs a bit, but not much."
    "他有一點動作，但不大。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2913
translate Tchinese medicinedone_82919217:

    # m "\"Hey come on.\""
    m "喂，醒醒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2914
translate Tchinese medicinedone_18c83578:

    # "I shake his shoulder this time."
    "我搖晃他的肩膀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2915
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6d4e0170:

    # m "\"You gotta wake up.\""
    m "你快醒醒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2916
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d5f7d228:

    # "His head rolls a bit and before he looks up at me."
    "他的頭微微轉動，然後抬起看向我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2917
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35966b0f:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}What do you need?\""
    ra "{cps=18}找我幹嘛？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2918
translate Tchinese medicinedone_79cf6714:

    # m "\"Jesus.\""
    m "天啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2920
translate Tchinese medicinedone_30df6b95:

    # m "\"You sound a lot worse.\""
    m "你氣色糟多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2922
translate Tchinese medicinedone_18efe66f:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}You tend to get worse with these things before you get better.\""
    ra "{cps=18}這些症狀通常會先惡化才好轉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2924
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19861e57:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}Though admittedly I do feel pretty bad.\""
    ra "{cps=18}但我的確非常不舒服。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2926
translate Tchinese medicinedone_76403b73:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}Did you follow my instructions?\""
    ra "{cps=18}我的指示你都照辦了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2928
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e2d30ef3:

    # m "\"Yes?\""
    m "對呀？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2930
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52f0ede0:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}I mean with the dosages...\""
    ra "{cps=18}我是指劑量……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2932
translate Tchinese medicinedone_04e830f5:

    # m "\"Obviously.\""
    m "那還用說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2934
translate Tchinese medicinedone_24e515bb:

    # m "\"What else would you be fuckin’ talking about?\""
    m "不然你指的還能是什麼鬼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2936
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e450a868:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}...if I’m this bad off, you should definitely check the others.\""
    ra "{cps=18}……連我都這麼糟了，你最好去看看其他人吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2938
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e3e392a0:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}You still have doses?\""
    ra "{cps=18}劑量還有剩嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2940
translate Tchinese medicinedone_151eb8b3:

    # m "\"Yeah, I still have doses Ralph.\""
    m "對，還有，Ralph。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2942
translate Tchinese medicinedone_62b27166:

    # m "\"I thought we were supposed to stagger them.\""
    m "你說要錯開時間給的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2944
translate Tchinese medicinedone_51d083d5:

    # ra "\"{cps=18}Just go ahead and do a second dose.\""
    ra "{cps=18}直接給第二劑吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2950
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7e18e2d9:

    # "I go back to the rooms."
    "我回到房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2952
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d205fe44:

    # "Jim is still moving, but barely."
    "Jim還有動作，但很微弱。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2954
translate Tchinese medicinedone_13415379:

    # "Neil’s breast rises, but goes down with a wheeze each time."
    "Neil的胸膛每次起伏都伴隨著勉強的喘息。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2956
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a9dce714:

    # "Murdoch isn’t moving."
    "Murdoch一動也不動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2958
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d44e2ba3:

    # "I check his pulse."
    "我檢查他的脈搏。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2960
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7675607f:

    # "I can’t tell if I’m feeling his or feeling mine."
    "分不清是他的還是我的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2962
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8bf62828:

    # "He’s warm but he doesn’t look like he’s breathing."
    "他還有體溫，但好像沒氣息了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2964
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b47bd00c:

    # "I lift his head and try to open his jaw but it’s clenched shut."
    "我抬起他的頭想撬開他的下巴，但嘴緊閉著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2966
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fb6e33a2:

    # "Shit."
    "我操。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2968
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ac040100:

    # "Shit shit shit."
    "我操我操我操。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2970
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ba48e4a:

    # "I’m in over my head."
    "我已經應付不來了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2972
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f71c1157:

    # "I’m not a doctor."
    "我不是醫生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2974
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3cda91f2:

    # "I’ve gotta drag him out to Ralph."
    "得把他拖去給Ralph看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2976
translate Tchinese medicinedone_726c7bab:

    # "If anybody knows what to do, it’s him."
    "現在只有他有辦法了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2978
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd8d516a:

    # "He feels heavier than before but I’m still able to move him."
    "他感覺比之前更重，但我還是能搬動他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2982
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c1c8ceb5:

    # "Ralph rouses again, {nw}"
    "Ralph又醒來了，{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2984
translate Tchinese medicinedone_da56bc31:

    # extend "the sobers up when he sees what I’m doing."
    extend "在看到我的舉動後便徹底清醒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2986
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ceb30b1b:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}What are you doing?\""
    ra "{cps=30}你在幹嘛？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2988
translate Tchinese medicinedone_684647d3:

    # m "\"What’s it look like?\""
    m "看起來像在幹嘛？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2990
translate Tchinese medicinedone_05faa4a3:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}Why are you dragging him around?!\""
    ra "{cps=30}你為什麼要拖著他！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2992
translate Tchinese medicinedone_249899c6:

    # m "\"Because his mouth is clenched shut!\""
    m "他嘴巴閉得很緊！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2994
translate Tchinese medicinedone_221cbb86:

    # m "\"I need help!\""
    m "來幫忙！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2996
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d86429b6:

    # "The rate lurches forward and grabs his wrist."
    "老鼠衝向前，抓住他的手腕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:2998
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9b76db96:

    # "He drops it with a flinch."
    "驚愕地鬆開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3000
translate Tchinese medicinedone_be626d86:

    # "He hisses at me through his teeth."
    "他咬牙對我嘶聲說："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3002
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a38ffe2f:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}His heart isn’t beating!\""
    ra "{cps=30}他心跳沒了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3004
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19d285ce:

    # m "\"The fuck do you mean?\""
    m "這他媽什麼意思？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3006
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd63ad8e:

    # m "\"His skin is still warm?\""
    m "他身體還是溫的啊？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3008
translate Tchinese medicinedone_63f658c2:

    # ra "\"{cps=30}That doesn’t mean shit!\""
    ra "{cps=30}那有個屁用！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3010
translate Tchinese medicinedone_622750e4:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}MOVE!\""
    ra "{cps=35}{b}閃邊去！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3012
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ce27b449:

    # "The rat rips open his shirt."
    "老鼠撕開他的襯衫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3014
translate Tchinese medicinedone_62061521:

    # "He pushes his hands down on the fox’s chest."
    "雙手按在狐狸的胸口上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3016
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c9b7c95:

    # "He pushes down until I hear a crunch."
    "下壓到一陣碎裂聲傳出。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3018
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9bc0475a:

    # m "\"You’re breaking his bones!\""
    m "你弄斷他的骨頭了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3021
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b5507aa1:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}I HAVE TO, he has a HEART FAILURE!\""
    ra "{cps=35}{b}不這樣不行，他心臟衰竭了！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3023
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b21ddd59:

    # "This isn’t my fault."
    這不是我的錯。""

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3025
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e31d82db:

    # "He took the poison, he {i}knew{/i} it was poison."
    "毒是他自己喝的；他{i}知道{/i}那是毒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3027
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9f49e050:

    # "Was that even the right antidote?"
    "解藥本身是正確的嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3029
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b47a58c2:

    # "Ralph keeps pushing."
    "Ralph繼續按壓。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3031
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5e0f43a3:

    # "Murdoch still isn’t moving."
    "Murdoch還是一動不動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3032
translate Tchinese medicinedone_99d5b224:

    # "He keeps going but nothing changes."
    "他努力不懈，但徒勞無功。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3034
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b22317c4:

    # "I keep staring at the fox’s claws, looking for some sort of movement."
    "我一直盯著狐狸的爪，希望能見到什麼動靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3036
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cbd55f2e:

    # "If there’s anybody who could do this, it’s got to be Ralph."
    "現在只有Ralph能救他了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3038
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9979a58c:

    # "Right?"
    "沒錯吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3040
translate Tchinese medicinedone_221adfff:

    # "I don’t know what to do."
    "我不知道該如何是好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3042
translate Tchinese medicinedone_091aa370:

    # "Then the worst thing possible happens."
    "然後最糟糕的事發生了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3044
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2b46220d:

    # "I hear something else up the front corridor."
    "我聽見前方走廊有其他聲響。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3046
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d106b747:

    # "First it sounds like a door opening."
    "起先是開門聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3048
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2419f7a0:

    # "Now I hear footsteps."
    "現在是腳步聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3050
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ac14fe74:

    # "I don’t want to leave them here."
    "我不想把他們丟在這。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3052
translate Tchinese medicinedone_585948f9:

    # "But Ralph can’t stop what he’s doing."
    "但Ralph現在不能停下急救。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3054
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5fa21212:

    # "Not that it looks to be working."
    "雖然似乎沒有作用。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3056
translate Tchinese medicinedone_43c6f57c:

    # "Do I go up and stop them?"
    "我要過去阻止他們嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3058
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4333898a:

    # "Or do sit back and let them come to me."
    "還是坐在這裡等他們過來？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3060
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f142f221:

    # "If it’s Harlan I don’t have to hesitate."
    "如果是Harlan，就不必猶豫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3062
translate Tchinese medicinedone_32f22612:

    # "If it’s somebody else I can’t help them if I’m caught."
    "如果是其他人，我先被發現的話就幫不上忙了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3064
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cdc2b36c:

    # "So I stand up."
    "於是我站起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3066
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc4cb4ec:

    # "I step back."
    "往後退。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3068
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f0339eaf:

    # "Ralph looks up at me."
    "Ralph抬頭看我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3070
translate Tchinese medicinedone_56013837:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}Where do you think you’re going?!\""
    ra "{cps=35}你這是要去哪！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3072
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a637cc59:

    # "I hold up a digit to my snout, but that just prompts a look of rage in his eyes."
    "我在嘴邊豎起一根手指，但這只激起了他眼中的怒火。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3074
translate Tchinese medicinedone_20dfbba1:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}I said where are you {i}going?{/i}\""
    ra "{cps=35}我問你要去{i}哪裡{/i}？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3076
translate Tchinese medicinedone_57918af0:

    # grunk "\"Who’s there?\""
    grunk "什麼人？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3078
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7408578f:

    # "All of the blood drains out of Ralph’s face as he looks behind him."
    "Ralph看向身後，臉上血色盡失。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3080
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9389b351:

    # "I keep stepping back."
    "我繼續後退。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3082
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ac4c6dd3:

    # "I’m behind the door that leads to the exit."
    "退到通往出口的門後面。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3084
translate Tchinese medicinedone_898369fd:

    # grunk "\"What are you doing here?\""
    grunk "你在這裡做什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3086
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0d4f43c9:

    # "I don’t hear Ralph respond immediately."
    "Ralph沒有馬上回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3088
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86126650:

    # grunk "\"What is {i}he{/i} doing here?\""
    grunk "{i}他{/i}怎麼在這裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3090
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e20667a2:

    # grunk "\"Why is he curled up like that, on the floor!\""
    grunk "他怎麼倒在地上！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3092
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6526698e:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}Ma’am?\""
    ra "{cps=35}夫人？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3094
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1113162b:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}He’s sick.\""
    ra "{cps=35}他身體出問題了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3096
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52a604a5:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}I’m doing my best to help him!\""
    ra "{cps=35}我正在盡力幫他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3098
translate Tchinese medicinedone_78da7e9f:

    # grunk "\"Why would he be sick?\""
    grunk "他身體為什麼會出問題？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3100
translate Tchinese medicinedone_263747fe:

    # grunk "\"What have you done to him?\""
    grunk "你對他做了什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3102
translate Tchinese medicinedone_47667f9f:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}Please!\""
    ra "{cps=35}拜託！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3104
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cdf4ae4c:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}Just TRUST ME!\""
    ra "{cps=35}{b}相信我！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3106
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c0d88cc7:

    # grunk "\"His heart’s not beating.\""
    grunk "他心臟沒在跳了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3108
translate Tchinese medicinedone_27598430:

    # grunk "\"Oh my God!\""
    grunk "我的天啊！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3110
translate Tchinese medicinedone_496644e1:

    # grunk "\"He’s dead!\""
    grunk "他死了！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3112
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fbdd3f13:

    # ra "\"{cps=35}I can bring him ba--\""
    ra "{cps=35}我可以把他救——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3114
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9fa7567:

    # "I hear a gun shot."
    "槍聲響起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3116
translate Tchinese medicinedone_78713c03:

    # "I cover my mouth as I keep backing away."
    "我捂住嘴巴繼續後退。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3118
translate Tchinese medicinedone_95997df7:

    # "Oh my god."
    "我的天啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3120
translate Tchinese medicinedone_44d0ee47:

    # "She shot him."
    "她把他射死了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3122
translate Tchinese medicinedone_32c7b0e6:

    # "Now nobody’s able to help."
    "現在沒人能幫忙了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3124
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2fece98c:

    # "Why did I wait to see?"
    "我為什麼選擇等著？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3126
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6e6f5cf6:

    # "I should have just said something!"
    "早知道就該直接開口的！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3128
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f24bbc32:

    # "I feel the tears rolling down my cheeks but I’m not making any sounds."
    "我感覺眼淚滑下臉頰，卻沒有發出任何動靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3130
translate Tchinese medicinedone_993078d2:

    # "What about the others?"
    "其他人呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3132
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2fede503:

    # "If the medicine didn’t work on Murdoch, it wouldn’t work on the other men, would it?"
    "如果藥對Murdoch沒效，對其他男的應該也沒效吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3134
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d791d1d9:

    # "Are they all going to die down here?"
    "他們都會死在這裡嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3136
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e967e3d4:

    # "I tried to help them."
    "我嘗試過幫助他們了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3138
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9dc2c4f4:

    # "But it just made everything worse."
    "但只是讓一切惡化。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3140
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9da92f26:

    # "Why didn’t I just say something about the water?"
    "我怎麼就不直接說那水有問題？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3142
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d8f79530:

    # "They might have listened."
    "他們或許會聽。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3144
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aa09b337:

    # no "\"They wouldn’t have.\""
    no_TW "他們不會聽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3146
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe3a4cb8:

    # no "\"There is no way off the path.\""
    no_TW "這條路沒有出口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3148
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35a3b3e5:

    # no "\"No more chances.\""
    no_TW "沒有其他機會了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3150
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc4d8771:

    # no "\"Your only way forward is to run.\""
    no_TW "你唯一的前進方式就是跑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3152
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48879fe9:

    # no "\"Run, and don’t stop.\""
    no_TW "跑，不要停。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3154
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0f64f35f:

    # no "\"Run until your footprints bleed.\""
    no_TW "跑到腳印渗血。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3156
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d14f9955:

    # no "\"The moment you stop is when I’ll be there.\""
    no_TW "你一停下，我就會現身。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3158
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5c3c719:

    # "Somebody’s sobbing."
    "有人在啜泣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3160
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a1626f9:

    # "But somebody else is laughing."
    "但也有人在笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3162
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2f35a5cf:

    # "Who could be doing that?"
    "誰能笑得出來？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3164
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1eb1db7d:

    # "Who the fuck would be doing that?"
    "誰他媽的在笑？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3166
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f01ec59:

    # "I have to get out."
    "我必須出去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3168
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f009988:

    # "I don’t care how noisy I am."
    "我不在乎發出多大動靜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3170
translate Tchinese medicinedone_95ba29e0:

    # "I don’t care who sees me or calls my name."
    "我不在乎誰被誰看見或呼喚。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3172
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f01ec59_1:

    # "I have to get out."
    "我必須出去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3175
translate Tchinese medicinedone_02221846:

    # "I storm up the stairs."
    "衝上樓梯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3177
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9c5ea6db:

    # "Then I remember that it’s locked."
    "才想起來門是鎖著的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3179
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8d89ccbe:

    # "I can’t get out."
    "我出不去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3181
translate Tchinese medicinedone_56cff30f:

    # "I can’t--"
    "我逃不——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3183
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c00ad8d1:

    # "There’s another sound behind me."
    "身後傳來另一道聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3185
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9fc4acb4:

    # "Then I feel the pain before I hear the popping sound."
    "我先是感覺到痛，才聽見炸裂聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3187
translate Tchinese medicinedone_62cb7084:

    # "I can’t breathe."
    "我沒法呼吸了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3189
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c95213f7:

    # "Liquid gushes around my throat."
    "液體從喉嚨湧出。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3191
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e69689c0:

    # "Red soaks into my hands, and I fall down the stairs."
    "鮮紅染透雙手，然後跌下樓梯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3193
translate Tchinese medicinedone_94dc0958:

    # "It hurts."
    "好痛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3195
translate Tchinese medicinedone_573ff060:

    # "It hurts so bad."
    "好她媽痛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3197
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0153d8e8:

    # "I was told once before by my uncle that when you begin to die, things start to go numb."
    "我叔叔以前跟我說過，人快死掉的時候，感覺會逐漸麻木。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3199
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8413f7ee:

    # "But this is getting worse."
    "但我現在卻越來越痛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3201
translate Tchinese medicinedone_78b230e3:

    # "The bullet feels like a razor blade in my throat, rawing it from the inside out."
    "子彈像一把剃刀，把喉嚨從內切到外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3203
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5646154:

    # "I look around myself."
    "我環顧四周。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3205
translate Tchinese medicinedone_06ea2e43:

    # "I’m in the basement."
    "我在地下室。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3207
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc31a3b7:

    # "I try to make out the killer, just to make sure I know who did it before I go."
    "我試圖看清兇手，只想在死前知道是誰幹的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3209
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c77f20c6:

    # "But I don’t see anybody with a gun."
    "但沒看到拿槍的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3211
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dcb5a3d6:

    # "I just see that old furnace."
    "只看見那老舊的爐子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3213
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ebac87ca:

    # "The lid begins to open."
    "爐蓋正在開啟。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3215
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a2022224:

    # "Something’s crawling out of it."
    "有東西從裡面爬出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3217
translate Tchinese medicinedone_96af48d7:

    # "Black bodies. Charred to bone. Crawing out and over each other."
    "一堆燒成枯骨的漆黑軀體。彼此重疊爬行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3219
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f0029e4:

    # "There’s no eyes in their sockets."
    "眼窩裡沒有眼珠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3221
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f6b4b1e8:

    # "They move together, like one living thing."
    "一起移動，像一個活物。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3223
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c1d3294a:

    # "Then their hands are all over me."
    "然後伸手搭在我全身上下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3225
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e3ac9d1f:

    # "I can only keep them away with one hand because the other is on my throat."
    "我只有一隻手能抵抗，因為另一隻還要壓著喉嚨。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3227
translate Tchinese medicinedone_58a1348a:

    # "But they’re dragging me now."
    "但現在正被他們拖走。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3229
translate Tchinese medicinedone_af334661:

    # "I don’t want to go there."
    "我不想去那裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3231
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c8e6e97c:

    # "I don’t want go {i}there.{/i}"
    "我不想去{i}那裡{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3237
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9f8eed1e:

    # "But then somebody starts to retch."
    "但接著有人開始乾嘔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3239
translate Tchinese medicinedone_73cc5b21:

    # "It seems to be Murdoch judging by the sound of it."
    "聽聲音應該是Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3241
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d6a54717:

    # "Ralph said that was a good thing, I think."
    "Ralph說過那是好事，我記得。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3243
translate Tchinese medicinedone_41ccac9f:

    # "I go to fetch the other bottle of medicine."
    "我去拿另一瓶藥。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3245
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a5873ded:

    # "But then somebody grabs my sleeve."
    "但有人抓住我的袖子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3247
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e416dca1:

    # mu "\"Hey.\""
    mu "嘿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3249
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a16b9def:

    # m "\"Murdoch?\""
    m "Murdoch？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3251
translate Tchinese medicinedone_144dfc7f:

    # m "\"You’re right here?\""
    m "你人在這？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3253
translate Tchinese medicinedone_61e3bea2:

    # mu "\"Should I not be?\""
    mu "我不該在這嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3255
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5d9ddbe5:

    # m "\"I thought that was you over there in the corner.\""
    m "我以為角落那個人是你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3257
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bd9265f1:

    # mu "\"Jim and I probably sound fairly similar when we throw up.\""
    mu "我和Jim嘔吐的聲音大概差不多。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3259
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6032bfdd:

    # m "\"Congratulations.\""
    m "那恭喜你喔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3261
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ab58df91:

    # mu "\"It’s the muzzle shape.\""
    mu "是吻部形狀的關係。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3263
translate Tchinese medicinedone_98ad23b0:

    # m "\"You’re supposed to be throwing up too.\""
    m "你也應該要吐才對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3265
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a9b2970a:

    # mu "\"I already did.\""
    mu "我已經吐過了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3267
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e96ded36:

    # mu "\"You slept through it.\""
    mu "只是你還在睡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3269
translate Tchinese medicinedone_73341dc1:

    # m "\"No, that’s no good.\""
    m "不行，這下糟了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3271
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52f0e192:

    # m "\"Why didn’t you wake me?\""
    m "你怎麼沒叫醒我？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3273
translate Tchinese medicinedone_104cdb72:

    # mu "\"You looked like you really needed the sleep.\""
    mu "你看上去真的很需要睡眠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3275
translate Tchinese medicinedone_018d675d:

    # m "\"No...\""
    m "不行……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3276
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f04b422f:

    # m "\"If you threw up your medicine, that’s when you’re supposed to get more.\""
    m "如果你把藥吐出來了，就該再喝一次。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3278
translate Tchinese medicinedone_daa9ea78:

    # mu "\"I don’t feel that bad.\""
    mu "我感覺沒那麼糟。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3280
translate Tchinese medicinedone_104c0519:

    # m "\"I don’t care.\""
    m "我不管。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3281
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5f324de1:

    # m "\"There were instructions.\""
    m "我被吩咐過了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3282
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aef821ed:

    # m "\"You’re getting more medicine.\""
    m "你還要再喝藥。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3284
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a0b56e9:

    # "Murdoch looks like he’s about to say something but I don’t let him."
    "Murdoch似乎想說什麼，但我沒讓他開口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3286
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3f7d1569:

    # "I’m getting up."
    "我站起身子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3288
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aa1acf4e:

    # "Going to the door."
    "走向門口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3290
translate Tchinese medicinedone_627dbdf8:

    # "He hooks his arm around mine."
    "他用手臂勾住我的手。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3292
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a28bc336:

    # mu "\"Can’t you just sit with me for a moment?\""
    mu "你就不能陪我坐一下嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3294
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c651d0c8:

    # m "\"No.\""
    m "不能。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3296
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c6209c7:

    # m "\"Medicine.\""
    m "藥。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3298
translate Tchinese medicinedone_60af0abe:

    # "He doesn’t seem happy with my answer, but that’s too damn bad."
    "我的回答讓他不太高興，但這可由不得他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3302
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc51ad8a:

    # "It makes him follow me out into the hall and back into the chamber with all of the medicine."
    "於是他跟著我來到走廊上，回到放藥的房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3304
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aabaf3f1:

    # "I don’t think he should be walking around right now, but it doesn’t matter."
    "我感覺他現在不該走動，但無所謂了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3306
translate Tchinese medicinedone_55c95231:

    # "He’s learning over the table, barely able to keep himself up now."
    "他靠在桌子上，勉強撐起自己。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3308
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d4e66ba0:

    # "He’s obviously still not okay."
    "他狀況明顯還是很差。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3310
translate Tchinese medicinedone_68e2feaf:

    # "So I’m going to make him drink this."
    "所以我一定要讓他喝下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3312
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f5fc617:

    # m "\"Open your mouth.\""
    m "張嘴。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3314
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d44f3933:

    # mu "\"Okay.\""
    mu "好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3316
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a14374b2:

    # "I shove it in his mouth."
    "我把藥灌進他嘴裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3318
translate Tchinese medicinedone_27441404:

    # m "\"Take it.\""
    m "喝了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3319
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1e4da550:

    # "He cringes and nods."
    "他皺著臉點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3321
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3ba0343d:

    # m "\"Swallow.\""
    m "吞下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3323
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3ead094b:

    # "I pull back his head."
    "我把他的頭向後拉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3325
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a394e6d:

    # "A little forcefully."
    "稍微用力了點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3327
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ff5d26f:

    # "It might be because I’m a little angry with him."
    "可能是因為我有點生他的氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3329
translate Tchinese medicinedone_908da7f4:

    # "But holding him this close sends chills up my back."
    "但這樣緊抱著他讓我背脊發麻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3331
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0234ca4a:

    # "It’s a nice feeling."
    "感覺真棒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3333
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e7e02088:

    # "I don’t want to lose it."
    "我不想失去這種感覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3335
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0f4e773:

    # "How dare he do this to me?"
    "他怎麼敢這樣對我？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3337
translate Tchinese medicinedone_551c4726:

    # "His life isn’t just his anymore."
    "他的命已經不只屬於他自己了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3339
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fbbdac97:

    # "It’s mine now too."
    "現在也是我的了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3341
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ae5fb0c0:

    # "At least this time getting the medicine down is a little easier."
    "好歹這次餵藥比較順利。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3343
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5006f4b:

    # "I don’t let him take the jar from his muzzle until he’s swallowed it all."
    "直到他全嚥下去，我都沒讓他把罐子移開嘴邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3345
translate Tchinese medicinedone_02ce4d7f:

    # m "\"You done yet?\""
    m "全吞了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3347
translate Tchinese medicinedone_adc3e2cf_1:

    # "He nods."
    "他點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3349
translate Tchinese medicinedone_02784371:

    # m "\"Good.\""
    m "很好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3351
translate Tchinese medicinedone_13aeabcb:

    # m "\"Now why the hell did you drink Harlan’s water?\""
    m "現在告訴我，你他媽為什麼要喝Harlan給的水？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3353
translate Tchinese medicinedone_128fa6ff:

    # "He doesn’t answer immediately."
    "他沒有馬上回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3355
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4e3ede91:

    # m "\"You knew he was poisoning us, didn’t you?\""
    m "你知道他想給我們下毒，對不對？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3357
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cb1589c5:

    # mu "\"Yes, but I knew that {i}you{/i} knew.\""
    mu "對，但我知道{i}你{/i} 知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3359
translate Tchinese medicinedone_57b9a512:

    # m "\"But you weren’t sure.\""
    m "這你又不能確定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3361
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b666b328:

    # mu "\"I was pretty sure.\""
    mu "我很確定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3363
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4a661da4:

    # mu "\"Sure enough that Ralph wouldn’t drink either.\""
    mu "還確信Ralph也不會喝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3365
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c793f27:

    # m "\"Ralph drank.\""
    m "Ralph喝下去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3367
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86814205:

    # mu "\"...What?\""
    mu "……什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3369
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9801086d:

    # m "\"He knew it was poison too, but Harlan watched him.\""
    m "他也知道那是毒，但Harlan死盯著他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3371
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c37cea37:

    # m "\"He ended up swallowing some too before he could spit.\""
    m "他最後還是吞了一些下去，沒能全吐出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3373
translate Tchinese medicinedone_662ff8b6:

    # "He looks embarrassed."
    "他一臉尷尬。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3375
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ff08fca5:

    # mu "\"I wouldn’t have swallowed if I knew that would happen.\""
    mu "早知道會這樣，我就不會吞下去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3377
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ea5394c0:

    # m "\"So why did you?\""
    m "所以你到底為什麼要喝？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3379
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a620e554:

    # "The fox crosses his arms and leans against the wall, letting his tail wrap around him."
    "狐狸雙手抱胸靠在牆上，尾巴纏住自己。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3381
translate Tchinese medicinedone_03753858:

    # mu "\"A couple of reasons.\""
    mu "有幾個理由。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3383
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cea778b1:

    # m "\"...Like?\""
    m "……比如說？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3385
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b94b4871:

    # "He waits a moment to speak again."
    "他等了一下才再次開口："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3387
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3ec3ae53:

    # mu "\"I wanted to let him see that I swallowed, so he would get confident.\""
    mu "讓他看到我吞下去，就能滿足他的自信。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3389
translate Tchinese medicinedone_54de6214:

    # m "\"...By drinkin’ something that {i}could have killed you.{/i}\""
    m "……但喝了{i}可能會死{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3391
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d15e902a:

    # m "\"Might {i}still{/i} kill you if Ralph is wrong about the kind of poison it was.\""
    m "要是Ralph猜錯了毒的種類，你可能{i}還是要死{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3393
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86c53861:

    # mu "\"If Ralph got a taste, I don’t think he’d be wrong.\""
    mu "Ralph都嚐到味了，應該不至於會猜錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3395
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d628dbde:

    # m "\"So why else?\""
    m "那其他理由呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3397
translate Tchinese medicinedone_82cb88af:

    # m "\"What are you leaving out?\""
    m "你還隱瞞了什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3399
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fa27de0d:

    # mu "\"...I wanted to test the effects down here.\""
    mu "……我想在這裡測試效果。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3401
translate Tchinese medicinedone_051d4576:

    # m "\"Of course you did.\""
    m "我就知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3403
translate Tchinese medicinedone_316a49fb:

    # mu "\"We know there’s something to that.\""
    mu "我們都知道這其中有玄機。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3405
translate Tchinese medicinedone_914460d6:

    # m "\"...Do we?\""
    m "……有嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3407
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0448dea:

    # mu "\"Yes!\""
    mu "當然囉！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3409
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0ed2c98:

    # mu "\"If we alter ourselves, it can’t alter us!\""
    mu "只要改變自己，它就動不了我們！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3411
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c80b7db1:

    # m "\"Or...\""
    m "或是說……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3413
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc2435b4:

    # mu "\"Or what?\""
    mu "或什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3415
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dd49cd0e:

    # m "\"It was tricking you into thinking that’s how it worked, so you’d willingly drink poison.\""
    m "是它騙你以為這樣有效，然後你就會自願服毒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3417
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc2a4bd4:

    # m "\"Whatever’s here wants you dead.\""
    m "這裡的東西想要你死。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3419
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3c36a00c:

    # mu "\"Why?\""
    mu "為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3421
translate Tchinese medicinedone_14773c39:

    # m "\"I don’t know.\""
    m "我哪知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3424
translate Tchinese medicinedone_413d2295:

    # alunk "\"What are you doing here?\""
    alunk "你們來這裡做什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3426
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7eb19165:

    # "Both of us freeze."
    "我們兩個都僵住了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3434
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cfdc2507:

    # "Murdoch’s father is standing in the cellar doorway."
    "Murdoch的父親就站在地下室門口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3435
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7644b0b0:

    # "He has a gun and he’s pointing it at both of us."
    "他拿著一把槍，指著我們兩個。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3437
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c815a621:

    # mu "\"Father?\""
    mu "父親？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3439
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aded6d56:

    # mu "\"What are you doing her--\""
    mu "你怎麼會在——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3441
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f625b185:

    # al "\"Don’t play stupid, Murdy.\""
    al "別裝傻了，Murdy。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3444
translate Tchinese medicinedone_945a3ef3:

    # al "\"This a locked room.\""
    al "這房間上了鎖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3448
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6ea9169f:

    # al "\"Only I and your mother knew the code.\""
    al "只有我和你媽知道密碼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3450
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a0790f5:

    # mu "\"Then why was there another man in here?\""
    mu "那怎麼還有另一個男人在？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3451
translate Tchinese medicinedone_91b247f6:

    # "Alfred looks genuinely surprised."
    "Alfred似乎真的很訝異。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3453
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ac8cfa4d:

    # al "\"There shouldn’t be.\""
    al "不應該啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3456
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e40fe68c:

    # mu "\"Harlan Perkins.\""
    mu "Harlan Perkins。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3457
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7427a444:

    # mu "\"The bartender from the Hip.\""
    mu "Hip的酒保。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3459
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c8883100:

    # al "\"Oh.\""
    al "喔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3463
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4eb4358c:

    # al "\"Him.\""
    al "是他啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3465
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e17b329e:

    # mu "\"Dad, what do you mean {i}him?{/i}\""
    mu "爸，你知道{i}他{/i}？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3467
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f3ba9320:

    # al "\"If he was here, he wasn’t supposed to be.\""
    al "他確實不該出現在這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3470
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7f4f6bef:

    # al "\"He has an arrangement with your mother and I.\""
    al "我和你媽跟他之間有協議。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3473
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8e292006:

    # al "\"But this was supposed to be off limits.\""
    al "但他是不准來這裡的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3475
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1d3decbc:

    # mu "\"Off-limits for what purpose?\""
    mu "為什麼不准？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3477
translate Tchinese medicinedone_46ca41d6:

    # "You already know the answer, Murdoch."
    "你已經知道答案了，Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3479
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1c952c65:

    # "Just play dumb."
    "裝傻就是了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3481
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bce768e0:

    # al "\"I think you know.\""
    al "你應該也知道了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3485
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b11458c4:

    # al "\"How long have you been down here?\""
    al "你們在這待多久了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3487
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f5101b7c:

    # mu "\"Does it matter?\""
    mu "這重要嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3489
translate Tchinese medicinedone_467012fa:

    # al "\"Are you an idiot?\""
    al "你傻啊？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3492
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6745a7d0:

    # al "\"Of course it DAMN MATTERS.\""
    al "當然很他媽{b}重要{/b}重要了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3495
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a8fe4f48:

    # al "\"WHAT HAVE YOU SEEN?\""
    al "{b}你看到了什麼？{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3497
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b558804b:

    # "It’s strange being in the room with a gun pointed at me, but feeling a little forgotten."
    "明明同在被人拿槍指著的房間裡，我卻似乎被遺忘了，感覺真奇妙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3499
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ceb86b3:

    # "I don’t think he sees me as a person anymore."
    "他好像已經不把我當人看了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3501
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8bd90a9b:

    # "But is he going to underestimate me, or is he just going to shoot me?"
    "但他是會低估我，還是直接開槍？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3503
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cde51fde:

    # "I don’t really know which."
    "很難說會是哪一個。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3505
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3dd5a31a:

    # "I don’t like the unpredictability."
    "我討厭這種不確定性。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3507
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52ddebca:

    # mu "\"We’ve found remains.\""
    mu "我們找到了遺骸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3510
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69c5f0d8:

    # al "\"Which remains?\""
    al "哪些遺骸？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3512
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d1b3ba12:

    # "He doesn’t sound surprised when he ask."
    "他發問的語氣並不驚訝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3514
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c85319bc:

    # mu "\"Below the rooms with the eyes.\""
    mu "在有眼睛的房間下面。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3517
translate Tchinese medicinedone_adc3e2cf_2:

    # "He nods."
    "他點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3519
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e5352510:

    # al "\"The people who founded this town knew James the First was a sick one.\""
    al "建立這個小鎮的人，知道James一世是個變態。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3522
translate Tchinese medicinedone_60c054c3:

    # al "\"They just never had the proof.\""
    al "只是他們苦苦找不到證據。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3525
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5376f2dc:

    # al "\"We did, son.\""
    al "我們找到了，兒子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3528
translate Tchinese medicinedone_53aa4d17:

    # al "\"That’s just one of the things that kept this family strong.\""
    al "而這也不過是我們家族鼎盛的原因之一。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3531
translate Tchinese medicinedone_200c66ae:

    # al "\"Nobody else had it in them to keep those vampires on the hillside in check but us.\""
    al "除了我們，沒人能制衡山坡上的那些吸血鬼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3534
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1bb0ed49:

    # al "\"We found their weakness and brought them to heel.\""
    al "我們找到了他們的弱點，使之屈服。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3537
translate Tchinese medicinedone_147b4743:

    # al "\"And you’ll be taking this secret to the grave, so bury it in your head and then prance onward with your merry little distractions.\""
    al "我要你把這個秘密帶進墳墓。所以就埋葬在腦子裡，然後隨便你繼續那些小消遣吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3540
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b09c16ff:

    # al "\"Have I made myself clear?\""
    al "我說得夠清楚了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3542
translate Tchinese medicinedone_07c0d720:

    # "Murdoch doesn’t speak for a while."
    "Murdoch沉默了好一陣子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3544
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a06e132b:

    # "He opens his mouth to talk, but no words come out."
    "他張開嘴想說話，卻沒發出聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3547
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0db67c52:

    # al "\"Good.\""
    al "很好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3550
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ec113fcb:

    # al "\"Now quit your complaining and be grateful for what we have done.\""
    al "往後別再抱怨，只管感謝我們所做的一切吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3553
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22591adf:

    # mu "\"Dad...\""
    mu "爸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3555
translate Tchinese medicinedone_77467b2f:

    # al "\"{i}What,{/i} Murdoch?\""
    al "{i}幹嘛{/i}，Murdoch？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3558
translate Tchinese medicinedone_798c4f92:

    # mu "\"Why is your sleeve covered in blood?\""
    mu "你的袖子為什麼都是血？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3560
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a5ca81f8:

    # "It’s not a little bit."
    "不只一點點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3562
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1df14364:

    # "And by the look of his arm, it isn’t his."
    "從手臂看來，那不是他的血。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3565
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9395c294:

    # al "\"I was in a fight.\""
    al "我跟人打了場架。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3567
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f7e8c05c:

    # mu "\"Lot of blood for a fight.\""
    mu "打個架流這麼多血啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3569
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5029fa3c:

    # al "\"It was a bad fight.\""
    al "是場硬架。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3571
translate Tchinese medicinedone_05dfa837:

    # mu "\"But what are you doing down {i}here?{/i}\""
    mu "可是你來{i}這裡{/i}又是要做什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3573
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4d5cca65:

    # "Alfred stands there sheepishly."
    "Alfred尷尬地站在原地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3575
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f60e5511:

    # al "\"It doesn’t matter.\""
    al "這不重要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3577
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd310cbb:

    # mu "\"But it does though.\""
    mu "這很重要啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3587
translate Tchinese medicinedone_92356876:

    # "His father raises his hand and takes a step towards him."
    "他父親舉起手，朝他走近一步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3590
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9d3a03ee:

    # al "\"Stop.\""
    al "住口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3592
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ae7d1d94:

    # "Murdoch looks bewildered."
    "Murdoch困惑不已。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3594
translate Tchinese medicinedone_77429d7b:

    # al "\"It’s not your place to question me.\""
    al "{i}你永遠{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3597
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ee0e1d48:

    # al "\"About anything.\""
    al "沒資格質疑我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3600
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9af5637:

    # al "\"{i}Ever.{/i}\""
    al "不管是什麼事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3602
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7325fc2b:

    # "Murdoch keeps staring at the bloodstain on his father’s arm."
    "Murdoch一直盯著他父親手上的血跡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3604
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f25cc6c7:

    # mu "\"But--\""
    mu "可是——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3607
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0a7b418a:

    # al "\"No buts.\""
    al "沒什麼好可是的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3610
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4f5e6036:

    # mu "\"Don’t you see why--\""
    mu "你難道不明白為什麼——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3613
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0889657e:

    # al "\"I TOLD you to {i}stop talking.{/i}\""
    al "我叫你{i}閉嘴{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3616
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c19fac07:

    # "He shuts his mouth."
    "他閉上嘴巴。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3618
translate Tchinese medicinedone_15cbb362:

    # al "\"I clothe you.\""
    al "我給你衣服穿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3621
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c80ac817:

    # al "\"I feed you.\""
    al "給你飯吃。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3624
translate Tchinese medicinedone_785abea9:

    # al "\"I sheltered you for most of your life.\""
    al "庇護了你大半輩子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3627
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e405d522:

    # al "\"I employ you.\""
    al "給你工作。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3630
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a1bae460:

    # al "\"So much of what I have done has been for {i}you.{/i}\""
    al "做的這麼多事都是為了{i}你{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3633
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1e7f9307:

    # al "\"So it’s time for you to start {i}acting{/i} like it.\""
    al "你現在也該有所{i}表現{/i}了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3636
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7d606a46:

    # "Murdoch’s mouth opens."
    "Murdoch張口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3638
translate Tchinese medicinedone_31783222:

    # "Then it closes."
    "然後又閉上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3640
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9b6b1aea:

    # mu "\"I don’t disagree with any of that.\""
    mu "這些我都不否認。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3641
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0b13de4b:

    # mu "\"But what does that have to do with--\""
    mu "但這跟現在有什麼——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3644
translate Tchinese medicinedone_553ff409:

    # al "\"Murdoch.\""
    al "Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3647
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0e470f36:

    # al "\"You’re going to go through the cellar, back into the basement, and up the stairs.\""
    al "我要你現在離開地窖，回到地下室，然後上樓。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3650
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b9986739:

    # al "\"You will wait for your mother, and your older sister.\""
    al "等著你母親和姐姐。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3653
translate Tchinese medicinedone_15543d0b:

    # al "\"And we are going to wait this fire out.\""
    al "然後全家人"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3656
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe4dd074:

    # al "\"Together.\""
    al "一起"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3659
translate Tchinese medicinedone_185044a9:

    # al "\"As a family.\""
    al "等這場火燒完。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3662
translate Tchinese medicinedone_23b52f86:

    # mu "\"Which door did you come from, Dad?\""
    mu "你是從哪扇門進來的，爸？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3664
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a9d3f64c:

    # "Alfred sighs."
    "Alfred嘆氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3666
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4cc754f4:

    # al "\"Why do you need to know son?\""
    al "你為什麼想知道，兒子？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3669
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8cf87e96:

    # mu "\"Because I asked you...\""
    mu "我就是想問……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3671
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f7198d1b:

    # mu "\"I think you should show me.\""
    mu "你應該要帶我去看看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3673
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d7c2fb73:

    # al "\"I don’t think I’m going to.\""
    al "我不想。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3675
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd54e90a:

    # mu "\"It sounds like there’s a reason you don’t want to show me.\""
    mu "你好像有不想告訴我的理由。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3678
translate Tchinese medicinedone_519f5a41:

    # "Alfred smacks his paw on the wall." with hpunch
    "Alfred一爪拍在牆上。" with hpunch

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3681
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d71993e3:

    # al "\"Let it lie son.\""
    al "別再追究了，兒子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3685
translate Tchinese medicinedone_34228653:

    # al "\"All you have to do is leave it be.\""
    al "你只管放下就好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3687
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8d98a5e9:

    # mu "\"If it’s so simple then why can’t you tell me?\""
    mu "如果有這麼簡單，那又為什麼不能告訴我？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3689
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc77c79c:

    # mu "\"Why can’t you tell me anything?\""
    mu "為什麼你什麼都不肯告訴我？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3692
translate Tchinese medicinedone_84f2314e:

    # al "\"Because I love you son.\""
    al "因為我愛你，兒子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3694
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86814205_1:

    # mu "\"...What?\""
    mu "……什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3696
translate Tchinese medicinedone_70863eed:

    # al "\"Because I love you, and I know what’s best for you.\""
    al "因為我愛你，也知道什麼對你最好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3700
translate Tchinese medicinedone_066853a2:

    # mu "\"You’ve never said that before.\""
    mu "你從來沒說過這種話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3702
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35182aa7:

    # al "\"Well, I’m saying it now.\""
    al "嗯，我現在不就說了嗎。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3705
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f51c718d:

    # al "\"I love you, and you should listen to me.\""
    al "我愛你，所以你應該聽我的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3709
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a10cf4e6:

    # al "\"If I show you what’s in that room, it’ll only upset you.\""
    al "帶你去看那個房間，只會害你難過。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3711
translate Tchinese medicinedone_128763cc:

    # al "\"And it will upset your sister.\""
    al "也會傷你姐姐的心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3714
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3dff365f:

    # al "\"And it will upset your mother.\""
    al "也會傷你媽媽的心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3717
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6ef655ae:

    # al "\"Your friend doesn’t want you to stay here very much longer either...\""
    al "你朋友想必也不希望你在這裡待太久……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3720
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ef69d66f:

    # al "\"Does he?\""
    al "對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3722
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6cc60c45:

    # "He looks at me."
    "他看向我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3724
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3e3499eb:

    # m "\"...No.\""
    m "……是的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3726
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cec8699a:

    # mu "\"Sam?\""
    mu "Sam？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3728
translate Tchinese medicinedone_54070999:

    # m "\"Not really, sir.\""
    m "不太想，先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3730
translate Tchinese medicinedone_771a0fb7:

    # "Alfred smiles."
    "Alfred微笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3732
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7141b91b:

    # al "\"You see?\""
    al "看到沒？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3735
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9a1efd45:

    # al "\"This is how things should be.\""
    al "這才像話嘛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3739
translate Tchinese medicinedone_04af19d0:

    # al "\"Now, is there anybody else down here?\""
    al "好了，這裡還有其他人嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3742
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9b12547:

    # al "\"Surely your other friend is around somewhere.\""
    al "你另一個朋友肯定也在附近吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3745
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bbc25c4d:

    # al "\"Maybe Holly’s fiance too?\""
    al "Holly的未婚夫是不是也在？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3748
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c7f76134:

    # al "\"You were together after all.\""
    al "畢竟你們是一起來的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3750
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5db725fa:

    # m "\"They all ran away.\""
    m "他們都跑掉了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3752
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5e7f2ab8:

    # m "\"During the fire.\""
    m "在起火的時候。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3754
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52f6b29c:

    # al "\"Of course they did.\""
    al "這也理所當然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3757
translate Tchinese medicinedone_78675ba8:

    # al "\"Jim’s a resourceful boy.\""
    al "Jim是個機靈的孩子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3760
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ca2c8e24:

    # al "\"His friends are able men.\""
    al "他的朋友都很能幹。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3763
translate Tchinese medicinedone_30790ea1:

    # al "\"Let’s go back upstairs, Murdoch.\""
    al "我們回樓上去吧，Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3766
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b2ebef1f:

    # al "\"Let’s go and be happy.\""
    al "離開這裡，過上幸福的生活。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3768
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3b079ab7:

    # "Murdoch doesn’t move."
    "Murdoch沒有動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3770
translate Tchinese medicinedone_21ee1f5d:

    # mu "\"I won’t ever be happy around you if you do not show me that room.\""
    mu "要是你不帶我去看那個房間，我在你身邊永遠感受不到幸福。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3773
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2daafcb7:

    # al "\"Bull.\""
    al "少胡扯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3775
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc42697a:

    # mu "\"You think I’m lying?\""
    mu "你覺得我在胡說？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3777
translate Tchinese medicinedone_56862957:

    # "Alfred frowns."
    "Alfred皺眉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3779
translate Tchinese medicinedone_926395f3:

    # al "\"I think you’re acting spoiled.\""
    al "我覺得你被寵壞了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3782
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0b75e360:

    # al "\"You lose your temper when you don’t get your way.\""
    al "一不順心，就會發脾氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3785
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d7d1db5f:

    # mu "\"I’m calm dad.\""
    mu "我很冷靜，爸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3787
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19889cde:

    # mu "\"If you don’t show me what’s in that room, then I will never talk to you again.\""
    mu "不讓我看那房間裡面有什麼，我就跟你斷絕關係。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3789
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a7da281b:

    # mu "\"I will leave town.\""
    mu "離開這個小鎮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3791
translate Tchinese medicinedone_de054b94:

    # al "\"Is that really true?\""
    al "你是認真的嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3794
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3e0ae4b:

    # mu "\"...It is.\""
    mu "……是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3796
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9e4c2740:

    # al "\"...And how’s that fair to the rest of the family?\""
    al "……這對其他家人公平嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3799
translate Tchinese medicinedone_75c23774:

    # mu "\"You’ll have to manage without me.\""
    mu "我不在，你們也能過得下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3804
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2e6a7ccd:

    # mu "\"I will never be able to look at you again...\""
    mu "我再也無法正眼看你了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3808
translate Tchinese medicinedone_543aac87:

    # al "\"...Unless you see the room?\""
    al "……除非你看了那個房間？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3810
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6cd29b26:

    # "Murdoch nods."
    "Murdoch點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3811
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eb4cfdf2:

    # mu "\"Unless I see the room.\""
    mu "除非我看了那個房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3813
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aebc770c:

    # "Alfred turns and a scowl creeps up the corner of his snout."
    "Alfred轉過身，嘴角勾起怒色。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3815
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b32218fa:

    # al "\"This the moment of your life where you’re going to show me what your word actually means.\""
    al "這是你人生中，向我證明你說話算話的重要時刻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3818
translate Tchinese medicinedone_39f9b81b:

    # al "\"You can’t go back on it if you want me to see you as a man.\""
    al "要想我把你當男人看，就不能出爾反爾。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3820
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4a2cd211:

    # mu "\"I’m going to ask you one last time.\""
    mu "我再問你最後一次。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3822
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3061cb12:

    # al "\"Are you sure that you really want me to show you the door?\""
    al "你真心確定，要我帶你去看那扇門嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3829
translate Tchinese medicinedone_225cecbe:

    # mu "\"Yes.\""
    mu "是的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3830
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9f9303c5:

    # "Murdoch doesn’t hesitate in the slightest."
    "Murdoch毫無猶豫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3832
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c209bbf8:

    # "Alfred looks down and he puts his paw in his front pocket."
    "Alfred低頭，一爪伸進前口袋。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3834
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bf012bf0:

    # "Then he looks back at Murdoch."
    "然後轉頭回望Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3836
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc9ee05d:

    # al "\"Things won’t ever be the same if we do this.\""
    al "要是真做了，就再也回不去從前了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3839
translate Tchinese medicinedone_839a9a2d:

    # mu "\"Things haven’t been the same for a very long time.\""
    mu "過往，老早就回不去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3842
translate Tchinese medicinedone_adc3e2cf_3:

    # "He nods."
    "他點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3844
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f0c3c247:

    # al "\"Very well.\""
    al "那好吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3846
translate Tchinese medicinedone_20679e8f:

    # "He points at the third door on the left."
    "他指向左邊第三道門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3848
translate Tchinese medicinedone_504cd147:

    # al "\"It’s this one.\""
    al "就是這一扇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3850
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4dc68972:

    # mu "\"Open it for me.\""
    mu "幫我打開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3852
translate Tchinese medicinedone_93511a07:

    # "The older fox hobbles over to the right passage and pulls on the handle."
    "老狐狸跛著腳走到右邊通道，拉開把手。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3854
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f57bed26:

    # "Murdoch steps forward."
    "Murdoch向前一步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3856
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0dc24dfa:

    # "It’s not a small chamber like the rest of the rooms."
    "這間房不像其他房間那麼小。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3859
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3963dbd1:

    # "Rather, it’s another chamber before what looks to be the cave passage."
    "反而是另一個通往洞穴通道的房間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3861
translate Tchinese medicinedone_215942f8:

    # "But what has my attention isn’t the doorway."
    "但吸引我目光的不是門道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3863
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c7382a5c:

    # "It’s the piles of bodies stacked on top of one another."
    "而是一堆堆交疊的屍體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3865
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cdacf891:

    # "Most of them look shriveled and old."
    "大部分都乾癟老舊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3867
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d09d1058:

    # "But one of them is fresh."
    "但其中一具是新鮮的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3869
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fa679ad2:

    # "On the floor there was Reed Morris."
    "Reed Morris倒在地板上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3871
translate Tchinese medicinedone_be9468bb:

    # "But he isn’t breathing."
    "但他沒有呼吸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3873
translate Tchinese medicinedone_36e9ffe7:

    # "His entire throat is gone."
    "整個喉嚨都不見了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3880
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bf7cc2b2:

    # mu "\"What is this?\""
    mu "這是什麼情況？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3882
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2b46d10e:

    # al "\"You know exactly what it is.\""
    al "你再清楚不過了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3885
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4926e248:

    # al "\"Don’t you think it’s time you grew up?\""
    al "你不覺得，是時候該長大了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3887
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48090ba9:

    # mu "\"But these are people.\""
    mu "他們可是人啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3889
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86325a4e:

    # al "\"Were people.\""
    al "曾經是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3892
translate Tchinese medicinedone_55b9eacd:

    # al "\"Do you think that makes them precious?\""
    al "你以為他們會因此而有價值嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3895
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86814205_2:

    # mu "\"...What?\""
    mu "……什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3897
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9bd175e0:

    # gr "\"I think I can explain.\""
    gr "我來解釋吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3900
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a5446386:

    # mu "\"...Mother?\""
    mu "……母親？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3902
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9e4a90f:

    # gr "\"This man, Reed Morris, helped one of town bankers, Mr. Greene, financially entrap and rape his wife for over two decades.\""
    gr "這個男人，Reed Morris，協助鎮上的銀行家Greene先生，以金錢手段陷害並強暴了他的妻子長達二十多年。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3904
translate Tchinese medicinedone_77cf0678:

    # "She points to another one of the corpses, a polecat whose skin is bare and shriveled, as though the water was sucked right out of him."
    "她指向另一具屍體：一隻皮膚乾癟、彷彿全身水分被吸乾的臭鼬。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3906
translate Tchinese medicinedone_423a58e6:

    # gr "\"This man, Brandon Hennisey, didn’t commit any sexual crimes to my knowledge. But he did steal the inheritance left to his late wife Meryl after he had her institutionalized under exaggerated charges.\""
    gr "這個男人，Brandon Hennisey，據我所知，是沒有犯下任何性犯罪。但他在把在世時的亡妻Meryl以經過修飾誇大的罪刑送進精神病院後，搶走了本該留給她的遺產。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3908
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d798a354:

    # "She points out a bear whose nose has rotted off of his face."
    "她指向一隻鼻子已經腐爛的熊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3910
translate Tchinese medicinedone_59b09d44:

    # gr "\"This one strangled both of his wives and walked the earth for seven years after.\""
    gr "這人掐死了的兩任妻子，之後還活在這世上七年之久。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3912
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0eb52439:

    # "She walks over to a kit fox whose mouth is so dry there are more teeth than anything else of him."
    "她走向一隻嘴巴乾到只剩牙齒的耳廓狐。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3914
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9b6c2f9c:

    # gr "\"This one was embezzling the school’s education funds for gambling.\""
    gr "這人挪用學校教育經費去賭博。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3917
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5d638f7:

    # gr "\"Spare me the sanctimony and drop the surprised act.\""
    gr "別再裝驚訝了，省省你的道貌岸然吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3919
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4933e33d:

    # mu "\"...Mother.\""
    mu "……母親。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3920
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f782b1c7:

    # mu "\"I’m not acting.\""
    mu "我不是裝的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3921
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e102b70e:

    # "She crosses her arms and looks him up and down."
    "她抱起雙臂，上下打量他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3923
translate Tchinese medicinedone_20abead4:

    # gr "\"Sometimes I wonder.\""
    gr "有時候我很懷疑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3926
translate Tchinese medicinedone_350835b1:

    # gr "\"Performance or no, I don’t think you’re surprised to see me here, are you?\""
    gr "不管是不是裝的，你在這見到我，應該也沒有多驚訝吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3929
translate Tchinese medicinedone_58248564:

    # gr "\"After all, you are {i}here{/i} aren’t you?\""
    gr "畢竟，你人也在{i}這裡{/i}，不是嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3932
translate Tchinese medicinedone_91567527:

    # gr "\"Either you lurked around long enough to find it...\""
    gr "要不是你長時間摸索發現的……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3935
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ef339c31:

    # gr "\"Or if not that, then somebody must have told you the combination.\""
    gr "就是有人告訴你密碼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3938
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c8ace184:

    # "She eyes her husband."
    "她瞥向她丈夫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3940
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5bcb8c12:

    # gr "\"Or somebody left it lying around somewhere.\""
    gr "或者有人隨便亂放。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3943
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48c0b335:

    # al "\"I didn’t leave it {i}anywhere.{/i}\""
    al "我可沒有亂放。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3946
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d4deda0f:

    # gr "\"Do you know how many times you’ve lost your glasses in the bedroom?\""
    gr "你知不知道自己在臥室搞丟多少次眼鏡了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3949
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22670155:

    # gr "\"Sometimes I think you’d lose your head if it weren’t attached.\""
    gr "我都覺得要不是你頭長在脖子上，哪天也會被你搞丟了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3952
translate Tchinese medicinedone_11910070:

    # m "\"Is this really the time for this?\""
    m "……現在真的是吵這個的時候嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3953
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1f9897d9:

    # "The parents turn their heads to me."
    "他爸媽轉頭看向我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3955
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3600cf4a:

    # "They both look like they’re sizing me up."
    "都在打量我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3957
translate Tchinese medicinedone_582aa220:

    # gr "\"Finally the mute speaks.\""
    gr "啞巴終於開口了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3961
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c13e1a54:

    # gr "\"We have all the time in the world until the smoke clears out.\""
    gr "在濃煙散去之前，我們有的是時間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3964
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2c06ecfb:

    # gr "\"Nobody’s going very far tonight, now are they?\""
    gr "今晚也沒人能跑遠，對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3969
translate Tchinese medicinedone_090bc060:

    # gr "\"And it’s not like you have much room to talk, Mr. Ayers.\""
    gr "況且，你也沒什麼資格說話，Ayers先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3970
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1898611f:

    # "I stiffen up a bit."
    "我身體微微繃緊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3972
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3178471c:

    # m "\"...And what’s that supposed to mean?\""
    m "……這是什麼意思？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3974
translate Tchinese medicinedone_18875e6c:

    # gr "\"Jack Abner was you, was he not?\""
    gr "Jack Abner是你幹的，對不對？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3976
translate Tchinese medicinedone_97eefda7:

    # "I feel my blood run cold."
    "我感覺全身血液變冷。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3977
translate Tchinese medicinedone_df8ec4bc:

    # m "\"What?\""
    m "……什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3979
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b5d56774:

    # gr "\"Not the best kept secret, but a secret all the same, is it not?\""
    gr "這秘密守得不怎麼好，但總歸是個秘密，對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3981
translate Tchinese medicinedone_873b7bfa:

    # "I feel my heart start beating rapidly in my chest."
    "我感覺心臟開始狂跳。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3984
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f6c80b21:

    # m "\"She’s lying.\""
    m "她說謊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3986
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6b7e3faa:

    # gr "\"Mmm, no?\""
    gr "嗯，沒有啊？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3989
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0cc1c8bd:

    # gr "\"The sightings and the testimonies of each witness are quite tightly aligned with the time frame.\""
    gr "所有目擊者的證詞和時間點都高度吻合。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3992
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1fa2332e:

    # gr "\"I’d say you’d get the noose if somebody were to take it to court.\""
    gr "要是有人把這件事告上法庭，你肯定會被判絞刑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3994
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3a171da1:

    # "How did she know?"
    "她怎麼知道？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3996
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8c3395bc:

    # "Who told her?"
    "誰告訴她的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:3998
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7b3e0ad3:

    # "Was I really that obvious?"
    "我真的有那麼明顯嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4000
translate Tchinese medicinedone_00b128e4:

    # "I thought the only one who saw me was Nik..."
    "我還以為看到我的只有Nik……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4002
translate Tchinese medicinedone_356886a7:

    # "But I haven’t seen him for weeks."
    "但我也已經好幾個禮拜沒看到他了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4004
translate Tchinese medicinedone_98e17165:

    # m "\"Don’t believe a word she’s saying Murdoch.\""
    m "別信她說的任何一個字，Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4006
translate Tchinese medicinedone_39dedc11:

    # m "\"I didn’t murder Jack Abner.\""
    m "我沒有謀殺Jack Abner。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4008
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9b241789:

    # "She gives me a suspicious look."
    "她狐疑地望著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4010
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f4fe57de:

    # gr "\"But you {i}did{/i} kill him.\""
    gr "但殺了他的{i}是你{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4013
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bc3dddcd:

    # gr "\"That’s rather well-established in my sources.\""
    gr "我的消息來源很可靠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4016
translate Tchinese medicinedone_67f614f1:

    # gr "\"Frankly there’s no need for a fuss.\""
    gr "說實話，這沒什麼好大驚小怪的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4019
translate Tchinese medicinedone_40ccec96:

    # gr "\"He was also on my list.\""
    gr "他也在我的名單上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4021
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fdcfd18e:

    # m "\"Why?\""
    m "為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4023
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2aa28b5b:

    # gr "\"That sounds like a question you only ask about somebody you knew.\""
    gr "這種問題只有在對方跟你有關的時候才會問吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4026
translate Tchinese medicinedone_219354e0:

    # gr "\"So you did know him?\""
    gr "所以，你的確認識他？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4028
translate Tchinese medicinedone_596aae0c:

    # m "\"...\""
    m "……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4030
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a6301af6:

    # gr "\"Sweet Mary.\""
    gr "我的天。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4033
translate Tchinese medicinedone_09801136:

    # gr "\"You didn’t even mean to do it, did you?\""
    gr "你根本沒想殺他的，對不對？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4036
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6da333d5:

    # gr "\"And here I was looking for common ground.\""
    gr "我還以為我們有共通點呢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4039
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7461f4ff:

    # m "\"I don’t want to kill people.\""
    m "我不想殺人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4040
translate Tchinese medicinedone_90015048:

    # m "\"I mean, sometimes I think I do.\""
    m "我是說，有時候我是會想想。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4042
translate Tchinese medicinedone_71722fb1:

    # gr "\"Well, that’s a start.\""
    gr "嗯，這就對了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4044
translate Tchinese medicinedone_933a4d3c:

    # m "\"I’m not looking to start {i}wanting{/i} to!\""
    m "我不希望自己變得{i}想要{/i}殺人！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4047
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dbece7ff:

    # gr "\"Do you really think taking life is the worst thing that somebody can do?\""
    gr "……你真的認為，奪人性命是人所能做的最壞的事嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4049
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bd158c91:

    # m "\"{i}What?{/i}\""
    m "{i}什麼？{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4052
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0044655a:

    # gr "\"I’m requesting that you put your emotions to the side for the time being and consider some things.\""
    gr "請你暫且放下情緒，認真思考。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4055
translate Tchinese medicinedone_826d4ee5:

    # gr "\"Our own government kills people all of the time.\""
    gr "我們自己的政府，一直都在殺人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4058
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e9665e7a:

    # gr "\"Surely you know that?\""
    gr "你肯定知道吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4060
translate Tchinese medicinedone_596aae0c_1:

    # m "\"...\""
    m "……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4062
translate Tchinese medicinedone_64a9a269:

    # gr "\"Sometimes they’re in uniforms, sometimes they’re in business suits...\""
    gr "時而身穿制服，時而身穿正裝……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4065
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9e0c7a71:

    # gr "\"When you live in a world surrounded by enemies, family is who you must trust to survive.\""
    gr "世上敵人無處不在，只有家人可以賴以為生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4068
translate Tchinese medicinedone_57f700bd:

    # al "\"That’s right.\""
    al "沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4071
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ab5e4d6:

    # al "\"Amen.\""
    al "阿們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4074
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6c6e6f64:

    # gr "\"I like you very much, Mr. Ayers, but you’ve obviously seen too much.\""
    gr "我很中意你，Ayers先生，但你顯然知道得太多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4077
translate Tchinese medicinedone_10e0e8f0:

    # gr "\"So you know that means that we’re going to have to come to some sort of agreement with you.\""
    gr "想必你也知道，我們之間必須達成協議。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4080
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fb391e7a:

    # gr "\"You could cooperate with us, and we could all walk out of here alive...\""
    gr "你可以選擇與我們合作，大家相安無事離開這裡……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4083
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3ec5192:

    # gr "\"Or, you could choose to die in this hole, because the concept of loyalty eludes you.\""
    gr "或者，選擇死在這個洞裡，只因為你不懂得忠誠的概念。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4086
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3e150d25:

    # "She holds out a paw to me."
    "她向我伸出爪。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4088
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e74a650f:

    # gr "\"Well?\""
    gr "如何？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4090
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d81ef355:

    # "I just stare at it for a moment."
    "我只是盯著它看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4092
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc740192:

    # "I feel like all of the people in the pile are staring at me, even though they don’t have eyes anymore."
    "感覺洞裡所有人都在盯著我，哪怕他們已經沒有眼睛了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4095
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7934a822:

    # m "\"I don’t know if I could live with myself if I did that.\""
    m "要是那麼做，我不知道還能不能原諒自己。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4096
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c0444c5a:

    # m "\"Maybe I’d survive a little longer, but I don’t think my soul would.\""
    m "也許我的身體能活久一點，但恐怕我的靈魂不會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4097
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7bab903b:

    # "The edge of her snout tightens a little deeper."
    "她吻部邊緣繃得更緊了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4099
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3db2d4f0:

    # gr "\"There’s something I can respect at least.\""
    gr "在這點上，我倒是能尊重你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4102
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2956c7ae:

    # gr "\"But I think you’re mistaken about something.\""
    gr "但我想你誤會了一件事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4105
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8cce58cd:

    # gr "\"Warfare isn’t murder, Mr. Ayers.\""
    gr "戰爭不是謀殺，Ayers先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4108
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19510907:

    # gr "\"Not all lethal force is sin.\""
    gr "並非所有致命性的武力都是罪惡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4111
translate Tchinese medicinedone_94d70563:

    # gr "\"Each of these men were killing this community in some way or another with outright malice.\""
    gr "這些男人們，一個個的都在以徹底的惡意、各自的方式，殺害這個社區。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4113
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9aa8bfa5:

    # m "\"But you don’t think killing me is a problem.\""
    m "但你不覺得殺我有問題。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4115
translate Tchinese medicinedone_61d28727:

    # gr "\"Have you paid no attention.\""
    gr "你都沒在聽嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4118
translate Tchinese medicinedone_155f9730:

    # gr "\"I’m not trying to kill you.\""
    gr "我又不是想殺你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4120
translate Tchinese medicinedone_75ef5310:

    # m "\"But you will if I don’t agree to keep quiet?\""
    m "但如果我不同意保持沉默，你就會殺我？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4122
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1cb4c92e:

    # gr "\"It would be a threat to the work at hand, yes.\""
    gr "是的，那對我們的業務是個威脅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4125
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0625aba8:

    # gr "\"I’m giving you options.\""
    gr "我是在給你選擇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4128
translate Tchinese medicinedone_17133a0c:

    # gr "\"But if you wanted to walk the path of a martyr for some misguided sense of spiritual exaltation...\""
    gr "但如果你想為了盲目的崇高感而踏上殉道之路……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4131
translate Tchinese medicinedone_02bae31e:

    # gr "\"There are painless ways to go you know.\""
    gr "那也有無痛的方式可選，你知道吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4135
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9aa7d99f:

    # gr "\"Much nicer ways than a bullet.\""
    gr "比吃子彈好多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4138
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d93608c2:

    # "I see her reaching into her purse."
    "她在手提包中摸索。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4140
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe141afd:

    # "She pulls out a crystal bottle with an ornate looking top."
    "掏出一個有著精緻瓶蓋的水晶瓶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4144
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52955f23:

    # gr "\"I’m rather good at making painless potions.\""
    gr "我很擅長調製無痛的藥劑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4146
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3d1dc005:

    # "What she’s saying feels like cold ice crawling up my leg."
    "她的話語化為冰冷的寒意，攀上我的腿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4148
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7073b9da:

    # gr "\"They’re gentle, even though they are inevitable.\""
    gr "即便致命，卻很溫和。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4151
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b580c5ad:

    # gr "\"If you take this, it will feel just like going to sleep.\""
    gr "喝了這個，感覺會像入睡一樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4153
translate Tchinese medicinedone_599d26ed:

    # "I almost let out a laugh."
    "我差點笑出聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4155
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d22728a7:

    # "I see where Harlan got the poison from."
    "總算明白Harlan的毒是從哪來的了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4156
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4f96ce04:

    # "They’ve been working together."
    "他們一直都在合作。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4158
translate Tchinese medicinedone_634601e8:

    # "I just saved everybody from this."
    "我才剛把大家從這東西手中救回來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4160
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dd22de01:

    # "And now I’m the one who’s supposed to drink it?"
    "現在卻輪到我喝了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4162
translate Tchinese medicinedone_73c9d99b:

    # m "\"You’re out of your mind.\""
    m "你瘋了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4164
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6e19f9ee:

    # "Gretchen shakes her head."
    "Gretchen搖搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4166
translate Tchinese medicinedone_10b89da2:

    # gr "\"I promise it’s not personal.\""
    gr "我保證這不是在針對你個人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4169
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5e29887d:

    # gr "\"I’m not averse to using the way that’s not so nice if you want to put up a struggle.\""
    gr "要是你想反抗，我也不介意動用較不溫和的方式。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4172
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc5716f0:

    # gr "\"But something tells me you’re not going to.\""
    gr "但我覺得你不會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4174
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9a50e8b:

    # m "\"...And why’s that?\""
    m "……怎麼說？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4177
translate Tchinese medicinedone_30fb033c:

    # gr "\"Because you know that even if you run out of here, and make this all public, that I’ll still be able to manage better press than you.\""
    gr "因為你知道，哪怕你能成功逃脫、公開一切，我的話語權依舊凌駕於你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4180
translate Tchinese medicinedone_736649be:

    # gr "\"Because you’re factually guilty of your own crime, and it will get you the noose.\""
    gr "因為你犯了罪是事實，從而導致你被絞死。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4183
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a9a28871:

    # gr "\"So is it starting to make sense yet?\""
    gr "現在懂了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4186
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ee87b290:

    # gr "\"You’re going in the same direction.\""
    gr "殊途同歸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4190
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7d3c1662:

    # gr "\"It’s just up to you which the route will be.\""
    gr "只是走的路會有多痛苦，取決於你的選擇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4192
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2dd09077:

    # gr "\"You don’t even have to die.\""
    gr "你甚至都沒必要死。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4194
translate Tchinese medicinedone_27c67918:

    # m "\"They’re fucking crazy, Murdoch.\""
    m "他們都他媽瘋了，Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4196
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4978696e:

    # gr "\"I don’t know why you’re bothering talking to him.\""
    gr "我不知道你為什麼還要向他喊話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4198
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e8bfc85e:

    # gr "\"He’s the only one here who’s never killed.\""
    gr "他是這裡唯一沒殺過人的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4202
translate Tchinese medicinedone_16e83955:

    # al "\"He never was good with blood.\""
    al "他一直不擅長見血。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4204
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d788f90b:

    # gr "\"No, he wasn’t.\""
    gr "是啊，他不擅長。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4207
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0f727571:

    # gr "\"Then again, that method is too brutal for my taste as well.\""
    gr "不過，那種方法對我個人而言也算過於殘暴。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4209
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1d93f2f1:

    # m "\"Murdoch, why aren’t you {i}saying{/i} anything?\""
    m "Murdoch，你為什麼{i}不說話{/i}？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4211
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8504cb18:

    # gr "\"Probably because he knows you’re a killer.\""
    gr "大概是因為他知道你是個殺人犯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4214
translate Tchinese medicinedone_471846d4:

    # al "\"He’s known us his entire life, Mr. Ayers.\""
    al "他認識我們一輩子了，Ayers先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4217
translate Tchinese medicinedone_95a6bf28:

    # al "\"You’ve known him less than a month.\""
    al "而你認識他還不到一個月。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4220
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4756269c:

    # mu "\"Wait.\""
    mu "等等。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4222
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e6e81974:

    # "For once, his voice gets them to stop talking."
    "他的聲音第一次打斷了我們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4224
translate Tchinese medicinedone_56671e6c:

    # mu "\"I think there are things I deserve to know...\""
    mu "我想有些事我有權知道……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4225
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3859ae3c:

    # mu "\"Before you decide anything.\""
    mu "先別急著做決定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4227
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5ff3eece:

    # "Alfred shakes his head."
    "Alfred搖搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4230
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3a35435e:

    # al "\"We can talk after he drinks. Or I shoot.\""
    al "等他喝下或我開槍之後再說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4232
translate Tchinese medicinedone_353221b7:

    # "Gretchen, on the other hand, looks slightly baffled."
    "Gretchen則相反，面露困惑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4234
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9df3fe27:

    # gr "\"I’m sorry, but was there anything said that was not clear?\""
    gr "抱歉，我說的有哪裡不夠清楚嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4237
translate Tchinese medicinedone_780617ad:

    # gr "\"I think you should have a pretty good idea about who you’ve been working with and what we’ve been doing.\""
    gr "你應該很清楚自己一直以來在跟什麼樣的人來往，還有我們所做的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4239
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1a9d0277:

    # gr "\"Some of these men knew about you, son.\""
    gr "這裡有些男人知道你的事，兒子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4242
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a6732c51:

    # gr "\"Some of them were going to kill you.\""
    gr "有些人本來還想殺你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4245
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dd79d482:

    # "Murdoch opens his mouth to speak."
    "Murdoch張開嘴想說話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4247
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ac9592f:

    # "Then he closes it."
    "然後又閉上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4249
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1b2f675d:

    # "He inhales."
    "吸氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4250
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52179db1:

    # "Then he exhales."
    "然後吐氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4255
translate Tchinese medicinedone_620a555a:

    # mu "\"Just tell me why you were dumping bodies at the lake.\""
    mu "先告訴我，你們為什麼要把屍體丟進湖裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4257
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a4dd4526:

    # "For the first time, Gretchen looks surprised."
    "Gretchen初次表現出驚訝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4259
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5ca4d957:

    # gr "\"We haven’t been.\""
    gr "我們沒有啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4262
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ff151deb:

    # mu "\"Yes, you have.\""
    mu "有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4263
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a38275cc:

    # mu "\"Sam and I saw them being dumped at night at the river.\""
    mu "我和Sam在晚上看見有人往河裡拋屍。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4265
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a191a406:

    # mu "\"Before the islet, where the current is strong.\""
    mu "在小島前面，水流很強的地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4268
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1819554d:

    # al "\"He’s talking about the disposal.\""
    al "他說的是處理屍體的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4270
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a08604d4:

    # "Gretchen whirls on her husband."
    "Gretchen猛然轉向丈夫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4272
translate Tchinese medicinedone_304e3959:

    # gr "\"What do you mean the disposal?\""
    gr "你說什麼處理？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4276
translate Tchinese medicinedone_75ba4861:

    # gr "\"We have the lime vat in here for a reason.\""
    gr " 我們已經在這準備了石灰池啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4278
translate Tchinese medicinedone_385393c9:

    # al "\"He means the little ones.\""
    al "他是指那些小孩。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4282
translate Tchinese medicinedone_050ae190:

    # gr "\"Excuse me?\""
    gr "你說什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4284
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d8b73a1e:

    # al "\"The ones I find in the tunnels.\""
    al "我在隧道裡找到的那些。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4287
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5455d6b5:

    # gr "\"Alfred, what the {i}fuck{/i} are you talking about?\""
    gr "Alfred，{i}你他媽{/i}到底在說什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4289
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0e286b2a:

    # "The old fox shifts uncomfortably."
    "老狐狸不安地挪動身體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4292
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7234bca0:

    # al "\"It just didn’t seem right, leaving them there, down in the dark.\""
    al "我只是覺得把他們遺留在黑暗中不太對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4295
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22d9be0f:

    # gr "\"Alfred.\""
    gr "Alfred。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4297
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6af190bd:

    # "The vixen is staring him down."
    "母狐狸瞪著他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4299
translate Tchinese medicinedone_33e639a5:

    # gr "\"We had nothing to do with them.\""
    gr "我們跟他們無關。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4302
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b655ba45:

    # gr "\"You had nothing to do with them.\""
    gr "你跟他們無關。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4305
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ee73d42d:

    # al "\"I know.\""
    al "我知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4308
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eb5d53ce:

    # gr "\"So why in the {i}fuck{/i} are you cleaning up other people’s messes.\""
    gr "那{i}你他媽{/i}為什麼要去收拾別人的爛攤子？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4311
translate Tchinese medicinedone_da8a5051:

    # al "\"It just seemed right.\""
    al "我只是覺得應該這麼做。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4314
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6c27cc13:

    # al "\"That’s all.\""
    al "就這樣而已。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4318
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48fe2333:

    # "She looks at him as if he’s grown a second head."
    "她不可置信地瞪著他，彷彿他長出了第二顆頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4320
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5d15feba:

    # gr "\"But {i}why{/i} would you {i}do{/i} that?\""
    gr "但你{i}為什麼{/i} 要{i}那麼{/i} 做？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4322
translate Tchinese medicinedone_552abc1f:

    # "He doesn’t answer."
    "他沒有回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4324
translate Tchinese medicinedone_04464f48:

    # mu "\"But why would you put them {i}there?{/i}\""
    mu "那你為什麼要把他們丟在{i}那裡{/i}？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4326
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b052d718:

    # mu "\"Down there in that dark, dirty water?\""
    mu "拋進那深不見底的髒水裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4328
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86b8221c:

    # mu "\"Seamus wouldn’t have wanted that!\""
    mu "Seamus不會希望你那麼做的！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4330
translate Tchinese medicinedone_50898daa:

    # "I hear a hiss so sharp that I can’t tell where it’s coming from."
    "我聽見一道嘶聲，尖銳得無法分辨來源。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4333
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2493882b:

    # al "\"{i}Yes, he would have.{/i}\""
    al "{i}他會的。{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4335
translate Tchinese medicinedone_63c90d9e:

    # "His voice is more unsettling now that he isn’t yelling."
    "他不再大吼，聲色更令人不安了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4337
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1d026778:

    # al "\"You think you’re so wise?\""
    al "你以為自己很聰明嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4341
translate Tchinese medicinedone_109216fe:

    # al "\"You have the gall to tell me what {i}your{/i} baby brother wanted, like {i}you{/i} knew him better than {i}me?{/i}\""
    al "居然有膽子告訴我{i}你{/i} 弟弟想要什麼，好像比{i}我{/i} 更了解他一樣？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4344
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4491aa77:

    # al "\"Well, you don’t.\""
    al "你根本就不了解他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4347
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dd8cf5e3:

    # al "\"Your brother {i}understood{/i} the respect we owe to the dead.\""
    al "你弟第{i}理解{/i}我們對死者應有的尊重。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4350
translate Tchinese medicinedone_43d114e4:

    # al "\"Your brother understood what it really meant to make sacrifices for your family. Him better than {i}anybody.{/i}\""
    al "你弟明白什麼叫作為家族犧牲奉獻。他比任何人都懂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4353
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cdf2e6ba:

    # al "\"He would scab his hands washing the floor, get {i}splinters{/i} in his paws laying posts, busting his ass and picking up slack while you and that lazy sunuvabitch played with instruments and probably yourselves!\""
    al "他會竭盡全力幫忙，洗地板到手都起繭子了、鋪木板到爪都被{i}木屑{/i}刺了；而你和那狗娘養的懶鬼卻在忙著玩樂器，可能還在玩自己！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4355
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f2f31961:

    # "His whole body is shaking."
    "他渾身顫抖不已。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4358
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f063f69e:

    # al "\"You think you really knew him just because you took him fishing a few times?\""
    al "你真以為帶他釣個幾次魚就算了解他了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4362
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e52d82af:

    # al "\"Because you gave him a few damn bottle rockets to scare the neighbors with?\""
    al "就因為給了他幾個蠢瓶子火箭嚇鄰居玩？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4365
translate Tchinese medicinedone_624d00ca:

    # al "\"You think if he were alive today that he’d fuck around like how you fuck around with your life?\""
    al "要是他今天還活著，你以為他會像你一樣虛度人生？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4369
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2020903b:

    # al "\"No, he had a light in his eyes.\""
    al "不，他眼裡有光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4372
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9f32e752:

    # al "\"That boy was going places.\""
    al "那孩子前途無量。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4375
translate Tchinese medicinedone_359382f1:

    # al "\"But you’re going to stand there...\""
    al "而你卻站在這裡……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4378
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a6b39c8f:

    # al "\"And tell me you think he’d be {i}upset that I gave all those poor kids rest in the water?{/i}\""
    al "對我叫囂說，你覺得他會{i}因為我把那些可憐的孩子安葬在水裡而生氣？{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4381
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5e505e09:

    # al "\"When you don’t even realize that if he were with us today, he’d be embarrassed by you?\""
    al "你甚至沒意識到，他今天要是還在，會為你感到羞恥嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4384
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f430efaf:

    # al "\"Just like the rest of the family is?\""
    al "就像家裡其他人一樣？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4386
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1e55b358:

    # "Murdoch doesn’t say anything for a while."
    "Murdoch好一陣子沒有說話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4389
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ad52a396:

    # al "\"Well you wanted to hear the truth, didn’t you Murdoch?\""
    al "你不是想聽真相嗎，Murdoch？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4392
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1b7ff377:

    # al "\"I hope it satisfies you.\""
    al "希望你滿意我的回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4394
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a5646996:

    # "Alfred looks at his son."
    "Alfred看向兒子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4395
translate Tchinese medicinedone_61f84345:

    # "I can’t tell what expression Murdoch is wearing from behind, but he looks to be staring past his father."
    "我在Murdoch身後，看不出他是什麼表情，但他視線似乎穿越了父親。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4396
translate Tchinese medicinedone_acb82d66:

    # "I doubt he can make eye contact."
    "他大概沒法與對方對視吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4397
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3663bdfb:

    # "Alfred gives a stiff nod, then turns away."
    "Alfred僵硬地點點頭，然後轉身。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4399
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7f8f49eb:

    # mu "\"Dad.\""
    mu "爸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4401
translate Tchinese medicinedone_99761947:

    # "The way he says the word surprises me."
    "他呼喚的語氣出乎我意料。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4402
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3393841f:

    # "He doesn’t sound hurt, or shocked."
    "既不受傷、也不震驚。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4403
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cb78f8d5:

    # "It sounds like he’s phrasing it again as a question."
    "聽起來像是問句。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4406
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc41363d:

    # mu "\"Why did you say bottle rockets?\""
    mu "你為什麼會提到瓶子火箭？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4408
translate Tchinese medicinedone_44379ca5:

    # al "\"What the fuck kind of question is that?\""
    al "這他媽是什麼問題？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4410
translate Tchinese medicinedone_01286258:

    # mu "\"We only made bottle rockets one time.\""
    mu "我們只做過一次瓶子火箭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4411
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0a827634:

    # "Murdoch’s tone now sounds like his mother’s."
    "現在Murdoch的語氣聽起來像他媽。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4412
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ee4bde47:

    # "The mood in the air is different somehow."
    "現場氣氛隱約變了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4413
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b881e477:

    # "Something’s changed, but I can’t tell what."
    "有什麼變了，但我說不準究竟是什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4415
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c74b817d:

    # al "\"What’s your point, son?\""
    al "你想說什麼，兒子？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4417
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7cd5a543:

    # mu "\"My point is rockets weren’t allowed in town.\""
    mu "我想說的是，鎮上不准放火箭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4418
translate Tchinese medicinedone_31d9d866:

    # mu "\"They were cracking down on the easterners, so it was impossible to buy any.\""
    mu "他們當時在打壓東邊來的人，所以買都買不到。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4419
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22b19665:

    # mu "\"I never told you that Seamus had bottle rockets.\""
    mu "我從來沒有告訴你Seamus有瓶子火箭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4421
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1c2da367:

    # mu "\"And that’s important because... he did.\""
    mu "這一點很重要，因為……他真的有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4423
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8cd1297c:

    # mu "\"Ralph made them.\""
    mu "Ralph做的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4425
translate Tchinese medicinedone_33e91412:

    # "Gretchen isn’t looking at her husband anymore."
    "Gretchen不再看著丈夫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4426
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b03b3f88:

    # "She’s paying attention to her son."
    "注意力都在兒子身上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4427
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bd9f5ce5:

    # "It might be the most attentive I’ve ever seen her be towards him."
    "這可能是我見過她對他最專注的一次。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4429
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bfa3fa04:

    # mu "\"You were out of town.\""
    mu "你當時不在鎮上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4430
translate Tchinese medicinedone_611abc63:

    # mu "\"How did you know?\""
    mu "怎麼會知道這件事？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4433
translate Tchinese medicinedone_77b4e645:

    # al "\"What does it matter?\""
    al "這又有什麼關係？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4436
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cca549d4:

    # al "\"I obviously misremembered.\""
    al "肯定是我記錯了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4438
translate Tchinese medicinedone_89e3538b:

    # mu "\"You hated them because you said they reminded you of the war.\""
    mu "你說那會讓你想起戰爭，所以討厭得要命。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4439
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6d5753cd:

    # mu "\"We always had to hide them from you.\""
    mu "我們都得藏著不讓你發現。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4440
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5fada489:

    # "Now Alfred looks like he’s stuck."
    "Alfred面露難色。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4441
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22b19665_1:

    # mu "\"I never told you that Seamus had bottle rockets.\""
    mu "我沒告訴過你Seamus有瓶子火箭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4442
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a6a92b51:

    # mu "\"Not once.\""
    mu "從來沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4445
translate Tchinese medicinedone_11bce89a:

    # gr "\"Alfred, what is he talking about?\""
    gr "Alfred，他這是什麼意思？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4448
translate Tchinese medicinedone_84ef9b25:

    # al "\"He’s confused.\""
    al "是他記錯了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4451
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a7281ca8:

    # al "\"He can’t even get store the store inventory straight.\""
    al "他連店裡的庫存都搞不清楚。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4454
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4d7e6714:

    # ra "\"Five copper rockets, six zinc, three potassium.\""
    ra "五個銅火箭、六個鋅的、三個鉀的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4459
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4eacd0f1:

    # "None of us noticed that Ralph was in the doorway."
    "沒人注意到Ralph出現在門口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4461
translate Tchinese medicinedone_188532e1:

    # al "\"There’s {i}more{/i} people down here?\""
    al "下面{i}還有{/i}其他人？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4464
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3c53d5ed:

    # al "\"What have you {i}done{/i}?!?\""
    al "你們{i}做了{/i}什麼！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4467
translate Tchinese medicinedone_749c1315:

    # gr "\"Ralph...\""
    gr "Ralph……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4469
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4f92e3a1:

    # ra "\"Yes Mrs. Byrnes?\""
    ra "是，Byrnes夫人？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4471
translate Tchinese medicinedone_adac167d:

    # gr "\"Were there really no other sales of bottle rockets in town in the summer of 1905?\""
    gr "1905年夏天，鎮上真的沒有其他地方在賣瓶子火箭嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4474
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e24bd8ac:

    # ra "\"There were not, ma’am.\""
    ra "沒有的，夫人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4476
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e60579a0:

    # gr "\"Had you ever made bottle rockets for either of my sons prior?\""
    gr "你在那之前有為我兒子們做過瓶子火箭嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4478
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b4fbfaff:

    # ra "\"I had not.\""
    ra "沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4480
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1901ce9a:

    # "She nods slowly."
    "她緩緩點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4484
translate Tchinese medicinedone_26311edf:

    # gr "\"I believe you.\""
    gr "我相信你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4486
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6c23cf27:

    # ra "\"I suspected you would.\""
    ra "我就覺得妳會的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4488
translate Tchinese medicinedone_99d52468:

    # "Her lips thin."
    "她抿起嘴唇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4490
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d475b12b:

    # gr "\"I never liked you Ralph.\""
    gr "我從來都不喜歡你，Ralph。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4493
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c42e5e8c:

    # ra "\"The feeling is mutual Mrs. Byrnes.\""
    ra "我有同感，Byrnes夫人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4495
translate Tchinese medicinedone_75f512ea:

    # ra "\"But finesse recognizes finesse.\""
    ra "但英雄識英雄。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4497
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f67ccb6e:

    # "Her lips grow tighter."
    "她嘴唇抿得更緊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4498
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8c4f3e2c:

    # "She doesn’t disagree."
    "沒有反駁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4499
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2749845b:

    # "She’s looking at her husband."
    "看向丈夫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4501
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ed789ae1:

    # gr "\"Explain to me how you knew that our son had bottle rockets on the day of his death.\""
    gr "解釋一下，你是怎麼知道咱們兒子在死的那天有瓶子火箭的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4504
translate Tchinese medicinedone_76559c8d:

    # al "\"It was just an assumption.\""
    al "我只是猜他有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4507
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d148a970:

    # gr "\"You have complained to me, day in and day out, about the specific placements of store inventory over the last twenty years.\""
    gr "過去二十年間，你成天都在向我抱怨店裡特定商品的擺放位置。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4510
translate Tchinese medicinedone_06fa15ad:

    # gr "\"I wouldn’t have trusted you to do what we do if you were sloppy about details.\""
    gr "要不是你注重細節，我不可能會信任你來幹我們在這的勾當。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4513
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b2920d02:

    # gr "\"Give me a reason -- any reason Alfred.\""
    gr "給我一個理由——任何理由，Alfred。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4516
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a74be4cb:

    # gr "\"Any reason at all for me to believe that you did not kill my son.\""
    gr "任何理由，能讓我相信我兒子不是你殺的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4518
translate Tchinese medicinedone_594b6a8c:

    # "He just stands there."
    "他呆站原地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4521
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2dda9787:

    # al "\"He saw me with the old mayor.\""
    al "他撞見我跟老市長的事了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4524
translate Tchinese medicinedone_84249292:

    # al "\"He was going to tell.\""
    al "他想說出去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4527
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22d9be0f_1:

    # gr "\"Alfred.\""
    gr "Alfred。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4530
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ecc4932:

    # al "\"He should have never been there.\""
    al "他本來就不該出現在那的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4533
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cb4684e2:

    # gr "\"Do you mean to tell me that {i}you{/i} killed my baby?\""
    gr "你這是在說，{i}是你{/i}殺了我的寶貝兒子嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4535
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7d7b4734:

    # "Nobody speaks while they wait for his answer."
    "沒有人說話，大家都在等他回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4537
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0c6d81fb:

    # al "\"Just listen to me.\""
    al "聽我說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4540
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22d9be0f_2:

    # gr "\"Alfred.\""
    gr "Alfred。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4543
translate Tchinese medicinedone_72c1e16f:

    # al "\"{i}Listen!{/i}\""
    al "{i}先聽我說！{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4546
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6c52f485:

    # gr "\"...I’m listening.\""
    gr "……我在聽。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4549
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9ed9c5fa:

    # al "\"He tried to run.\""
    al "他想逃跑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4552
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6d9ee57d:

    # al "\"He called {i}out{/i} Gretchen.\""
    al "他出聲{i}大喊{/i}了，Gretchen。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4556
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c7944e16:

    # al "\"I meant to knock him out.\""
    al "我本來只是想打昏他的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4559
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5f4e858d:

    # mu "\"So you were the one at the house.\""
    mu "所以在家裡的是你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4561
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c393c25f:

    # mu "\"You were the one who knocked me out.\""
    mu "把我砸暈的就是你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4563
translate Tchinese medicinedone_97d6ea21:

    # al "\"YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO WATCH HIM!\""
    al "{b}你應該要看好他的！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4565
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1cbe8d29:

    # mu "\"Holly and I--\""
    mu "Holly和我——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4568
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cf999aaf:

    # al "\"{i}Always{/i} blaming others!\""
    al "{i}永遠{/i}都在怪別人！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4570
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a7022e10:

    # "Alfred’s tongue hisses."
    "Alfred以舌發出嘶聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4572
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c0ed3c03:

    # al "\"You are always the victim!\""
    al "你永遠都在扮演受害者！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4575
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4695f3c0:

    # al "\"DID YOU FORGET? YOU WERE TOLD EXPLICITLY NOT TO COME TO THE HOUSE!\""
    al "{b}你難道忘了嗎，你被囑咐過不要來屋子的！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4579
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e6577d6f:

    # al "\"ARE YOU PROUD OF WHAT YOU MADE ME DO?\""
    al "{b}你是在為逼我下手而沾沾自喜嗎？{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4582
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22d9be0f_3:

    # gr "\"Alfred.\""
    gr "Alfred。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4585
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b0045b34:

    # al "\"I {i}TOLD{/i} YOU TO LI--\""
    al "{b}我叫你先聽——{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4588
translate Tchinese medicinedone_80180688:

    # "A shot {nw}"
    "一聲{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4595
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5fd79000:

    # extend "goes off."
    extend "槍響。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4596
translate Tchinese medicinedone_99fd8f54:

    # "Blood splatters the walls."
    "鮮血濺滿牆壁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4598
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dbcf0223:

    # "Alfred Byrnes has a blank look in his eyes as a part of his brains still hang from the side of his skull."
    "Alfred Byrnes眼神空洞，部分腦子還掛在頭顱旁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4599
translate Tchinese medicinedone_43cdb7df:

    # "Smoke blows out of the length of Gretchen’s pistol."
    "Gretchen的手槍冒出煙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4608
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c75add1:

    # "It takes longer than we’d expect for Alfred to hit the floor, but the impact sounds wet."
    "Alfred在經過比想像中更長的時間後才倒在地上，發出濕黏的撞擊聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4614
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a8dea637:

    # m "\"You better be a pretty quick draw if you want to take the three of us down.\""
    m "要想幹掉我們三個，妳得是個快槍手。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4616
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e2cb5f97:

    # gr "\"Hardly.\""
    gr "不會的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4619
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0acae10:

    # gr "\"Everything I’ve ever done has been for my family.\""
    gr "我做過的一切都是為了家庭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4623
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b4f19d0a:

    # gr "\"But I just found out that he buried it ten years ago.\""
    gr "但我現在才發現，他十年前就把我們家給埋葬了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4626
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bbe9232c:

    # gr "\"I think some part of me knew that things had already fallen apart.\""
    gr "我內心某部分恐怕早就知道事情已經分崩離析了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4629
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a67c122f:

    # gr "\"But now that everything’s up in ashes, I have to wonder if this is how things were meant to be.\""
    gr "但如今一切都化為灰燼，我不禁懷疑，這是否就是命中註定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4631
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d6ddfb43:

    # "She lifts her pistol in the air."
    "她把槍舉向空中。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4633
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3770b641:

    # gr "\"I never preferred killing like this.\""
    gr "我從來不喜歡用這種方式殺人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4636
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8a5f3f75:

    # gr "\"Like I said, the right kind of poison is gentler.\""
    gr "我說過了，適當的毒藥更溫和。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4639
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4d6984cd:

    # gr "\"Tidier.\""
    gr "更乾淨。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4642
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f7003e7:

    # gr "\"If you want to rush me so you can take me to the sheriff, granted he’s still {i}alive,{/i} be my guest.\""
    gr "如果你們想撲過來把我抓住交給警長——要是他還{i}活著{/i}——那就請便。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4645
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4d811277:

    # gr "\"I’ll be looking for a priest regardless, since there’s only one judge I put any stock in.\""
    gr "但我會去找神父的，因為我相信的審判者只有一位。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4648
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe856435:

    # gr "\"You can also tell the world about what you’ve found here, but I can’t promise that they’ll be understanding.\""
    gr "要想把這裡的一切公諸於世也行，但我不能保證人們會作何反應。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4651
translate Tchinese medicinedone_832e35ac:

    # gr "\"Because I will make sure you tell them everything.\""
    gr "因為我會確保來龍去脈鉅細靡遺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4654
translate Tchinese medicinedone_80d5b53f:

    # gr "\"Or you could just walk away, and let what’s buried here stay burried.\""
    gr "或者也可以就此離開，讓這裡的東西永不見光。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4657
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bf206b40:

    # gr "\"Either way, it’s out of my hands.\""
    gr "無論如何，事情已經脫離了我的掌控。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4659
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fb92ded5:

    # "She points the pistol directly at my heart."
    "她把槍直直指向我的心口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4661
translate Tchinese medicinedone_82dcdb5d:

    # gr "\"Go now.\""
    gr "快走。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4664
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3b65751d:

    # gr "\"Before I change my mind.\""
    gr "免得我改變心意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4666
translate Tchinese medicinedone_041319fe:

    # "I walk backwards, slowly."
    "我慢慢向後退。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4668
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ec460a17:

    # "So does Ralph."
    "Ralph也是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4669
translate Tchinese medicinedone_09679970:

    # "Murdoch is still staring at the body of his father."
    "Murdoch還在望著他父親的屍體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4670
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9602a562:

    # "I can’t tell what he’s thinking."
    "我看不出他在想什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4671
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8ce4f946:

    # "But eventually, he turns his back to him, and to her."
    "但最終，他轉身背對父親，還有她。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4673
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d4643da4:

    # "I presume that he’s decided she’s not going to shoot him."
    "我猜他是斷定她不會開槍射他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4681
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c1d0a20:

    # "Murdoch closes the door behind us."
    "Murdoch在我們身後關上門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4684
translate Tchinese medicinedone_afa10d12:

    # "I want to ask him how he’s feeling."
    "我很想詢問他的感受。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4686
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c102977f:

    # "But it’s a stupid thing to ask, considering what just happened."
    "但考慮到剛才發生的那些事，這就是個蠢問題。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4688
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d086003b:

    # "So I start to talk about what’s next."
    "所以我開口談往後的事："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4692
translate Tchinese medicinedone_244eef33:

    # m "\"Here’s what I think we should do.\""
    m "我們接下來應該這樣做。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4694
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ba01384:

    # m "\"We rouse everybody who’s still here.\""
    m "叫醒還在這裡的所有人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4696
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4348e1c5:

    # m "\"We lock the door behind us.\""
    m "鎖上通過的門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4698
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ba842968:

    # m "\"We head for the train station in the sunrise.\""
    m "在日出時前往火車站。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4700
translate Tchinese medicinedone_893c96ee:

    # m "\"Do y’all agree?\""
    m "你們同意不？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4702
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aa548e46:

    # ra "\"That’s what I’m going to do, regardless.\""
    ra "我就是這麼個打算。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4704
translate Tchinese medicinedone_04c38a9e:

    # ra "\"Do you understand that we’re leaving tomorrow, Murdoch?\""
    ra "你明白我們明天就要離開了嗎，Murdoch？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4706
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc5422e1:

    # mu "\"...I understand.\""
    mu "……我知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4708
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bd6e1d15:

    # ra "\"No more poking around.\""
    ra "別再亂跑探查了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4710
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0f5e73d8:

    # ra "\"I’m sorry if you didn’t find what you were looking for.\""
    ra "如果你沒找到想要的答案，那我很遺憾。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4712
translate Tchinese medicinedone_31ffdc35:

    # ra "\"And I’m even more sorry if you did find it.\""
    ra "要是真找到了，那我更加遺憾。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4714
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9cceb15:

    # m "\"That was ugly.\""
    m "剛才那真有夠糟的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4716
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b4528348:

    # mu "\"It always has been.\""
    mu "一直都這麼糟。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4718
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0fcd4ca8:

    # mu "\"But being here only made them worse.\""
    mu "但是，待在這裡只會更糟。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4720
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c0f11e6c:

    # mu "\"I’m still certain of that.\""
    mu "這一點我還是很確定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4722
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f92cc6bd:

    # mu "\"Leaving is the best idea.\""
    mu "離開就是最好的選擇。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4724
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e6cb991b:

    # mu "\"I’ll tell you why if we make it to sunrise.\""
    mu "如果咱們能活到日出，我再告訴你原因。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4729
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0f82c572:

    # "Ralph has to to give Jim and Neil another round of charcoal, {nw}"
    "Ralph得再給Jim和Neil一劑活性炭，{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4731
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3d79ff55:

    # extend "but I help him drag their bodies upstairs."
    extend "而我則幫他把他們拖上樓。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4733
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4737a707:

    # "When Cynthia sees us her eyes widen with terror, {nw}"
    "Cynthia一看到我們，就因驚恐而瞪大雙眼，{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4735
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6156678e:

    # extend "but she sighs a breath of relief whenever she notices Jim’s diaphragm heaving."
    extend "但她注意到Jim的胸膛還在起伏，便鬆了一口氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4737
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2d5e6341:

    # "I see Blithe, Melissa, Reubin and Dahlia asleep on the ground, and feel a pang of jealousy."
    "眼見Blithe、Melissa、Reubin和Dahlia睡在地上，我感覺很嫉妒她們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4739
translate Tchinese medicinedone_266534fc:

    # "I still don’t feel safe enough to sleep."
    "我還是覺得不夠安全，睡不著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4741
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f28db43c:

    # "I sit on the front steps of the school and wait until the sunrises."
    "我坐在學校前的台階上，等待太陽升起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4744
translate Tchinese medicinedone_88d569f5:

    # "The sky is foggy when the sun comes out, but tinges of gold peak out from behind the fog."
    "日出時天空霧濛濛的，但金色的光芒穿透了煙霧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4746
translate Tchinese medicinedone_57104579:

    # "The feeling like I’m being watched is gone."
    "那種被盯著的感覺消失了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4747
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0befc23f:

    # "I hear somebody coughing."
    "有人在咳嗽。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4750
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2338e1a6:

    # "Jim rouses."
    "Jim醒了過來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4752
translate Tchinese medicinedone_063898c8:

    # ji "\"What happened?\""
    ji "發生什麼事了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4754
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7043184f:

    # ra "\"You were both poisoned.\""
    ra "你們兩個中毒了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4756
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0d6c10db:

    # ji "\"...Jesus.\""
    ji "……我靠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4758
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5eeaa3f:

    # nei "\"It was the canteen, wasn’t it?\""
    nei "是那壺水，對吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4761
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c19a99c5:

    # "Neil is sitting up."
    "Neil坐了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4763
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c806ebc0:

    # m "\"Yeah.\""
    m "對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4766
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4f7b9675:

    # nei "\"He should have made it stronger.\""
    nei "他應該下更重的劑量。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4769
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a4c85ede:

    # nei "\"He’ll wish he had the next time I see him.\""
    nei "下次再見面，我會讓他後悔沒下夠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4773
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0b1340b0:

    # dh "\"You won’t.\""
    dh "你不會再見到他了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4776
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35611a26:

    # ji "\"We might.\""
    ji "可能會。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4779
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fb708085:

    # ji "\"He told us that he was headed for the train.\""
    ji "他說了要去火車站。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4782
translate Tchinese medicinedone_01a44098:

    # dh "\"I saw what happened to him.\""
    dh "我看到他的下場了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4785
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3d9cd61e:

    # dh "\"He isn’t our problem anymore.\""
    dh "不用再管他了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4788
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8becc009:

    # ji "\"Pray tell us why.\""
    ji "麻煩解釋一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4791
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f5ace48c:

    # "She looks to Blithe, whose eyes meet her gaze, and Melissa, fast asleep."
    "她看向與她對視的Blithe，以及在夢鄉的Melissa。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4793
translate Tchinese medicinedone_adbb0bf8:

    # "Then she looks back to Jim."
    "然後轉頭回望Jim。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4796
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48e9ca95:

    # dh "\"Because I saw him go somewhere that he won’t be coming back from.\""
    dh "因為我看到他去了一個回不來的地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4799
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d17f3511:

    # dh "\"Do you want to know the details?\""
    dh "你想知道細節嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4802
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d7352536:

    # ji "\"...No.\""
    ji "……不用了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4805
translate Tchinese medicinedone_823a10f9:

    # dh "\"I didn’t suspect that you would.\""
    dh "我也這麼想。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4809
translate Tchinese medicinedone_364fe9b3:

    # reu "\"...Mother fucker.\""
    reu "……去他媽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4812
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c16b94a5:

    # reu "\"Did any of you see how that old hare came at me?\""
    reu "你們有人看到那老兔子是怎麼襲擊我的嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4815
translate Tchinese medicinedone_38d731f3:

    # ji "\"If we had we wouldn’t have passed out ourselves.\""
    ji "要是有，我們自己就不會昏過去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4818
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f7217abe:

    # reu "\"...You all passed out?\""
    reu "……你們全都昏倒了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4821
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1285e107:

    # nei "\"...Not by choice.\""
    nei "……不是自願的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4823
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3bbe3aa:

    # m "\"...Is it ever?\""
    m "……昏倒還有自願的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4827
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eb44a1ee:

    # "They both answer {i}yes{/i} at the same time."
    "他倆異口同聲回答『有』。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4831
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0e97c9a7:

    # ji "\"Now that everybody’s awake, might I suggest that we leave?\""
    ji "現在大家都醒了，我們是否也該離開了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4834
translate Tchinese medicinedone_db6f6731:

    # ji "\"I don’t wish to linger here a moment longer.\""
    ji "我是一刻都不想多待在這了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4837
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7dba9d46:

    # "We all agree upon walking to the station above ground."
    "我們都同意在地面上走到車站。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4839
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ab7a4a21:

    # "When we leave the school, I can’t help wondering about who knows about the bodies beneath the school."
    "離開學校時，我忍不住在想都有誰知道學校底下那些屍體。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4841
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e86aa471:

    # "Who among us knows about the Hendricks family bodies. Who of us knows about the Byrnes family bodies..."
    "我們之中，有誰知道Hendricks家的屍體、誰知道Byrnes家的屍體……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4843
translate Tchinese medicinedone_815ea879:

    # "There isn’t much talking in the line."
    "隊伍中沒什麼交談。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4845
translate Tchinese medicinedone_71c3de79:

    # "Not until Lucy speaks up."
    "直到Lucy開口。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4847
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0179f9c:

    # lu "\"Did we ever decide where we’re going?\""
    lu "大家決定好要去哪裡了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4848
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c456220e:

    # lu "\"Once we reach the station, I mean?\""
    lu "我是說，抵達車站之後？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4857
translate Tchinese medicinedone_749f8a55:

    # "We walk straight on through the sand, kicking up dust for a while before anybody answers."
    "我們好一陣子沒人回答，只是徑直穿過沙地，踢起塵土。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4859
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dad0c879:

    # ra "\"Anywhere but here is fine with me.\""
    ra "只要不待在這，我哪裡都行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4861
translate Tchinese medicinedone_00433655:

    # reu "\"I’ll be going as far east as soon and as comfortably as I can.\""
    reu "我只想盡速趕回東岸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4864
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5887f80:

    # reu "\"Expenses be damned.\""
    reu "不管什麼經費了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4866
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1d9d78a9:

    # cy "\"Payton is where we mean to stop.\""
    cy "我們打算停留在沛頓。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4867
translate Tchinese medicinedone_913ee6a7:

    # cy "\"The Madam said she telegrammed for several rooms for us, until we can figure out what we’re doing next.\""
    cy "夫人說她已經用電報幫我們預訂了幾間房，直到我們決定好下一步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4868
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0a1a155:

    # m "\"Payton isn’t the worst idea.\""
    m "沛頓不算差。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4870
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b55fdbff:

    # ji "\"The wonderful thing about trains is that they have plenty of stops.\""
    ji "火車的好處就是有很多停靠站點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4873
translate Tchinese medicinedone_12c2770b:

    # ji "\"You can all do as you wish.\""
    ji "你們可以隨心所欲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4876
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e022acf8:

    # ji "\"But I wouldn’t make plans until you have your ticket and we move out of here.\""
    ji "但我在拿到車票、離開這裡之前，不會做任何計劃。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4880
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2cb6b4e5:

    # "It’s still too early in the morning when we arrive."
    "我們抵達時還是清晨。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4881
translate Tchinese medicinedone_47770d92:

    # "The station isn’t as full of people as I thought it would be."
    "車站的人潮沒有我想像中多。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4882
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c950ce2b:

    # "Either most of them got out yesterday, or..."
    "要麼大多人昨天就離開了，不然就是……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4883
translate Tchinese medicinedone_74e812ae:

    # "I don’t want to really think about it."
    "我不太願意去想。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4886
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19609d22:

    # "I was just hoping to see more familiar faces."
    "只希望能見到更多熟面孔。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4887
translate Tchinese medicinedone_905ad6e7:

    # "Mostly what I see looks like the faces of ghosts."
    "我看到的大多數臉龐都像幽魂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4894
translate Tchinese medicinedone_40885f0f:

    # hounk "\"Jim!\""
    hounk "Jim！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4897
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c9c8a9a4:

    # "Holly walks up, dressed in her ordinary clothes."
    "Holly走了過來，身穿日常服裝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4898
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ccfa91b0:

    # "Grandma Rowan stands close behind her, but keeping her distance."
    "Rowan奶奶跟在她身後，但保持一點距離。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4901
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5fcd05d3:

    # ho "\"You look terrible.\""
    ho "你看起來糟透了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4903
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1e0b8a16:

    # "She’s addressing him, and only him."
    "她只向他說話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4905
translate Tchinese medicinedone_da9c9a70:

    # ji "\"It was a hell of a night, Holly.\""
    ji "昨晚的確是糟透了，Holly。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4908
translate Tchinese medicinedone_60d839ce:

    # ho "\"The house was safe.\""
    ho "房子是安全的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4911
translate Tchinese medicinedone_193ed5e0:

    # ho "\"Grandma knew what to do.\""
    ho "奶奶知道應對方法。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4914
translate Tchinese medicinedone_171848bc:

    # ho "\"You should come back and clean yourself up before you go.\""
    ho "你應該先回去打理一下再走。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4917
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e55e5d5e:

    # ji "\"And risk my ticket out of here?\""
    ji "冒著錯過機會離開的風險？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4920
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6913bc8d:

    # ji "\"I’m fine.\""
    ji "不用了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4923
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5cf857b0:

    # ji "\"Thanks.\""
    ji "謝謝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4926
translate Tchinese medicinedone_03fedf95:

    # ji "\"You should go too.\""
    ji "妳最好也離開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4929
translate Tchinese medicinedone_01b94951:

    # ho "\"That was the plan until you decided you didn’t want me to.\""
    ho "我本來是這樣打算的，直到你決定不想要我跟著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4932
translate Tchinese medicinedone_32052768:

    # ji "\"You don’t have to come with me to get out.\""
    ji "妳要想離開這裡，也不是非得跟著我不可。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4935
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bcd980b7:

    # ji "\"You’re educated and you’re pretty.\""
    ji "妳受過教育，長得又漂亮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4938
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b594622a:

    # ji "\"You’ll do well elsewhere.\""
    ji "在其他地方會過得很好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4941
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ae64a9e9:

    # ho "\"I need support if I want to get out of here, Jim.\""
    ho "我需要援助才能離得開，Jim。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4944
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6634d66b:

    # ho "\"You’ve always had money so I know you’ve never understood that.\""
    ho "你一直不愁錢，所以我知道你根本不懂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4947
translate Tchinese medicinedone_571dceae:

    # ho "\"All of my connections are here.\""
    ho "我所有的人脈都在這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4949
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5f55c1ce:

    # "She turns to Murdoch, her voice incredulous."
    "她不可置信地說道，並轉向Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4951
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b854502c:

    # ho "\"That’s why Murdoch hasn’t left either.\""
    ho "Murdoch也還沒離開，就是這個原因。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4954
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9fa5e1d2:

    # ho "\"Family has to stick together.\""
    ho "家人必須團結一心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4957
translate Tchinese medicinedone_41295a76:

    # mu "\"I’m leaving too, Holly.\""
    mu "我也要走了，Holly。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4959
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c43ac3bc:

    # ho "\"...What?\""
    ho "……什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4962
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8f2f09b5:

    # mu "\"I’m not living in this town anymore.\""
    mu "我不會再住在這個鎮上了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4963
translate Tchinese medicinedone_067d768a:

    # mu "\"I’m leaving.\""
    mu "我要離開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4965
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f7551d60:

    # ho "\"And where would you go?\""
    ho "那你要去哪裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4967
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2721a605:

    # mu "\"I don’t know.\""
    mu "我不知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4969
translate Tchinese medicinedone_92255ac9:

    # ho "\"What would you even do?\""
    ho "那你打算做什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4972
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2721a605_1:

    # mu "\"I don’t know.\""
    mu "我不知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4973
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9d598fcd:

    # mu "\"It’s well past the time for me to find out though.\""
    mu "不過，我早該去追尋這個答案了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4975
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0d541283:

    # mu "\"We aren’t children anymore.\""
    mu "我們已經不是孩子了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4977
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bb7fa7db:

    # "The train howls in the distance."
    "火車在遠處鳴笛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4978
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7ca163df:

    # "We see it chugging toward us."
    "朝我們駛來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4980
translate Tchinese medicinedone_440c18dd:

    # ho "\"If you think I won’t go to the press...\""
    ho "如果你以為我不會去報社……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4982
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bf78145b:

    # mu "\"That doesn’t matter anymore.\""
    mu "那已經無所謂了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4984
translate Tchinese medicinedone_614e4809:

    # ho "\"Oh, indeed?!\""
    ho "哦，是嗎！？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4990
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0017acda:

    # "Murdoch walks up to her."
    "Murdoch走向她。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4992
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f3db3402:

    # "He whispers something in her ear."
    "在她耳邊低語。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4995
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4a58fa30:

    # "Holly’s eyes widen."
    "Holly兩眼瞪大。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:4999
translate Tchinese medicinedone_db731c5d:

    # "Then she slaps him across the face."
    "然後甩了他一巴掌。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5001
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aadc1ecd:

    # ho "\"LIAR!\""
    ho "{b}騙子！{/b}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5004
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1216708e:

    # "Murdoch rubs his cheek, then looks at his paw."
    "Murdoch揉了揉臉頰，看向自己的爪。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5005
translate Tchinese medicinedone_34e601a5:

    # "Holly is heaving, her lips curl into a snarl."
    "Holly喘著粗氣，嘴唇扭曲咆哮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5010
translate Tchinese medicinedone_02a03f00:

    # "He turns his back to her."
    "他轉身背對她。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5012
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3a26ab5d:

    # ho "\"You {i}lying{/i} piece of shit!\""
    ho "你這個死{i}騙子{/i}！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5019
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8c263070:

    # "She runs up and shoves him in the back."
    "她衝上前從後面推他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5021
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cfae89e9:

    # "He stumbles to the ground."
    "害他跌坐在地。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5022
translate Tchinese medicinedone_51cb06d4:

    # "Then he gets back up."
    "隨即又站了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5023
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d4beed91:

    # "She runs at him again."
    "她再次衝向他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5027
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bb97a953:

    # "I step between them."
    "我擋到他們中間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5028
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eaa761db:

    # "Then she stops for a moment."
    "她停了一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5030
translate Tchinese medicinedone_85e88fd9:

    # ho "\"Get out of the way.\""
    ho "滾開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5032
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9a8325e:

    # m "\"I think he understands your message.\""
    m "我想他已經明白妳的意思了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5034
translate Tchinese medicinedone_727b1df0:

    # ho "\"I’m not through.\""
    ho "我話還沒說完呢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5036
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2898c0cb:

    # m "\"But I’m saying that you are.\""
    m "我要妳別再繼續了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5038
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bce9cec1:

    # ho "\"And who the fuck are you?\""
    ho "你他媽算老幾？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5040
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0843b38f:

    # m "\"...Didn’t you just say that family should stick together?\""
    m "……妳剛剛不是才說家人應該要團結嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5042
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ceb69f47:

    # ho "\"Is that a joke?\""
    ho "你是在開玩笑嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5044
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6291e4a3:

    # m "\"Am I laughing?\""
    m "我有在笑嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5045
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e9b8808e:

    # "She nods, slowly."
    "她緩緩點了個頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5047
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9ad138d5:

    # ho "\"So you’re the one who put him up to this then?\""
    ho "就是你慫恿他這麼做的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5050
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4cf9063f:

    # ho "\"Make sense.\""
    ho "說得通。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5053
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c14bfec1:

    # ho "\"You look the type to bring him to his knees.\""
    ho "你看著就像那種會讓他屈膝跪地的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5055
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aac87464:

    # m "\"I don’t have much say in what anybody does.\""
    m "我對別人的決定沒什麼話語權。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5057
translate Tchinese medicinedone_951f7411:

    # ho "\"Oh, don’t you?\""
    ho "哦，是嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5060
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9491c051:

    # ho "\"You think he hasn’t had dozens like you before?\""
    ho "你不知道他早就遇過幾十個像你這樣的人嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5063
translate Tchinese medicinedone_55a54d45:

    # ho "\"He chases {i}experiences.{/i}\""
    ho "他會追求{i}體驗{/i}。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5066
translate Tchinese medicinedone_021a625d:

    # ho "\"What’s he going to do when he wakes up and you’re not there, hrm?\""
    ho "當他醒來卻發現你人跑了，他該怎麼辦，嗯？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5069
translate Tchinese medicinedone_91a98208:

    # ra "\"He’ll always have me.\""
    ra "他永遠還有我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5070
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3d582260:

    # ra "\"You’re not the only one who’s thought about this, Holly.\""
    ra "妳不是唯一想過這件事的人，Holly。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5072
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a818bbb:

    # ho "\"As if {i}that{/i} means anything.\""
    ho "{i}口說無憑。{/i}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5075
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8bac9460:

    # ho "\"You were gone for nearly a decade.\""
    ho "你離開了將近十年。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5077
translate Tchinese medicinedone_82b13781:

    # "The door of the train opens up."
    "火車門打開了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5078
translate Tchinese medicinedone_125a2e77:

    # ra "\"And somehow I still have a better relationship with him than you do.\""
    ra "可是不知道為什麼，我跟他之間的關係還是比你好耶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5080
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eb818307:

    # ho "\"No offense, Ralph, but you’ve never been handsome enough to leave an actual impression on him.\""
    ho "我就直說了，Ralph，你又沒帥到能擄獲他的心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5083
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5ad3216c:

    # ra "\"Jesus Christ, Holly.\""
    ra "我的天啊，Holly。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5085
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4998adbb:

    # ho "\"But am I wrong?\""
    ho "難道我說錯了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5088
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1ffd27a2:

    # ho "\"You’re not the one who’s making him leave.\""
    ho "讓他離開的人不是你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5091
translate Tchinese medicinedone_18f7e295:

    # ho "\"It’s this stupid fucking brute.\""
    ho "是這個愚蠢的糙漢。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5093
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4fe32bbe:

    # ra "\"You really don’t think it could possibly be anything else?\""
    ra "妳真不覺得可能還有其他原因嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5094
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8aed3369:

    # "He raises his hands to the sky around him."
    "他向空中舉起雙手示意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5095
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4752c4e1:

    # ra "\"Anything else?\""
    ra "就想不到別的了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5097
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc1e3d92:

    # ho "\"Nothing as big, no.\""
    ho "沒有什麼比這更關鍵的了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5099
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69191a88:

    # ra "\"Fuck!\""
    ra "我操！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5100
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5721ac21:

    # ra "\"Okay then Holly.\""
    ra "那好吧，Holly。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5101
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d41a14c5:

    # ra "\"I’m going to tell you something I’ve wanted to say to you ever since I first met you.\""
    ra "我這就告訴妳一件打從我第一次見到妳就想說的事："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5102
translate Tchinese medicinedone_100cb844:

    # ra "\"Goodbye.\""
    ra "再見。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5106
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c262c50e:

    # "He hops aboard, back hunched and his hands in his pockets."
    "他彎著背、雙手插進口袋裡跳上車。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5107
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5f260483:

    # "Jim and his friends follow next."
    "Jim和他朋友們也跟上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5108
translate Tchinese medicinedone_31772b81:

    # "Murdoch stares at the door of the train, then looks back."
    "Murdoch望著火車門，然後回頭看。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5109
translate Tchinese medicinedone_afa7ce94:

    # "I still stand in between him and his sister and grandma."
    "我依然站在他和他姐姐、奶奶之間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5114
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7737f289:

    # mu "\"Goodbye, Grandma.\""
    mu "再見了，奶奶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5116
translate Tchinese medicinedone_beb798f7:

    # ci "\"You know my number.\""
    ci "你知道我的電話號碼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5117
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6e8f9950:

    # ci "\"Keep in touch.\""
    ci "保持聯絡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5119
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5db5f9f6:

    # mu "\"I will.\""
    mu "我會的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5121
translate Tchinese medicinedone_72d165ee:

    # mu "\"Goodbye Holly.\""
    mu "再見了，Holly。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5123
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cbeb98f9:

    # ho "\"Don’t even think about talking to me again if you step on that train.\""
    ho "你要敢踏上那輛火車，我們就絕交。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5126
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9a45f2c0:

    # ho "\"Don’t let somebody like {i}him{/i} make you do something that you’re going to regret.\""
    ho "別讓{i}他{/i} 這種人害你做出會後悔的傻事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5129
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c7418f65:

    # mu "\"The only thing I regret...\""
    mu "我唯一的後悔……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5131
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d92fffde:

    # mu "\"...is waiting for my life to happen.\""
    mu "……就是過著隨波逐流的人生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5133
translate Tchinese medicinedone_71281014:

    # mu "\"I didn’t mean to ruin anything for you because of that.\""
    mu "我不是有意因為這樣而連累妳的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5134
translate Tchinese medicinedone_54ba9e9c:

    # mu "\"...Try talking to him again after all of this has passed.\""
    mu "……等這一切過去後，再試著跟他談談吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5135
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b9b01c68:

    # mu "\"I think he’ll listen.\""
    mu "他應該會聽的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5137
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d1de7b20:

    # ho "\"Stop.\""
    ho "你"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5140
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4034c8ce:

    # ho "\"Telling.\""
    ho "別再"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5143
translate Tchinese medicinedone_677345e2:

    # ho "\"Lies.\""
    ho "撒謊了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5146
translate Tchinese medicinedone_29e47cec:

    # "Murdoch disappears into the train."
    "Murdoch人影消失在火車裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5147
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2e6f464b:

    # "Now all that’s left is me."
    "現在只剩我了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5149
translate Tchinese medicinedone_26aa1173:

    # ho "\"I can forgive a lot of things and a lot of people, Samuel Ayers.\""
    ho "我可以原諒很多人事物，Samuel Ayers。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5152
translate Tchinese medicinedone_94cf5dee:

    # ho "\"But if you get on that train?\""
    ho "但你要是踏上那列火車？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5155
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a13e8780:

    # ho "\"You alone I will never forgive.\""
    ho "唯獨你，我永遠不會原諒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5157
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bfae5013:

    # "I suck in air, then feel some mixture of a sigh and a groan escape my body."
    "我深吸一口氣，身體發出一道混雜著嘆息和呻吟的聲音："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5158
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f19d038:

    # m "\"Alright.\""
    m "這樣吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5159
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7f8d3b45:

    # m "\"Here’s some advice about threatening somebody.\""
    m "我給妳一點關於威脅人的建議。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5160
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8d3479dc:

    # m "\"If you’re going to do it, you need to matter to them.\""
    m "威脅別人的前提是，對對方有意義。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5161
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2735dbd3:

    # m "\"You, like your mother, have been able to do what you do, because you did it to the people who cared about you.\""
    m "你跟妳媽一樣，一直以來都能得逞，只不過是因為對象是在乎妳們的人罷了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5162
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b85119ba:

    # m "\"But me?\""
    m "但我呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5163
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0e0eddb2:

    # m "\"I barely even know who you are.\""
    m "我又跟妳不熟。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5164
translate Tchinese medicinedone_87b8fd9a:

    # m "\"Have a nice life.\""
    m "祝妳人生美滿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5165
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69d6f73e:

    # m "\"If you can.\""
    m "如果有辦法的話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5169
translate Tchinese medicinedone_50cec63e:

    # "I step onto the steps of the train cart and pass through the door."
    "我踏上火車車廂的階梯，穿過車門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5179
translate Tchinese medicinedone_93327921:

    # "Murdoch has a window seat."
    "Murdoch坐在靠窗的位置。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5180
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7cbb3787:

    # "Ralph sits beside him."
    "Ralph坐在他旁邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5181
translate Tchinese medicinedone_597d2173:

    # "I sit next to him."
    "我坐到他旁邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5182
translate Tchinese medicinedone_401f8f77:

    # "I think we’ve already said enough of what there is to say."
    "我們該說的話都說得差不多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5183
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e1c0aa33:

    # "Somebody walks up to us."
    "有人朝我們走來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5186
translate Tchinese medicinedone_abe81672:

    # "It’s Jim."
    "是Jim。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5188
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2412fd26:

    # ji "\"I know you were planning to stop by in Payton...\""
    ji "我知道你們本來打算停留在沛頓……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5191
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eea40d9b:

    # ji "\"But I have more than enough room on the east coast.\""
    ji "但我東岸的家很大。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5194
translate Tchinese medicinedone_214b6ab2:

    # ji "\"You could stay there for a while until you find employment.\""
    ji "你們可以在那住一陣子，直到找到工作。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5197
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc44ee91:

    # ji "\"Accommodations would be far better than you’re all used to, I assure you.\""
    ji "我保證生活條件遠比你們原先的好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5200
translate Tchinese medicinedone_df97785f:

    # mu "\"I’m not sure.\""
    mu "我不確定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5202
translate Tchinese medicinedone_85f26ab9:

    # "Jim puts his paws in his pockets and breaks eye contact."
    "Jim把爪伸進口袋，移開視線。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5204
translate Tchinese medicinedone_46a00bc3:

    # ji "\"Well, with everything that ah... happened, I think I understand why you’d be hesitant.\""
    ji "嗯，發生那麼多、呃……事情，我能理解你為什麼會猶豫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5207
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bd5a5de5:

    # mu "\"We’ll consider it.\""
    mu "我們會考慮的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5208
translate Tchinese medicinedone_89b94e58:

    # m "\"I don’t suppose the offer extends to us too?\""
    m "這個提議不包含我們吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5210
translate Tchinese medicinedone_762d903f:

    # ji "\"...It wouldn’t if you hadn’t saved my life.\""
    ji "……你們是我的救命恩人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5213
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b64452ca:

    # ji "\"It would be cheap not to repay the gratitude in some way.\""
    ji "這恩情不報就太說不過去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5215
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c238c6ca:

    # mu "\"That wasn’t a no.\""
    mu "我沒有拒絕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5216
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7277d75f:

    # mu "\"But it wasn’t a yes either.\""
    mu "但也不算答應。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5218
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7b19e50a:

    # ji "\"...Very well.\""
    ji "……那好吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5221
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c13c613f:

    # ji "\"I’ll leave you to think on it for a while.\""
    ji "你們仔細考慮一下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5224
translate Tchinese medicinedone_52fbc45f:

    # ji "\"To better days, then.\""
    ji "我先失陪了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5227
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ad2e246f:

    # "Jim slips away, his tail bristling a little bit from embarrassment."
    "Jim離去，尾巴因為尷尬而微微豎起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5229
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7b5caa68:

    # ra "\"...It’s not a bad idea, if it’s not permanent.\""
    ra "……不是永遠的話，這提議不差。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5230
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cd693ff2:

    # m "\"There’s always work on the coast.\""
    m "海岸總會有工作能幹。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5231
translate Tchinese medicinedone_43dee6cf:

    # m "\"I don’t think Murdoch would be okay with that though.\""
    m "但我不覺得Murdoch會願意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5233
translate Tchinese medicinedone_17a18119:

    # mu "\"I might be.\""
    mu "我或許願意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5235
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b9bdef8a:

    # mu "\"I have a good while to think about it before the Payton stop.\""
    mu "在到達沛頓之前，還有大把時間能考慮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5239
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b995fe59:

    # "Another pair of familiar faces show up."
    "另一對熟面孔出現了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5241
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5d982bb0:

    # "Blithe sits next to me without asking."
    "Blithe問都沒問就坐到我身旁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5243
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2f616efd:

    # "Her friend, who’s still limping, sits across from us."
    "她那位腳還有點跛的朋友坐到我們對面。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5245
translate Tchinese medicinedone_64a0b953:

    # "Blithe shoves something into my paw."
    "Blithe把某個東西塞進我爪裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5246
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc859670:

    # "It’s cold, and round."
    "又冷又圓。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5247
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bc09ff8a:

    # bl "\"Here’s your money as promised mister.\""
    bl "說好要給你的錢，先生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5249
translate Tchinese medicinedone_353e6899:

    # "I unball my fist."
    "我張開拳頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5250
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0da2692a:

    # "Staring back at me is an eagle coin."
    "一枚鷹揚金幣回望著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5251
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dd9c9f5e:

    # "I think about all the work we did at the general store."
    "我回想起在雜貨店做的所有工作。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5252
translate Tchinese medicinedone_113220ad:

    # "All of the boxes lifted."
    "搬的所有箱子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5253
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c6533f36:

    # "All of the photographs dipped in chemicals."
    "所有浸在化學藥劑裡的照片。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5254
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aab8d180:

    # "How locking lips and rushing into a bet could have lost me time in my life-- the kind of time so neatly weighed and expressed by material things such as this warm piece of metal in my hand."
    "接吻和衝動打賭差點讓我虛度光陰——能被這手中的溫暖金屬精準衡量並表達的光陰。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5255
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9988faf1:

    # "It’s crazy how just holding it can’t compare to real work."
    "僅是握著它，也無法體會到真正的苦勞，這實在太神奇了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5256
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8bb88d62:

    # "The next person who palm this slips into isn’t going to feel all those real experiences."
    "下一個拿到這玩意的人，並不會感受到那些真實的經歷。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5257
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ec469382:

    # m "\"You know, it’s funny...\""
    m "妳知道嗎，說來好笑……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5258
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7746e72c:

    # m "\"I had forgotten all about it.\""
    m "但我完全忘記這件事了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5260
translate Tchinese medicinedone_77632861:

    # bl "\"You saying you want me to take it back?\""
    bl "要我拿回去嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5262
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3e3499eb_1:

    # m "\"...No.\""
    m "……不要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5263
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd6a7692:

    # bl "\"That’s what I thought you’d say.\""
    bl "我就知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5266
translate Tchinese medicinedone_808f0b6e:

    # m "\"You ain’t gonna need it yourself?\""
    m "妳自己不需要嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5267
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9d05da62:

    # m "\"I’d think it would be hard for couple of kids to get by without any money.\""
    m "我感覺小孩子們沒錢會很難過活。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5269
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5d6f2629:

    # bl "\"Papa can meet us in Payton.\""
    bl "爸爸會在沛頓跟我們會合。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5271
translate Tchinese medicinedone_023a9735:

    # bl "\"He was looking for work there anyhow.\""
    bl "反正他本來就在那裡找工作。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5274
translate Tchinese medicinedone_17bc187f:

    # me "\"And I’m not going to wait around in an empty house.\""
    me "我也不想在空房子裡等著。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5277
translate Tchinese medicinedone_84c2c02c:

    # me "\"Not with an injury like this.\""
    me "我腿都傷成這樣了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5280
translate Tchinese medicinedone_94e4ef79:

    # bl "\"That doctor in the tuxedo said he could help, but I know it’s not gonna be free.\""
    bl "那個穿禮服的醫生說他會幫忙，但我知道肯定不是免費的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5283
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6387dae2:

    # bl "\"Piece of shit.\""
    bl "混帳東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5285
translate Tchinese medicinedone_98971b5f:

    # m "\"Then how are you going to pay?\""
    m "那妳要怎麼付？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5287
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e83f14f4:

    # bl "\"I told Ms. Byrnes to give me two hundred dollars.\""
    bl "我跟Byrnes女士要了兩百塊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5289
translate Tchinese medicinedone_55e1a14c:

    # "My first thought was which one, but that probably doesn’t matter."
    "我第一個念頭是哪一位，但那大概不重要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5290
translate Tchinese medicinedone_905963fa:

    # "I see Dahlia in one of the seats at the end of the train car."
    "我看見Dahlia坐在車廂尾端的座位上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5291
translate Tchinese medicinedone_98f45ec9:

    # "She’s talking to Lucy and Cynthia."
    "正在跟Lucy和Cynthia說話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5292
translate Tchinese medicinedone_93b197da:

    # m "\"Are you serious?\""
    m "真的假的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5294
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2f2c9f86:

    # bl "\"Should have asked for more considering it’s a bargain for the silence.\""
    bl "應該多要一點的，畢竟這是封口費。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5296
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f3866d28:

    # bl "\"For some reason she seems to think this whole situation...\""
    bl "不知道為什麼，她好像覺得這整個情況……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5298
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f211bdab:

    # "She gestures to the landscape outside."
    "她指向外面的風景示意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5300
translate Tchinese medicinedone_64c5c338:

    # bl "\"...is salvageable.\""
    bl "……還有救。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5303
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a6e0a44d:

    # bl "\"Personally, I don’t think it is.\""
    bl "我個人是不這麼認為啦。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5306
translate Tchinese medicinedone_030301ad:

    # bl "\"But I did what I was meant to do here, as far as I’m concerned.\""
    bl "但我反正已經做了自己份內的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5308
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1acb2f42:

    # "There’s something unnerving about the look in her eye, but she doesn’t sit still long enough for me to think on it."
    "她的眼神有點令人不安，但她沒有久坐，我也沒法細思。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5310
translate Tchinese medicinedone_20a6fd7c:

    # bl "\"Let’s go check out the dining cart Melissa.\""
    bl "我們去餐車看看吧，Melissa。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5313
translate Tchinese medicinedone_234e9d3e:

    # bl "\"You think they’ll have anything good?\""
    bl "妳覺得他們會有什麼好吃的嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5316
translate Tchinese medicinedone_614ff896:

    # me "\"No, but I’m hungry.\""
    me "不覺得，但我好餓。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5323
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ba83437:

    # "The whistle blows."
    "汽笛再次鳴起。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5325
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f176dadf:

    # "I feel the wheels of the train come to life again."
    "我感覺到火車的輪子開始轉動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5328
translate Tchinese medicinedone_622efb3a:

    # "We’re moving."
    "我們出發了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5329
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4b1de51d:

    # "There’s still people outside the window."
    "窗外還有人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5330
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cfdca067:

    # "Granny Rowan looks back at us."
    "Rowan奶奶回望著我們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5331
translate Tchinese medicinedone_33d66ffe:

    # "She’s not waving but there’s some look of satisfaction in her eyes that I don’t quite understand."
    "她沒有揮手，但眼中有一種我不太理解的滿意神情。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5332
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a81ed435:

    # "Holly looks back too."
    "Holly望著我們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5333
translate Tchinese medicinedone_37920494:

    # "There’s bitterness in her expression."
    "一臉苦悶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5335
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3559c354:

    # "But there’s somebody else standing behind her."
    "但她身後還站著另一個人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5336
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7d8661ef:

    # "I blink, to make sure that my vision isn’t blurry, that I’m not hallucinating."
    "我眨眨眼，確認視線沒有模糊、不是幻覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5337
translate Tchinese medicinedone_22579078:

    # "But there’s another white cougar."
    "但那裡有另一隻白美洲獅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5338
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1452b2b8:

    # "He’s waving goodbye to me."
    "正在向我揮手道別。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5339
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7fa63f36:

    # "He’s wearing my clothes."
    "穿著我的衣服。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5341
translate Tchinese medicinedone_07b3bc00:

    # "And he’s wearing a smile that’s too big for my face."
    "笑容大到我自己的臉都裝不下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5344
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0698095c:

    # "I shake Murdoch and his eyes open with a start."
    "我搖晃Murdoch，令他驚醒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5346
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d4837497:

    # m "\"Murdoch!\""
    m "Murdoch！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5347
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4cf4c1b9:

    # m "\"Did you {i}see{/i} that?\""
    m "你有{i}看到{/i}嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5349
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1bd6d855:

    # mu "\"See what?\""
    mu "看到什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5350
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7065ee31:

    # m "\"If you look real quickl--\""
    m "你快點看——"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5351
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ea397783:

    # "We’re already past the station."
    "我們已經駛離車站了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5352
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5352251d:

    # m "\"Shit!\""
    m "幹！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5354
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8332a72e:

    # mu "\"I don’t see the point anyway.\""
    mu "我反正認為是沒什麼意義。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5355
translate Tchinese medicinedone_425ea946:

    # mu "\"You know that your eyes lie here.\""
    mu "你也知道，在這裡眼見不一定為實。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5357
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dfd6cb41:

    # m "\"But if you had {i}seen{/i} what I {i}saw{/i}...\""
    m "但如果你{i}看到{/i} 我{i}看見{/i} 的景象……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5358
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ab8df3fa:

    # m "\"It felt like a threat.\""
    m "那感覺像是一種威脅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5360
translate Tchinese medicinedone_54b01709:

    # mu "\"Sam.\""
    mu "Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5361
translate Tchinese medicinedone_95990fe2:

    # mu "\"Everything here is a threat.\""
    mu "這裡的一切都是威脅。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5363
translate Tchinese medicinedone_88db99f3:

    # mu "\"But it pushed too much.\""
    mu "但它逼得太緊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5364
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9cd037c:

    # mu "\"Took too much.\""
    mu "奪走了太多。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5366
translate Tchinese medicinedone_05a97f59:

    # mu "\"Feasted too greedily.\""
    mu "吞噬得太貪婪。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5368
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eece02f5:

    # mu "\"It’s going to starve now that it can’t get back what it lost.\""
    mu "現在失去這麼多，就要挨餓了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5369
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2092c74e:

    # mu "\"Maybe that’s why it can’t come on the train with us.\""
    mu " 或許這就是它沒法跟著我們一起上火車的原因。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5371
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4bc4e03e:

    # m "\"...So what?\""
    m "……所以呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5372
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5510e066:

    # m "\"You think we’re going to be safe now, just running away?\""
    m "你覺得我們只要逃跑就安全了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5373
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d25ea2f8:

    # "He leans back and looks out the window."
    "他靠回椅背，看向窗外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5375
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9331b7cb:

    # mu "\"Safe probably isn’t the right word.\""
    mu "安全或許不是正確的形容。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5376
translate Tchinese medicinedone_941690e8:

    # m "\"Then what is?\""
    m "那什麼才是？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5377
translate Tchinese medicinedone_838effd8:

    # "Murdoch leans back in the chair, thinking."
    "Murdoch靠在椅子上思考。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5378
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ab1fb9e3:

    # "I speak again."
    "我再次開口："

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5379
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d4e2ee0c:

    # m "\"You know...\""
    m "你知道嗎……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5380
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5379dbb0:

    # m "\"The whole reason I went west looking for a better life.\""
    m "我為什麼會往西走，尋求更好的生活。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5381
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0c7f6423:

    # m "\"I always thought that if I could get away from that shithole down south I could find a way to turn things around.\""
    m "我一直以為只要逃離南邊那個鬼地方，我就能扭轉人生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5382
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2353beb3:

    # m "\"But it just seems like one small town is just the same as any other.\""
    m "但小鎮之間終究是大同小異。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5383
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19d47a65:

    # m "\"Evil is everywhere, man.\""
    m "邪惡無處不在啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5384
translate Tchinese medicinedone_038d68e7:

    # "Murdoch sits in silence for a while."
    "Murdoch沉默了一會兒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5385
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a2ed6c43:

    # "He still looks like he’s thinking."
    "好像還在思考。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5387
translate Tchinese medicinedone_edad416d:

    # mu "\"Maybe it is.\""
    mu "或許是這樣沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5388
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f7855099:

    # mu "\"...But I don’t think all evil is the same.\""
    mu "……但我覺得並非所有的邪惡都一樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5390
translate Tchinese medicinedone_14eb22f9:

    # "He breathes in."
    "他吸氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5391
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b0b35575:

    # "Then exhales."
    "然後吐氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5393
translate Tchinese medicinedone_924a4cda:

    # mu "\"Once something is over, it can never be the same again.\""
    mu "一旦某件事結束了，就永遠無法復原了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5394
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e0b71d41:

    # mu "\"No matter how convincing the imitation.\""
    mu "無論模仿得多麼相像。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5395
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0b3729d0:

    # mu "\"And that’s the one thing I think nobody on heaven or earth has any power over.\""
    mu "我認為天地間都沒有能力撼動這一點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5397
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8c91652b:

    # mu "\"It wants you back because it doesn’t want to be over.\""
    mu "它想把你拉回去，是因為它不想要終結。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5398
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c74a989f:

    # mu "\"It wants me back because it doesn’t want to be over.\""
    mu "它想把我拉回去，是因為它不想要終結。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5399
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b48fb3a8:

    # mu "\"Then once its through and done with us, it’ll look for what else is left.\""
    mu "我們跟它之間已經結束了，它就會去找剩下的事物。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5400
translate Tchinese medicinedone_569c13f6:

    # mu "\"But without an economy there isn’t going to be anymore.\""
    mu "但缺乏經濟，就什麼也沒有了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5401
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9364f9b9:

    # mu "\"Without a {i}life{/i} there isn’t going to be anymore.\""
    mu "缺少{i}生命{/i}，就什麼也沒有了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5403
translate Tchinese medicinedone_680f98a9:

    # mu "\"So I raise a glass to its overwhelming success.\""
    mu "所以我要為它取得壓倒性的成功而舉杯慶祝。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5404
translate Tchinese medicinedone_63591c38:

    # mu "\"The well of misery is tapped.\""
    mu "苦難之井已被汲盡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5405
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ca790952:

    # mu "\"There’s no reason to look back.\""
    mu "沒有理由回頭了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5407
translate Tchinese medicinedone_650c39c8:

    # mu "\"And what happened here can happen anywhere.\""
    mu "這裡發生的事，任何地方都有可能會發生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5408
translate Tchinese medicinedone_437a93a6:

    # mu "\"But the important point still stands.\""
    mu "但最重要的一點依然不變。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5409
translate Tchinese medicinedone_68930dda:

    # mu "\"The Echo I knew is no more.\""
    mu "我所知道的回音已不復存在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5410
translate Tchinese medicinedone_93c05b81:

    # mu "\"And it will never be again.\""
    mu "並且永遠不會再有了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5411
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5edf77db:

    # mu "\"No trick of the light can change that.\""
    mu "任何光線的把戲都無法改變這一點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5416
translate Tchinese medicinedone_990f9767:

    # "I look outside the window again."
    "我再次看向窗外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5417
translate Tchinese medicinedone_13d34e9d:

    # "The sky is pink now rather than red as we distance ourselves from the smoke and the fog."
    "隨著我們遠離煙霧，天空轉為粉紅而非紅色。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5418
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f989e773:

    # "The sun peaks shyly over the mountains and the shadow of saguaros bar the ground, taunting us like the light from prison cells."
    "太陽從山間探出頭來，仙人掌的影子橫在地上，呈現貌似監獄牢房的光線，彷彿在嘲諷我們。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5419
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe292fee:

    # m "\"Murdoch.\""
    m "Murdoch。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5421
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f6438c55:

    # m "\"...Are you going to be okay?\""
    m "……你還好嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5422
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1ea6e056:

    # "I see something tall in the distance."
    "我看到遠處有個高大的東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5423
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f346e2c:

    # "Probably the biggest cactus I’ve ever seen."
    "或許是我所見過最大的仙人掌。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5425
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9d1135d6:

    # "He tilts his head."
    "他歪著頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5426
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19614227:

    # "He’s noticed I’m looking out the window."
    "注意到我正望著窗外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5427
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4b37f5eb:

    # mu "\"...No.\""
    mu "……不好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5429
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3ac275e6:

    # "But he looks away from what I’m looking at, firm."
    "但他移開視線，不看我看著的東西，動作堅定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5430
translate Tchinese medicinedone_907b3998:

    # "Unfazed."
    "毫不動搖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5431
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0b767541:

    # mu "\"...But I am going to be.\""
    mu "……但我會好起來的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5439
translate Tchinese medicinedone_03720b99:

    # "For me, the easiest thing was always leaving people and places behind."
    "對我而言，與人事物分別，從來都是最簡單的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5440
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f9058659:

    # "The hard part was always finding the energy to keep on walking once you’d started."
    "啟程離去後，要找到走下去的動力，才是最難的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5441
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4306764f:

    # "I know that’s not the case for him."
    "我知道，他並不是這樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5442
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8ff0cb18:

    # "He had been betrayed by everybody close in some way."
    "所有他親近的人都背叛過他，形式各異。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5443
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2bfd747a:

    # "They stabbed him in the back in their special kind of way."
    "以各自特有的方式從他背後捅刀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5444
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bb6dec20:

    # "Soft but stern enough to draw blood."
    "柔軟卻又銳利到足以見血。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5445
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d11891f6:

    # "Never deep enough to carve muscle."
    "不會深到切開肌肉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5446
translate Tchinese medicinedone_de8db531:

    # "Sliced into a readily offered ink to dip their pens into."
    "只是切出小傷口，能輕易拿筆沾起墨水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5447
translate Tchinese medicinedone_00ce39e0:

    # "For writing in red to dictate why it was best for him to be grateful."
    "以紅字書寫，告訴他為何應該心懷感激。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5448
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1dcdb65b:

    # "Is it possible to leave behind a life like that?"
    "有人離得開這樣的人生嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5449
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fa829d8d:

    # "I had my doubts."
    "我很懷疑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5450
translate Tchinese medicinedone_113254fc:

    # "I’m not sure I could convince him that losing them was for the best."
    "我不確定能否說服他：放下才是最好的結果。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5451
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e11fb822:

    # "Some nights are much better than others."
    "有些夜晚安寧得多。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5452
translate Tchinese medicinedone_403e67d1:

    # "Ralph helped me wean him off of the harder things, but the screaming and the crying at night didn’t always make things easier."
    "Ralph有幫我讓他逐漸戒掉那些藥效強的，可夜驚和夜哭還是難以應付。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5453
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6762d995:

    # "Going on walks tends to help."
    "出去散步通常有益。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5454
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7c43b15c:

    # "Though I was surprised where he wanted to walk today."
    "不過他今天想去散步的地方，令我意外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5455
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fbdd0fc4:

    # "The beaches on the east coast can show you nothing but sand and water for miles at a time."
    "在東岸的海灘，可以看到綿延不絕的沙灘與海洋。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5456
translate Tchinese medicinedone_486fc50c:

    # "There’s no rocks or cliffs that hold you back."
    "沒有礙眼的岩石或懸崖。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5457
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b04a9e6c:

    # "It’s just you, the land, and the water."
    "只有自己、大地和海水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5458
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5c625faa:

    # "...I can’t help but wonder how no matter where I end up, there always seems to be sand beneath my feet."
    "……我不禁想道，無論我身在何方，腳下似乎總是有沙。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5463
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b7501602:

    # m "\"I’m surprised you wanted to be out here.\""
    m "我很意外你想來這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5464
translate Tchinese medicinedone_da607c2a:

    # "My companion walks beside me."
    "同伴走在我身旁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5465
translate Tchinese medicinedone_12130865:

    # "The cold of the foam washes our legs."
    "冰涼的泡沫沖刷著我們的腿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5466
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3c36a00c_1:

    # mu "\"Why?\""
    mu "為什麼？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5468
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cf8f6a4f:

    # "It sounds more like a rhetorical why."
    "聽起來比較像反問。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5469
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ca7a479e:

    # m "\"Considering you used to hate the water.\""
    m "你以前很討厭水啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5470
translate Tchinese medicinedone_64e0e5ea:

    # "He looks as though he expects more from me."
    "他好像在期待我會多說些什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5471
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ece15e6b:

    # mu "\"I don’t hate the water.\""
    mu "我不是討厭水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5472
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9c806e14:

    # mu "\"It’s hard to hate something that’s everywhere.\""
    mu "要討厭無處不在的東西也太難了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5473
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a399ed07:

    # mu "\"So why did you want me to come out here?\""
    mu "所以你為什麼想讓我來這裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5474
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3859d5c4:

    # m "\"...Because it’s low tide.\""
    m "……因為現在退潮了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5475
translate Tchinese medicinedone_75e43d96:

    # m "\"I wanted to feel the salt spray on my feet for once.\""
    m "我想體驗一次鹽水打在腳上的感覺。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5476
translate Tchinese medicinedone_11359e72:

    # "He gives me a thin smile."
    "他淡淡一笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5477
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d404daea:

    # m "\"Just kidding.\""
    m "開玩笑的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5478
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eb1327ae:

    # m "\"There’s something I want to show you.\""
    m "我想給你看個東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5479
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4346db13:

    # mu "\"...Oh?\""
    mu "……哦？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5480
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b4c3fea8:

    # m "\"It’s a surprise.\""
    m "是個驚喜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5481
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a72a725f:

    # "He keeps on walking forward."
    "他繼續往前走。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5482
translate Tchinese medicinedone_371ea4c4:

    # "He never strides too far ahead of me."
    "他從來不會走離我太遠。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5483
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fa9debf7:

    # mu "\"I don’t much care for surprises.\""
    mu "我不太喜歡驚喜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5484
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8a5b25f0:

    # m "\"I can also tell that you’re in a bad mood.\""
    m "我也看得出你心情不好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5485
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b4002846:

    # "He frowns."
    "他皺起眉頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5486
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f434203:

    # mu "\"Bad mood isn’t quite right.\""
    mu "說不上是心情不好。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5487
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4f1ba720:

    # m "\"...You’re still thinking about them aren’t you?\""
    m "……你還在想他們，沒錯吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5488
translate Tchinese medicinedone_72482a77:

    # "His expression sours."
    "他臉色苦悶。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5489
translate Tchinese medicinedone_32173eec:

    # mu "\"Thinking about who?\""
    mu "想誰？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5490
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c42c1d58:

    # m "\"Your family.\""
    m "你的家人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5491
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8ef34ec3:

    # mu "\"...You’re my family.\""
    mu "……你就是我的家人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5492
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8e7ed6f6:

    # m "\"You know what I meant.\""
    m "你知道我是指誰。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5493
translate Tchinese medicinedone_06cc8ee3:

    # m "\"...ah!\""
    m "……啊！"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5494
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8fde935f:

    # "The sudden surge of water makes me almost lose balance."
    "突然湧來的水浪害差點我失去平衡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5495
translate Tchinese medicinedone_61ad1175:

    # "Shit, this current is strong."
    "我操，這水流真強。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5496
translate Tchinese medicinedone_25e7fa9a:

    # "He opens his mouth to speak."
    "他張開嘴想說話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5497
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ac9592f_1:

    # "Then he closes it."
    "卻欲言又止。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5498
translate Tchinese medicinedone_be1fb872:

    # "He looks left to the horizon."
    "他望向左方的海平線。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5499
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b42cbeac:

    # "It’s blue and white as far as either of us can see."
    "放眼望去是一望無際的藍與白。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5500
translate Tchinese medicinedone_237bfd82:

    # mu "\"Holly called just the other day.\""
    mu "Holly前幾天打電話來了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5501
translate Tchinese medicinedone_99a34b1b:

    # "I spit on the ground."
    "我朝地上吐了口口水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5502
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2a0dc362:

    # m "\"Of course she did.\""
    m "那臭女人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5503
translate Tchinese medicinedone_782baa8d:

    # "Murdoch’s ears perk up as he listens to the wind."
    "Murdoch豎著耳朵聽風聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5504
translate Tchinese medicinedone_31e1fff8:

    # "He likes those calming noises."
    "他喜歡那些平靜的聲音。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5505
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9ba6d5e0:

    # "He’s said they’re helpful."
    "說是有益身心。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5506
translate Tchinese medicinedone_12d30e6b:

    # "I clear my throat."
    "我清了清嗓子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5507
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c37a7d32:

    # m "\"I’m surprised you still talk to her.\""
    m "我很驚訝你還跟她有聯絡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5508
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8a54fd59:

    # mu "\"I don’t.\""
    mu "我沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5509
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a8615e1f:

    # "We walk some more for a while."
    "我們又走了一會兒。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5510
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b8c74c39:

    # m "\"Then why are you answering her calls?\""
    m "那為什麼還要接她的電話？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5511
translate Tchinese medicinedone_438482bc:

    # mu "\"Because she buried mom.\""
    mu "因為她埋葬了母親。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5512
translate Tchinese medicinedone_596aae0c_2:

    # m "\"...\""
    m "……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5513
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d783cd4f:

    # "I’m starting to feel like the beach we’re walking down has no sense of time."
    "我開始覺得，我們正在散步的這片海灘，沒有時間的概念。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5514
translate Tchinese medicinedone_63b830d5:

    # "I don’t see other people."
    "沒有其他人在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5515
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3efa7cf9:

    # "No boats in the distance either."
    "遠處也沒有船隻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5516
translate Tchinese medicinedone_370662d4:

    # mu "\"She was the only one there left to do so.\""
    mu "她是唯一還留在那做這件事的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5517
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7ee237fb:

    # m "\"Where?\""
    m "在哪？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5518
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2b260e0e:

    # mu "\"Camp Rosa, next to grandma.\""
    mu "蘿莎營區，在奶奶旁邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5519
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1827191a:

    # "I grunt."
    "我悶哼一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5520
translate Tchinese medicinedone_21cff9c6:

    # m "\"That’s surprising.\""
    m "這倒是意外。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5521
translate Tchinese medicinedone_050a7e5c:

    # mu "\"...Is it?\""
    mu "……會嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5522
translate Tchinese medicinedone_395d5876:

    # "A sea hawk flies past us."
    "一隻海鷹飛過我們身旁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5523
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e2775e5f:

    # "We wait for it glide past us."
    "我們等著牠滑翔遠去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5524
translate Tchinese medicinedone_25b3956d:

    # m "\"I just figured she’s want to be by put the school.\""
    m "我只是以為她會想被葬在學校附近。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5525
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bb72c281:

    # m "\"...Wasn’t that her big accomplishment, after all?\""
    m "……畢竟，那不就是她最大的成就嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5526
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a32a6912:

    # mu "\"I think she must have grown to hate the place.\""
    mu "她一定是變得討厭那個地方了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5527
translate Tchinese medicinedone_683b780d:

    # mu "\"Knowing what she knew...\""
    mu "知道了那些事……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5528
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6d0cc441:

    # mu "\"What had really happened there, ever since its beginnings...\""
    mu "真相的來龍去脈……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5529
translate Tchinese medicinedone_30acdbaa:

    # mu "\"Plus there’s something else I know.\""
    mu "而且，我還知道了另一件事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5530
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fdfd7692:

    # mu "\"I heard a funny story.\""
    mu "我聽了個有趣的故事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5531
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5ccf82e7:

    # "A wave crashes a little too close to me."
    "一波浪打得離我非常近。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5532
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86a78f2b:

    # m "\"I’m betting it’s not that funny.\""
    m "我肯定不會覺得多有趣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5533
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9ea9be5e:

    # m "\"You know, I the funny stories I tend to prefer are the ones in the newspaper.\""
    m "你也知道，我喜歡的有趣故事是報紙上的那種。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5534
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4bf1fed2:

    # m "\"With the quippy pictures.\""
    m "帶插畫的那種。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5535
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d6e39e1d:

    # mu "\"...I heard the school burned down.\""
    mu "……我聽說學校燒掉了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5536
translate Tchinese medicinedone_45ada1ca:

    # "I inhale."
    "我吸了口氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5537
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc7b023c:

    # "Then exhale."
    "然後吐掉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5538
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dd8c6de8:

    # m "\"That sounds more like one of your funny stories, yeah.\""
    m "這確實是你會喜歡的那種吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5539
translate Tchinese medicinedone_15d80441:

    # m "\"...So, no shit?\""
    m "……真的假的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5540
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3e3aa7f:

    # mu "\"No shit.\""
    mu "真的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5541
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9ccf81b3:

    # mu "\"It really happened.\""
    mu "真的發生了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5542
translate Tchinese medicinedone_94c30ec4:

    # "I whistle."
    "我吹了聲口哨。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5543
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8f400d9d:

    # m "\"Damn...\""
    m "我靠……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5544
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0fbfc0f2:

    # "I put my paws in my pocket."
    "我把爪伸進口袋。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5545
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fd84703f:

    # m "\"...So did it happen close to when we left?\""
    m "……是在我們離開沒多久以後嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5546
translate Tchinese medicinedone_be8acbba:

    # mu "\"No.\""
    mu "不是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5547
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3e5d876:

    # mu "\"This was about ten years ago.\""
    mu "大概十年前吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5548
translate Tchinese medicinedone_95283c70:

    # m "\"Hm.\""
    m "嗯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5549
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d085c9bb:

    # "The waves rush past my legs again."
    "海浪再次沖刷我的腿。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5550
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a0df8330:

    # "I’m too deep in thought to flinch this time."
    "這次我沉浸在思緒中，不為所動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5551
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ecea795a:

    # m "\"So, we both think she did it, right?\""
    m "咱倆都覺得是她幹的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5552
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2721a605_2:

    # mu "\"I don’t know.\""
    mu "不好說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5553
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b1d8cab2:

    # mu "\"Probably.\""
    mu "大概是吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5554
translate Tchinese medicinedone_be678292:

    # mu "\"But she was old even then.\""
    mu "但那時候她也已經很老了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5555
translate Tchinese medicinedone_96bf9f5c:

    # m "\"By far not the first old person I’ve met capable of arson.\""
    m "她絕對不會是第一個縱火的老人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5556
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c16f83b0:

    # mu "\"Well, yeah.\""
    mu "這倒是。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5557
translate Tchinese medicinedone_678b38b8:

    # mu "\"I mean, she was always more careful than she was reckless.\""
    mu "只不過，她是個謹慎的人，不會馬虎。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5558
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2ea35dc7:

    # mu "\"I don’t think she’d like anybody poking around once it had been condemed.\""
    mu "在學校被判定為危樓後，她不會想要有人去亂逛的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5559
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0d5ae264:

    # mu "\"Though Dahlia tells me the county plans to rebuild it.\""
    mu "只是Dahlia告訴我，郡政府打算重建它。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5560
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a1d65da7:

    # mu "\"I can’t imagine why, considering the population’s never recovered.\""
    mu "我想不出箇中原因，人口又不見起色。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5561
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f13813b4:

    # m "\"...She’s still there too?\""
    m "……她也還在那裡？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5562
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7ff97a52:

    # mu "\"No, she’s in the capitol now.\""
    mu "沒，她現在在國會大廈了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5563
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8f536e5a:

    # mu "\"But the government has her keep in touch.\""
    mu "只是政府讓她保持聯絡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5564
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ebe714ec:

    # mu "\"Something about cross-referencing her the astronomy program for wealther areas along the west coast.\""
    mu "好像是在用她的天文項目交叉比對西岸繁榮區域什麼的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5566
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e0c22df6:

    # mu "\"...but yeah.\""
    mu "……總之。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5567
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4052fc04:

    # mu "\"Some people still live there.\""
    mu "還是有些人住在那裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5568
translate Tchinese medicinedone_58ad3a5c:

    # mu "\"It’s nothing like when we used to be there though.\""
    mu "但已經跟我們以前在的時候完全不同了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5569
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e619d0c6:

    # m "\"What, you afraid to say its name?\""
    m "怎麼，你怕呼喚它的名字？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5570
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e84afc83:

    # "The fox hums."
    "狐狸哼了一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5571
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5165e1ee:

    # mu "\"Maybe not afriad.\""
    mu "我不是害怕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5572
translate Tchinese medicinedone_19cea2ce:

    # mu "\"Just not interested.\""
    mu "只是懶得提。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5573
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3aaefbd:

    # mu "\"...Why?\""
    mu "……怎麼這麼問？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5574
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5ea5d5a1:

    # m "\"No reason.\""
    m "就想問問。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5575
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5fc3b09c:

    # mu "\"Have you ever thought of going back?\""
    mu "你有想過要回去嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5576
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a069b92f:

    # "I don’t answer immediately."
    "我沒有馬上回答。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5577
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69f20c6f:

    # m "\"I don’t think so.\""
    m "應該沒有。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5578
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d25f59f8:

    # "He stops walking."
    "他停下腳步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5579
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d5a8bfe9:

    # mu "\"Why the hesitation?\""
    mu "為什麼猶豫了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5580
translate Tchinese medicinedone_63033175:

    # m "\"Well...\""
    m "這個嘛……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5581
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe261402:

    # "I stop walking too."
    "我也停下腳步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5582
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a4faf6ec:

    # m "\"I just can’t help but think about how there’s still people there who I left behind.\""
    m "我只是忍不住會想，那裡還有我拋下的人在。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5583
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1c1409a4:

    # m "\"People who I’m not sure got out, I mean.\""
    m "我不清楚有沒有逃掉的那些人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5584
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7f73373a:

    # mu "\"If they did, there might be leads in Payton.\""
    mu "如果成功脫身了，在沛頓可能會有線索。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5585
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f40f7c3:

    # m "\"Maybe.\""
    m "或許吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5586
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ea32202c:

    # m "\"Payton’s a long ass way away to go though, asking about people folks might not even remember.\""
    m "不過，要去找不見得有人知道的人，沛頓還真夠遠的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5587
translate Tchinese medicinedone_135849b9:

    # "Murdoch hums again."
    "Murdoch又哼了一聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5588
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f9ec9930:

    # mu "\"I thought you had contacts still?\""
    mu "我以為你還有人脈啊？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5589
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1a4f8974:

    # m "\"Not that many.\""
    m "沒多少。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5590
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b2d06d1f:

    # mu "\"What about the former Hip employees?\""
    mu "Hip酒館的前員工呢？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5591
translate Tchinese medicinedone_39103fd8:

    # m "\"I still don’t know what happened to Harlan, though I imagine that meeting of the minds would involve catching the end of my crowbar than precious memories.\""
    m "我還是不知道Harlan的下落，但真見到面，他就要跟我的翹棍親密談談過往了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5592
translate Tchinese medicinedone_92a53b4b:

    # m "\"Plus, Dora’s gone, but she was old before we got old.\""
    m "Dora也已經走了，她在我們變老之前就已經很老了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5593
translate Tchinese medicinedone_48c3a196:

    # m "\"Cynthia told me about the ceremony a few years ago.\""
    m "Cynthia幾年前跟我說過那場告別式。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5594
translate Tchinese medicinedone_903b5bda:

    # m "\"The brothel never really recovered in the new location.\""
    m "娼館在新地方沒能重現過往的輝煌。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5595
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8bece214:

    # mu "\"They don’t seem like easy things to keep going.\""
    mu "那行業本就不容易維持下去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5596
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e02fa66f:

    # m "\"Not anymore at least.\""
    m 至少現在很難了。""

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5597
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f079222:

    # m "\"People are less private nowadays.\""
    m "現代人沒那麼注重隱私。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5598
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dc5f2981:

    # m "\"Seems like everybody’s a lot less inclined to mind their own damn business.\""
    m "時代是越來越開放囉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5599
translate Tchinese medicinedone_44dc0332:

    # m "\"...At least Cynthia’s found work though.\""
    m "……至少Cynthia找到工作了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5600
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f138ccfb:

    # m "\"Runs a bar.\""
    m "經營一家酒吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5601
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a8e05def:

    # mu "\"What kind of bar?\""
    mu "什麼樣的酒吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5602
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a86dd973:

    # m "\"The kind she likes.\""
    m "她喜歡的那種。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5603
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4fa34eb5:

    # m "\"More focused on new kinds of music.\""
    m "更注重流行音樂。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5604
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d655c809:

    # mu "\"Sounds respectable.\""
    mu "聽起來挺正經的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5605
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0bc798f2:

    # mu "\"You think about going?\""
    mu "你有想過去看看嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5606
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d10acd87:

    # m "\"Not really my kind of place.\""
    m "我不太喜歡那種地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5607
translate Tchinese medicinedone_10c193b4:

    # m "\"Would be nice to stop by if I have the time.\""
    m "有時間的話，順道去看看也還行。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5608
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1f803f5e:

    # mu "\"I sort of miss the less respectable places we used to go.\""
    mu "我有點懷念我們以前去的那些不太正經的地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5609
translate Tchinese medicinedone_709c2103:

    # "My lips tighten a little."
    "我嘴唇稍稍抿緊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5610
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b93e3427:

    # m "\"I guess there were some good parts.\""
    m "那確實還是有一些不錯的部分。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5611
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d7330879:

    # mu "\"There were great parts Sam.\""
    mu "簡直堪稱美好啊，Sam。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5612
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b9ef9211:

    # m "\"...Is that why you like being stuck there again?\""
    m "……所以你又想被困在那了？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5613
translate Tchinese medicinedone_03f4ed4f:

    # mu "\"...You mean in the fantasies?\""
    mu "……你說的是在幻想中吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5614
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c806ebc0_1:

    # m "\"Yeah.\""
    m "對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5615
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5f569ba7:

    # m "\"The fantasies.\""
    m "那些幻想。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5616
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c2dddd92:

    # "He frowns a bit."
    "他微微皺眉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5617
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b95948ef:

    # mu "\"Sometimes it feels like time is leaving us behind.\""
    mu "有時候，感覺時間把我們拋在了後頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5618
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ccac78a7:

    # mu "\"You keep me feeling young.\""
    mu "你讓我一直覺得自己還年輕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5619
translate Tchinese medicinedone_12c56faa:

    # m "\"...Even though I’m a mean old man?\""
    m "……我都已經是個臭老頭了耶？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5620
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e19eeae9:

    # "He smirks."
    "他撇嘴一笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5621
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3753a072:

    # m "\"At least I always know what you’re thinking.\""
    m "至少我總是知道你在想什麼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5622
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8edbbbd1:

    # mu "\"...Remember what I told you all those years ago?\""
    mu "……還記得我多年前告訴你的話嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5623
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ec625e3f:

    # mu "\"Before the disaster?\""
    mu "災難發生之前的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5624
translate Tchinese medicinedone_784671aa:

    # "He’s looking at me real careful."
    "他很嚴肅地望著我。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5625
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4417cec2:

    # "I can tell this is important."
    "我看得出這很重要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5626
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a39b0a86:

    # m "\"You told me a lot of things.\""
    m "你告訴過我很多事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5627
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc01b7fc:

    # m "\"...Would you be mad if I said I didn’t?\""
    m "……要是我說不記得了，你會生氣嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5628
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8c6f40dc:

    # mu "\"I mean in the tailor shop.\""
    mu "我指的是去裁縫店的時候。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5629
translate Tchinese medicinedone_df4a6852:

    # mu "\"Before the wedding.\""
    mu "婚禮之前那次。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5630
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bf78435b:

    # m "\"...vaguely.\""
    m "……有點印象。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5631
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1b722262:

    # m "\"Again, that was a long week.\""
    m "但那禮拜發生的事實在太多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5632
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3716a237:

    # "He puts his arms around my waist."
    "他雙臂環住我的腰。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5633
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e51c71f6:

    # "Then rests his head on the crook of my neck."
    "把頭靠在我頸窩上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5634
translate Tchinese medicinedone_630ee498:

    # mu "\"I was mostly going to apologize.\""
    mu "我主要是想道歉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5635
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3ac2aab2:

    # "I put my hand around his head and stroke him."
    "我把手放在他頭上輕撫他的毛髮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5636
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a5dc0177:

    # m "\"You could be more like me and just do less of that.\""
    m "你可以像我一樣，少做點道歉賠罪之類的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5637
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5aa46ce1:

    # mu "\"This one’s important.\""
    mu "這次很重要。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5638
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bdf803a5:

    # "I keep petting him."
    "我繼續撫摸他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5639
translate Tchinese medicinedone_df4ad979:

    # m "\"Mhm.\""
    m "嗯哼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5640
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b4896a85:

    # "He pulls away, slowly."
    "他緩緩退開。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5641
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f79ebf72:

    # mu "\"Just listen, and then I won’t talk about it again.\""
    mu "聽我說完，以後我都不會再提了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5642
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d2aec93d:

    # m "\"Mmhm.\""
    m "嗯哼。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5643
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cf55fb8d:

    # "He holds onto my wrists."
    "他握住我雙手手腕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5644
translate Tchinese medicinedone_72a91432:

    # mu "\"I need to say this.\""
    mu "我一定要說出來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5645
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b295c319:

    # m "\"...Go on?\""
    m "……那就說啊？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5646
translate Tchinese medicinedone_40d7c98d:

    # "He blows out a puff of air."
    "他吐出一口氣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5647
translate Tchinese medicinedone_06665e1e:

    # mu "\"Back then I thought I could put myself though anything if I found the right man to inspire me.\""
    mu "當時，我以為只要找到對的人來激勵我，我就能承受任何事情。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5648
translate Tchinese medicinedone_abeb3223:

    # mu "\"I chased after you like I chased a dream.\""
    mu "我像在追夢一樣追求你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5649
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fe4c3ca7:

    # mu "\"Sharing as much of myself with somebody I barely knew wasn’t okay.\""
    mu "我不該向一位剛認識的人吐那麼多苦水。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5650
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2a3cf8da:

    # mu "\"Getting to know the real you made it feel like I wasn’t floating anymore.\""
    mu "熟悉真正的你，讓我感覺自己不再載浮載沉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5651
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3a4a221:

    # mu "\"That’s part of why I don’t hate being in or around the water anymore.\""
    mu "我不再討厭待在水邊或水裡，也有這個原因。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5652
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d53abb71:

    # mu "\"Whether you believe it or not, I’m pretty sure that you saved my life.\""
    mu "信不信由你，但我很確定你拯救了我的人生。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5653
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a7983b95:

    # mu "\"Waking up every morning feels like a joy rather than an obligation.\""
    mu "在每天早上醒來都是一種快樂，而不是義務。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5654
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a197549d:

    # m "\"Even when that’s hard.\""
    m "雖然還是很難爬起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5655
translate Tchinese medicinedone_abc1a553:

    # m "\"I know.\""
    m "這我都知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5656
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d8ef62c4:

    # mu "\"But I don’t know if your realize how much knowing that bothers me.\""
    mu "但你有沒有意識到，你知道這件事令我有多困擾？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5657
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ef8907e:

    # "He lets go of my wrists."
    "他鬆開我的手腕。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5658
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d7fe25cf:

    # mu "\"I don’t think I can stand to be pitied.\""
    mu "我不喜歡受人憐憫。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5659
translate Tchinese medicinedone_088db350:

    # "I rub the back of my neck, nodding."
    "我揉了揉後頸，點了頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5660
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c2e90a27:

    # m "\"...most people probably get pitied for something or other.\""
    m "……大多人總會因為某些原因被人憐憫的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5661
translate Tchinese medicinedone_41130f96:

    # mu "\"But I don’t think I could stand being pitied by you.\""
    mu "但是被你憐憫，我忍不了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5662
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c81cd62b:

    # mu "\"If I trapped you into something because of guilt, it would make me no better than my father.\""
    mu "要是你因為愧疚而被我拴著，那我就跟我爸沒兩樣了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5663
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3b90b008:

    # m "\"I don’t mean any offense by this.\""
    m "那真不好意思。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5664
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3f1b922d:

    # m "\"But you’re not nearly as good at guilting me than I am at guilting myself.\""
    m "想讓我有罪惡感，你跟我自己比起來還差得遠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5665
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0f08a553:

    # m "\"I know we never really talked about it.\""
    m "我知道我們沒怎麼談過這件事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5666
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d5c7ebeb:

    # m "\"But I had to kill somebody that I loved.\""
    m "但我曾經不得不殺死一個我愛過的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5667
translate Tchinese medicinedone_07dbecae:

    # m "\"Because he made me know that it was going to be either him or me.\""
    m "因為他讓我知道，結局不是他死就是我活。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5668
translate Tchinese medicinedone_82818fb7:

    # m "\"I know it was an accident, know now that what I had to do was self-defense, but...\""
    m "我理解那是意外，如今也知道那算是自衛，可是……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5669
translate Tchinese medicinedone_eb8d10bc:

    # m "\"It doesn’t change the fact that it happened.\""
    m "覆水難收。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5670
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fee445cf:

    # m "\"And back then I thought about doing it to you too at points.\""
    m "當時我也有幾次想對你下手。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5671
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7340000e:

    # mu "\"So why didn’t you?\""
    mu "那為什麼沒有？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5672
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8e4943bd:

    # m "\"Because I needed you too.\""
    m "因為我也需要你。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5673
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a8b54d86:

    # m "\"Who the hell else in this world was gonna do math for me?\""
    m "這世上還有誰能幫我算數？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5674
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1e4ee8f9:

    # "He sputters."
    "他噗嗤一笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5675
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bef1063b:

    # "We both start laughing."
    "我倆都笑了起來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5676
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4cb3e490:

    # "It was meant to be just a little tease, but he starts laughing in a really {i}stupid{/i} way that keeps me going."
    "本來只是一番調侃，他卻笑成了一副{i}傻樣{/i}，害我也被逗笑。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5677
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ae743a75:

    # "We try to stop several times."
    "好幾次想停下來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5678
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7fb6c298:

    # "But it just keeps going."
    "但就是笑個不停。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5679
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5e8ecad6:

    # "It’s getting hard to breathe."
    "都快喘不過氣了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5680
translate Tchinese medicinedone_76203864:

    # m "\"I’m not with you because I needed somebody to save.\""
    m "我跟你在一起，不是因為我想拯救人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5681
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8cac3404:

    # m "\"It’s because you make things fun.\""
    m "而是因為你讓一切有了樂趣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5682
translate Tchinese medicinedone_95653826:

    # m "\"Especially things that have no right to be.\""
    m "尤其是那些本不該有趣的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5683
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a08d746f:

    # m "\"I’ll never get tired of you Murdoch Byrnes.\""
    m "我永遠都不會厭倦你，Murdoch Byrnes。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5684
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4c9e7c68:

    # m "\"Even if I never want to hear another damn thing about serial dilutions in my life.\""
    m "雖說我這輩子都不想再聽到什麼連續稀釋法了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5685
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3bafcef9:

    # m "\"Now shut your yapping and come just a little further.\""
    m "現在就別再多嘴了，再跟我走遠一點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5687
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86754fdd:

    # raunk "\"Ayers?\""
    raunk "Ayers？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5688
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2d468b99:

    # raunk "\"Did you bring the Birthday lad?\""
    raunk "你把壽星帶來了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5689
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3e4b9fd5:

    # m "\"I sure did.\""
    m "那當然。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5690
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b1bf3952:

    # mu "\"Is that Ralph I hear over the hill?\""
    mu "山丘那邊的聲音是Ralph嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5691
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b020762d:

    # ra "\"Sure is.\""
    ra "沒錯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5692
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9c22f18b:

    # mu "\"Did you pick the location then?\""
    mu "那地點是你選的？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5693
translate Tchinese medicinedone_dbdb0a44:

    # ra "\"That I did.\""
    ra "是我選的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5694
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fac1372f:

    # mu "\"If you wanted to give me a gift in person, you could have picked the diner.\""
    mu "你要想親自送我禮物，大可選在餐廳啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5695
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4308b682:

    # ra "\"Wouldn’t suit my needs.\""
    ra "那不符合我的需求。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5696
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7ac96207:

    # mu "\"It’s a remote location.\""
    mu "這裡很偏僻。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5697
translate Tchinese medicinedone_20fa3c1d:

    # mu "\"Reminds me of old times.\""
    mu "讓我想起以前的日子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5698
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5635a6f2:

    # mu "\"...Worse times.\""
    mu "……苦日子。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5699
translate Tchinese medicinedone_58f55354:

    # ra "\"No moping on your birthday.\""
    ra "生日這天別給我悶悶不樂的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5700
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d1ac3b6f:

    # ra "\"You’re in the prime of your life.\""
    ra "你可是正值人生巔峰時期啊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5701
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4917ee90:

    # mu "\"I’m sixty-two.\""
    mu "我都六十二了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5702
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ed0714bd:

    # ra "\"Not to old for fireworks I hope?\""
    ra "還沒老到不能放煙火吧？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5703
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fc254f89:

    # mu "\"...You made bottle rockets?\""
    mu "……你做了瓶子火箭？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5704
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3720dbb7:

    # ra "\"Aye.\""
    ra "對。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5705
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ddc169a:

    # ra "\"It was because I was nosy as usual.\""
    ra "因為我還是老樣子愛管閒事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5706
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc3ddf23:

    # ra "\"When I heard that your mum died I knew it would make all of those bad feelings come back.\""
    ra "聽說你母親過世，我就知道你又要鬱鬱寡歡了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5707
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b241f0e3:

    # mu "\"They do.\""
    mu "還真的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5708
translate Tchinese medicinedone_952a0776:

    # mu "\"I like to think that I’d forget them a little more each year.\""
    mu "我以為會一年年逐漸忘懷。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5709
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5c3bdbb0:

    # mu "\"But when I heard Holly’s voice on the phone again, it was like somebody painted the whole thing in my head again.\""
    mu "但一聽到電話裡Holly的聲音，我就感覺腦海裡又重演了一遍那些事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5710
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d2ad778b:

    # mu "\"It was...\""
    mu "非常……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5711
translate Tchinese medicinedone_87e864e9:

    # mu "\"Vivid.\""
    mu "鮮明。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5712
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c454ff00:

    # mu "\"It’s like you’re going back in time but nobody asked if you wanted to be there.\""
    mu "像是不由分說地被拉回過去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5713
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2f9e82a3:

    # ra "\"I unfortunately know what you mean.\""
    ra "很不幸，我明白你的感受。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5714
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69cf32dd:

    # ra "\"But then I got to thinking about the fireworks, and the bottle rocket that you said Seamus never got to light...\""
    ra "但後來我想到了煙火，還有你說過Seamus從來沒機會點燃的那個瓶子火箭……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5715
translate Tchinese medicinedone_50659146:

    # ra "\"And that’s, ah.\""
    ra "我就，嗯……"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5716
translate Tchinese medicinedone_77320c2b:

    # ra "\"I remembered the recipe.\""
    ra "想起了配方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5717
translate Tchinese medicinedone_46063d95:

    # ra "\"I mean the {i}exact{/i} recipe.\""
    ra "{i}一模一樣的{/i}配方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5718
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f0a2e566:

    # "Sitting on a stone facing the ocean, we see a bottle rocket sticking out of a coca cola bottle."
    "坐在面向大海的岩石上，一個可口可樂瓶火箭就在眼前。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5719
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c7290342:

    # "The words scrawled on the side were {i}Goodbye Seamus.{/i}"
    "側邊草草寫著「永別了 Seamus」。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5720
translate Tchinese medicinedone_aa044b29:

    # ra "\"I think he’s overdue for a proper send off.\""
    ra "他老早就該有個正式的送別會了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5721
translate Tchinese medicinedone_89c3f7f8:

    # "Ralph hands Murdoch a lighter."
    "Ralph遞給Murdoch一個打火機。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5722
translate Tchinese medicinedone_23723b15:

    # "Tears splash the metal."
    "眼淚濺在金屬上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5724
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5d9beb1e:

    # "He crouches down and ignites a spark."
    "他蹲下來點燃火花。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5726
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0fdd2dad:

    # "The twine sparks and Ralph tells me to stand back."
    "引線冒出火花，Ralph叫我站遠一點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5728
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b38ac124:

    # "It goes into the sky with a whizz."
    "它咻地一聲竄上天空。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5729
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8a19f50f:

    # "I think it’s swallowed by the sea before I hear {nw}"
    "咻聲被浪聲沒過{nw}"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5731
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9dc0e51a:

    # extend "the pop, then see the first explosion of gold, then the crimson spiral that ends in a blue burst."
    extend "然後發出爆炸聲，一道金光炸裂，接著轉為深紅螺旋，最後以藍色綻放作結"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5732
translate Tchinese medicinedone_176baa56:

    # "It ends far quicker than I thought it would."
    "結束得遠比我想像中要快。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5734
translate Tchinese medicinedone_076faf42:

    # "But Murdoch is still staring at the sea."
    "但Murdoch依然望著大海。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5735
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5042b639:

    # ra "\"If he needed a signal to guide his soul home, then I hope he finds it.\""
    ra "要是有需要，希望他能找到指引靈魂回家的信號。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5736
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69927cfc:

    # "Murdoch shakes his head."
    "Murdoch搖搖頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5737
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b320cf33:

    # mu "\"The only comfort I feel is that if he doesn’t exist anymore, his soul can’t remember what was done to him.\""
    mu "我唯一的慰藉是，如果他已經不存在了，靈魂就不會記得發生在他身上的事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5738
translate Tchinese medicinedone_add033e9:

    # mu "\"If he only lives through me as a ghost, from this day forward, I will only remember him laughing.\""
    mu "要是他只能鬼魂的形式活在我心中，那從今天起，我會只記得他的笑容。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5748
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7bc0cd6e:

    # "In an old manor, in an even older neighborhood, a large funeral has just taken place."
    "在十分老舊的街區上，一間老宅邸中，剛辦完一場盛大的葬禮。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5749
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b8650d2c:

    # "The esteemed physicist Murdoch Byrnes has lived to the age of eighty-one, known mostly for his advancements in theoretical and practical fiber optics technology."
    "備受尊崇的物理學家Murdoch Byrnes活到了八十一歲，主要以在理論與實用光纖技術上的貢獻聞名。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5752
translate Tchinese medicinedone_87b298bc:

    # "The last rites have been given."
    "最後的告別式已經結束。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5753
translate Tchinese medicinedone_40d20a3f:

    # "The crowd has dispersed."
    "人群散去。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5754
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3f0c7381:

    # "But a smaller crowd remains once the clergyman has left the building."
    "但在牧師離開建築後，還有一小群人留下。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5755
translate Tchinese medicinedone_884fc6f9:

    # "An old vixen waits in the reception hall where the wake is held."
    "一隻老雌狐在舉行守靈的接待廳等待。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5756
translate Tchinese medicinedone_acc6eedf:

    # "Her eyes are occluded by dark shades."
    "雙眼被深色面紗遮住。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5757
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f5148a0d:

    # "The only part of her that isn’t covered my clothing is her snout."
    "吻部是她身上唯一沒有被衣物遮蓋的部位。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5758
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f4cf41b1:

    # "A racket goes on outside the front door."
    "前門外傳來一陣吵鬧聲。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5759
translate Tchinese medicinedone_921eac05:

    # "A young man guarding the front argues fastidiously with an older woman."
    "門口的一個年輕男性守衛正與一位年長女性激烈爭執。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5760
translate Tchinese medicinedone_43f65014:

    # "Jim Sterling paces with some trepidation."
    "Jim Sterling略顯不安地踱步。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5761
translate Tchinese medicinedone_69864409:

    # dh "\"Hello, Jim.\""
    dh "你好，Jim。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5762
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8b79b587:

    # "The silver fox flinches when he hears her voice."
    "銀狐被她的聲音嚇了一跳。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5763
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0ed0063e:

    # ji "\"Thank you for coming, Dahlia.\""
    ji "謝謝妳來，Dahlia。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5764
translate Tchinese medicinedone_742d649e:

    # ji "\"In frankness I wasn’t sure that you would.\""
    ji "其實，我太不確定妳會不會來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5765
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b445d9d8:

    # dh "\"...You’ll need me before the end of the day.\""
    dh "……今天你會需要我的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5766
translate Tchinese medicinedone_20873a77:

    # "She looks to the front door."
    "她看向前門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5767
translate Tchinese medicinedone_437d738e:

    # dh "\"You should let her in too.\""
    dh "你也該放她進來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5768
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cc02c915:

    # dh "\"She had just as much right to be here as anybody.\""
    dh "她跟其他人一樣，有權出現在這裡。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5769
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7916d5e4:

    # dh "\"We’ll need her before the end of the day.\""
    dh "今天我們會需要她的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5770
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35463ece:

    # "Jim scowls, then nods."
    "Jim皺起臉，然後點頭。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5771
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5a35e276:

    # bl "\"I’ll wait for you in the car, Melissa.\""
    bl "我會在車上等妳，Melissa。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5772
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ebaa90a0:

    # "The black cat walks through the door, clopping in heels and a slim grey pencil skirt suit."
    "黑貓穿著貼身灰色窄身裙套裝，踩著高跟鞋聲走進門。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5773
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6a34c0d6:

    # "She stares at the small crowd with the one eye that her veil isn’t hiding."
    "她用面紗沒遮住的那隻眼盯著一這小群人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5774
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6e54b80e:

    # "Finally, it rests on Jim."
    "最後目光停在Jim身上。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5775
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a1e83471:

    # bl "\"If the deal is that we show up each time one of us dies, you need to keep your crackers in line.\""
    bl "既然說好我們每次有人死掉就要會面，你還不管好你那群蠢貨。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5776
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9896682f:

    # ji "\"Understood.\""
    ji "知道了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5777
translate Tchinese medicinedone_337c4287:

    # bl "\"Regardless, I‘m here.\""
    bl "反正我是來了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5778
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3c547a64:

    # bl "\"Drove half the way across the country to do it but let’s hear the reason.\""
    bl "我開了大半個國家的車來的，但先聽聽理由是什麼吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5780
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0bfddbeb:

    # ra "\"Do you remember me, Miss Washington?\""
    ra "妳還記得我嗎，Washington女士？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5780
translate Tchinese medicinedone_86854fce:

    # bl "\"Yeah.\""
    bl "嗯。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5781
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f2ec9720:

    # bl "\"Even after all these years, I’d remember that scrawny ass anywhere.\""
    bl "過了這麼多年，我還是能一眼認出你那瘦巴巴的屁股。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5782
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ea3102ca:

    # dh "\"The point is that we are among the few living people left who have had a first encounter with an extra-terrestrial.\""
    dh "重點是，我們是少數曾與外星生物有過初次接觸，並且還活著的人。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5783
translate Tchinese medicinedone_151c671e:

    # dh "\"And now one of our members is diminished.\""
    dh "而現在，我們其中一位成員已經逝去了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5784
translate Tchinese medicinedone_0fc1f726:

    # ra "\"In honesty I don’t think he cared.\""
    ra "實話實說，我不覺得他會在意。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5785
translate Tchinese medicinedone_411910d9:

    # ra "\"He saw enough.\""
    ra "他看得夠多了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5786
translate Tchinese medicinedone_01b93d96:

    # ra "\"He had enough.\""
    ra "他已經受夠了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5787
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ae5768d6:

    # ra "\"Now he’s somewhere it can’t reach him.\""
    ra "他已經去了那東西碰不到的地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5788
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bdc0c861:

    # dh "\"That’s what we’re here to check for.\""
    dh "我們就是要來確認這點的。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5789
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9604b05d:

    # dh "\"Is anything wrong, Blithe?\""
    dh "有什麼不對勁嗎，Blithe？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5790
translate Tchinese medicinedone_944f16f3:

    # "The cat looks at the molding and the state of the manor."
    "黑貓打量宅邸的裝飾和狀態。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5791
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e5065ab7:

    # bl "\"I see a lot of wrong, but not the kind that comes from the supernatural.\""
    bl "不對勁的地方多了去了，不過都跟超自然無關。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5792
translate Tchinese medicinedone_53a2d851:

    # dh "\"I need you to focus.\""
    dh "麻煩妳認真點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5793
translate Tchinese medicinedone_4ca156e4:

    # dh "\"We’re dealing with a highly active force that can engage in physical and temporal displacement, induce psychosis, and pollute the very light that touches our skin.\""
    dh "我們面對的是一股高度活躍的力量。它能實行物理與時間位移、誘發精神問題，還能污染照射我們皮膚的光線。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5794
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35606c8f:

    # dh "\"A thing that we know does not necessarily have to be limited to one space.\""
    dh "我們知道，那東西不一定受限於一個空間。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5795
translate Tchinese medicinedone_af8d1ca5:

    # bl "\"Again, I don’t see or sense anything.\""
    bl "總之，我是沒看到或感覺到任何東西。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5796
translate Tchinese medicinedone_bb53e907:

    # bl "\"Though it’s not like the things I can do just turn themselves on.\""
    bl "不過，我的能力也不是想發動就發動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5797
translate Tchinese medicinedone_87d2ba62:

    # bl "\"They either happen or they don’t.\""
    bl "可遇不可求。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5798
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d23206bd:

    # bl "\"And considering he’s your brother, I’d think you’d be bowing down to those stars you worship out of thanks.\""
    bl "再說，既然他是你哥，妳反倒會對妳崇拜的那些星星感恩戴德吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5799
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fdd41664:

    # dh "\"Then I’ll take this as a win.\""
    dh "那我就當是我們贏了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5800
translate Tchinese medicinedone_834266e3:

    # dh "\"You’re one step closer to paying off your debt, Miss Washington.\""
    dh "妳又向還清債務更進一步了呢，Washington女士。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5801
translate Tchinese medicinedone_daf6565f:

    # bl "\"As much as I like to bitch I still would have come.\""
    bl "我是很想抱怨，但我本來就打算過來。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5802
translate Tchinese medicinedone_30eb427d:

    # bl "\"That thing was not our friend.\""
    bl "那東西不是我們的朋友。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5803
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a60cbff6:

    # bl "\"We’re all still at risk while it lives.\""
    bl "只要它還活著，我們就還身陷危險。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5804
translate Tchinese medicinedone_61274555:

    # bl "\"If we can call it alive.\""
    bl "如果能稱作活著的話。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5805
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d3226df4:

    # ji "\"Even if it’s not alive it likely replicates through crystalization.\""
    ji "就算不是活物，也有可能透過結晶化自我複製。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5806
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c84739a2:

    # ra "\"Anyway I’m going to be frank about what I think.\""
    ra "總而言之，我就直說了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5807
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a02df75e:

    # ra "\"I don’t care about what’s back in Echo.\""
    ra "我才不在乎回音那邊是怎樣。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5808
translate Tchinese medicinedone_14b927d2:

    # ra "\"My best friend just died.\""
    ra "我最好的朋友剛剛過世。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5809
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2a7f170a:

    # ra "\"The only reason I’m here is that I’m making sure you put his body where he asked you to.\""
    ra "我來這裡的唯一原因，就是要確保你們把他安置在他要求的地方。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5810
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e6cff172:

    # ji "\"I’m not sure why you think you were the only one who cared about him.\""
    ji "我不懂你憑什麼覺得只有你在乎他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5811
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9e92e023:

    # ra "\"I didn’t say that.\""
    ra "我又沒這麼說。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5812
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6d0e429e:

    # ji "\"But I am going to make sure you do right by him.\""
    ji "但我一定會確保你正確對待他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5813
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2c55950c:

    # ra "\"I know about all the little favors he kept doing for you in exchange for the shelter.\""
    ra "我知道他為了換取庇護，都為你做了什麼事情。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5814
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1427dd58:

    # ji "\"You don’t know actually know as much as you think you do.\""
    ji "其實你知道的也不過就是一部分。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5815
translate Tchinese medicinedone_28936e21:

    # ji "\"Pick your next words carefully if you don’t want to upset me anymore than you have.\""
    ji "要是不想惹我更不爽，嘴巴最好放乾淨點。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5816
translate Tchinese medicinedone_cfed47f1:

    # ji "\"I just need assurance on thing.\""
    ji "我只是想要確保一件事。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5817
translate Tchinese medicinedone_14ecdf46:

    # ra "\"He wanted to be placed next to Sam.\""
    ra "他希望被安葬在Sam身旁。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5818
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c4df1f25:

    # ra "\"Are you going to respect that?\""
    ra "你能尊重這一點嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5819
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fdd38d00:

    # ji "\"Like Sam, he requested cremation.\""
    ji "他和Sam一樣，要求火化。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5820
translate Tchinese medicinedone_e9a073dd:

    # ji "\"We have plenty of space for him in the Sterling Mausoleum, next to the other ashes.\""
    ji "在Sterling家族的墓園，其他骨灰旁還有不少位置能安放他。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5821
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1418f2fb:

    # ji "\"That being said, none of us are actually his kin.\""
    ji "話雖如此，我們都不能算是他的親屬。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5822
translate Tchinese medicinedone_76574f26:

    # ji "\"Samuel had no close living relatives, so nobody could get in the way of that decision.\""
    ji "Samuel沒有近親，所以沒人妨礙他的決定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5823
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d22bf737:

    # ji "\"State law mandates that the relatives decide.\""
    ji "州法律規定要由親屬決定。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5824
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9f1dc046:

    # "All eyes turned Dahlia."
    "所有目光都轉向Dahlia。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5825
translate Tchinese medicinedone_6f4d5ecd:

    # "The vixen takes off her glasses and folds them into her hands."
    "雌狐摘下眼鏡，折起握在手中。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5826
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c5090945:

    # dh "\"On the behalf of Holly, she has recommended that his body be placed next to his mother in Camp Rosa.\""
    dh "我來轉達Holly的意向：她建議安放在蘿莎營地，他的母親旁邊。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5827
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3ec3ad08:

    # ji "\"Of course.\""
    ji "我就知道。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5828
translate Tchinese medicinedone_fbde4f82:

    # ra "\"And on behalf of me, you can tell Holly to go fuck herself.\""
    ra "而我的意向是，轉告Holly叫她吃屎去吧。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5829
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3c0a4e74:

    # dh "\"Keep in mind that I can contest her wishes.\""
    dh "別忘了，我有權反對她的意願。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5830
translate Tchinese medicinedone_3c0d4902:

    # dh "\"I can delay her long enough to ensure he gets his cremation.\""
    dh "我可以拖延夠久，確保他能順利火化。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5831
translate Tchinese medicinedone_8911ba41:

    # dh "\"Whether or not they will default to her because she is the elder, I’m not certain.\""
    dh "至於法律是否會因她年長而偏向她，我說不準。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5832
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ad01871b:

    # dh "\"Like always, she expects to get her way with little resistance.\""
    dh "一如既往，她預期自己能夠輕易得逞。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5833
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9affd98f:

    # dh "\"Which means she made the mistake not to travel.\""
    dh "所以採取了沒有親自前來的錯誤行動。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5834
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f0d2d801:

    # dh "\"Do with this information what you will.\""
    dh "如何運用這條情報，就看你們的造化了。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5835
translate Tchinese medicinedone_a45af6a0:

    # dh "\"I’m going to say goodbye to him one more time.\""
    dh "我要再跟他道別一次。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5836
translate Tchinese medicinedone_9652ab5d:

    # dh "\"Though I’d like to spend the night here.\""
    dh "不過，我希望能在這裡過夜。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5837
translate Tchinese medicinedone_35cd778d:

    # dh "\"Have you prepared space for myself, Miss Washington, and Miss Boike?\""
    dh "你為我、Washington女士和Boike女士準備好房間了嗎？"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5838
translate Tchinese medicinedone_f6f41292:

    # ji "\"Yes, I’ll have the servants can throw something together.\""
    ji "好，我會讓僕人準備。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5839
translate Tchinese medicinedone_ff99ff7e:

    # ji "\"Now if you’ll excuse me, I would like to mourn properly.\""
    ji "我就先失陪了，我想好好哀悼一番。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5840
translate Tchinese medicinedone_2e5d6171:

    # ji "\"There’s a lot of drinking I’d like to get through tonight.\""
    ji "今晚我要喝個爛醉。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5844
translate Tchinese medicinedone_5dd3b801:

    # "Jim Sterling awoke to one of the stronger headaches he had had in his life."
    "Jim Sterling醒來時，感受到了他人生中前幾嚴重的頭痛。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5845
translate Tchinese medicinedone_d9f73774:

    # "News from a servant announced Holly Byrnes' intentions to reclaim the remains of her brother."
    "僕人帶來消息，表示Holly Byrnes有意取回她弟弟的遺骸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5845
translate Tchinese medicinedone_7a851ac8:

    # "He found himself lamenting being old rather than time ill spent."
    "他發現，自己哀嘆的是上了年紀，而不是虛度的光陰。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5846
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b396dd8f:

    # "Although he worried for what would happen to his lands with the consideration that he had never married, and never had children of his own, he was at least relieved that she would have no say over the ashes of the only member of that family which he did love."
    "有鑑於他從未結婚生子，他是很擔心自家土地以後會如何，但他至少鬆了口氣，因為她對他在那家族中唯一心愛的成員的骨灰不具發言權。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5847
translate Tchinese medicinedone_855b8a07:

    # "Blithe Washington reported nothing strange that night near Murdoch’s body."
    "根據Blithe Washington的報告，當晚在Murdoch遺體附近並無發現任何異狀。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5848
translate Tchinese medicinedone_1c2366e8:

    # "But a small pyre was constructed on that island within the hour of the announcement."
    "但在消息宣布後一小時內，那座島上就建起了一個小小的火葬堆。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5849
translate Tchinese medicinedone_b3e0fbfc:

    # "After several days of ignoring the authorities, Jim Sterling said that a family friend had taken the remains of Murdoch Byrnes and Samuel Ayers."
    "在無視當局好幾天後，Jim Sterling表示一位家族友人已經取走了Murdoch Byrnes和Samuel Ayers的遺骸。"

# game/murdochroute4b.rpy:5853
translate Tchinese medicinedone_c29a8f59:

    # "Ralph Walker was last seen leaving the country on a boat, sailing out to the sea."
    "Ralph Walker最後一次被人目擊到，是在一艘離開本國、駛向大海的船上。"

